NK009(ta)002:0: dpal rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum
NK009(ta)002:1: bu'i 'grel pa snying po bsdus pa dpal chen dgyes
NK009(ta)002:2: pa'i zhal lung zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK009(ta)002:3: na mo gu ru sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa r+aa ya /
NK009(ta)002:4: sgrib bral mkha' dbyings rtsol rtog mtshan ma'i rdul gyis go skabs nam yang mi phyed kyang //
NK009(ta)002:5: ma rungs gdul daka'i yul la rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rjes 'bar ba'i phyag rgya rang shar ba //
NK009(ta)002:6: dus mtha'i me lce bye ba'i stobs kyis srid dang nyon mongs tshang tshing yud la sreg /
NK009(ta)002:7: bdud 'dul he ru ka dpal sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK009(ta)002:8: phrin las rdzogs mdzad lhag pa'i lha mchog des skyongs
NK009(ta)002:9: shig / dpal chen ye shes rol pa'i byin rlabs rgyun //
NK009(ta)002:10: gcig nas gcig brgyud rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang tshogs //
NK009(ta)002:11: spyi dang khyad par bka' bab gser gyi phreng //
NK009(ta)002:12: mkhon ston brgyud par bcas la dang bas 'dud //
NK009(ta)002:13: rtsod pa'i dus mthar u dum+b+aa ra ltar //
NK009(ta)002:14: ngo mtshar rnam thar blo 'das mkha' mthar son //
NK009(ta)002:15: bka' babs bdud ldan khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang //
NK009(ta)002:16: 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po snying dbus bsti //
NK009(ta)002:17: kun gsal ngos su snang byed bdag po bzhin //
NK009(ta)002:18: skye bar sbyangs pa'i mkhyen rab dri med la //
NK009(ta)002:19: gangs can mkhas pa sus kyang bskrun med pa //
NK009(ta)002:20: sa skya sana chen mchog de'i bka' drin las //
NK009(ta)002:21: gsar rnying kun gyi rtsod med rgyud sde ru //
NK009(ta)002:22: basngagasa pa'i me tog 'thor ba'i phrin las kyi //
NK009(ta)002:23: lha mchog rdo rje gzhon nu'i rtsa rgyud las //
NK009(ta)002:24: dum bu khol du byung ba'i rgyud 'di yang //
NK009(ta)002:25: legs par rtogs na phrin las rol pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:26: rgyud don man ngag lag len dang bcas pa //
NK009(ta)002:27: khong du chud phyir go sla nyung gsal gyi //
NK009(ta)002:28: rnam bshad blo ldan dga' ba'i skyed tshal dgod //
NK009(ta)002:29: 'dir phrin las phur pa rol pa'i rgyud sde chen
NK009(ta)002:30: po las bid+h+yot+ta ma la 'bum sde zhes rig pa
NK009(ta)002:31: mchog gi rgyud sde'i dum bu khol du phyung ba
NK009(ta)002:32: rtsa dum bu grags pa 'di nyid 'chad pa la
NK009(ta)002:33: / spyir gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i yo ga rnam
NK009(ta)002:34: pa gsum la 'chad lugs kyi chings chen po gsum
NK009(ta)002:35: / yod // de la thog mar bskyed pa ma
NK009(ta)002:36: h+aa yo ga'ang rgyud sde dang sgrub sde'i bshad srol
NK009(ta)002:37: / yod // gnyis // rgyud sde tan+t+ra chen po
NK009(ta)002:38: sde bco brgyad kyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa'
NK009(ta)002:39: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la 'phags yul pan chen so
NK009(ta)002:40: so'i 'grel t+ai ka dang sbyar te 'chad srol mang
NK009(ta)002:41: / yod // gnyis // rung // deng sang yongs
NK009(ta)002:42: grags pan chen bi ma la mi tra'i khog gzhung
NK009(ta)002:43: gi rjes su 'brangs nas bka' sde zur pa rnams
NK009(ta)002:44: kyis sa bcad lnga'am drug gi sgo nas 'chad pa
NK009(ta)002:46: zla gsang thig le sogs tan+t+ra gzhan rnams la grub
NK009(ta)002:47: pa'i slob dpon so sos 'chad tshul re re yod
NK009(ta)002:49: / 'dir phrin las phur pa rol pa'i rgyud sde
NK009(ta)002:52: bal po sh+ai la many+dzu gsum gyi dgongs pa bsdus
NK009(ta)002:53: pa 'grel chen 'bum nag gi dgongs pa ltar 'chad
NK009(ta)002:55: spyir phur pa'i rgyud kyi bsdu thabs gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:61: rtsa ba'i lha lnga bcu rtsa gcig dang /
NK009(ta)002:62: yan lag gi lha nyis stong phyed dang drug brgyar
NK009(ta)002:63: ngos 'dzin pa ste sa bcad chen po brgyad du
NK009(ta)002:64: bstan kyang / rgyud kyi thems sbyor bcu'i nang du gzhan rnams shugs kyis 'du ba ma zad /
NK009(ta)002:65: rtsa dum kho na'i dbang du byas na stod las byang chub sgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:66: smad las dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i dum bu gnyis su'ang 'adu'o //
NK009(ta)002:67: gong du spyir smos pa'i rgyud kyi bsdu thabs gnyis ni rtsa rgyud dang bshad rgyud gnyis te /
NK009(ta)002:68: dang po rig mchog 'bum sde dang rdo rje khros pa la sogs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:69: gnyis pa ni khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:70: rgyud kyi bshad thabs gsum ni rgyud dkar po gnas lung las /
NK009(ta)002:71: phur pa rgyud kyi rgyal po yin //
NK009(ta)002:72: phur pa lung gi bla ma yin //
NK009(ta)002:73: phur pa man ngag nges pa'i don //
NK009(ta)002:75: rgyud ltar rdo rje khros pa klong chen po bco brgyad nas bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:76: lung chen po nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:77: man ngag brgya rtsa brgyad du bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:78: rgyud kyi chings drug ni phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa las kyi gzhi gzung /
NK009(ta)002:79: dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum sngon du 'gro ba dang bcas te don gyi khog dbub /
NK009(ta)002:80: khams gsum na srog la dbang bskur nas srog gi ye shes sems dpas srog la dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)002:81: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing mchod cing bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud blang /
NK009(ta)002:82: gab pa'i sngags drug dang tshe lung khrus lung gis kha bskang te gdab pa'i las bya /
NK009(ta)002:83: mnan sreg 'phang gsum gyis las kyi mjug bsdu ba dang drug go //
NK009(ta)002:84: 'di dag gi don gsal la rgyas pa gu ru
NK009(ta)002:85: pad+mas mdzad pa'i rdo rje las rim sogs las rgyas
NK009(ta)002:86: par 'byung mod kyang 'dir yi ges 'jigs nas ma
NK009(ta)002:87: bris la / 'jam mgon kun dga' bsod nams kyis mdzad pa'i dkyil mchog dang /
NK009(ta)002:88: smad las kyi rnam bshad sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:89: 'dir skabs su babs pa rgyud kyi thems sbyor bcu ni /
NK009(ta)002:90: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum gyis spyi'i khog dbub /
NK009(ta)002:91: mtshan nyid rnam pa gsum gyis don gyi shan dbye /
NK009(ta)002:92: phur bu'i rgyu bzhis gang zag rnams pa bzhi mthar dbyung /
NK009(ta)002:93: sgrub lugs chen po gsum gyis phrin las kyi gzhung bsrang /
NK009(ta)002:94: thams cad 'dus pa'i sngags kyis ye shes kyi lha gnad la dbab /
NK009(ta)002:95: ngan sngags bsdu yig drug gsum bco brgyad kyis mkha' 'gro ma dngos su bkol /
NK009(ta)002:96: srog gi don po gsum gyis dmigs pa gsum gyi gnad dgrol /
NK009(ta)002:97: bsgral lugs chen po bco brgyad kyis brnag pa'i las bya /
NK009(ta)002:98: mthar phyin brgyad kyis las kyi kha bskang /
NK009(ta)002:99: mtha' brtul gsum gyis las kyi lto ba gdab ces pa dang bcu'o //
NK009(ta)002:100: de la dang po gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum gyis spyi'i khog dbub ces 'byung bas /
NK009(ta)002:103: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang gsum du sdud par mdzad kyang /
NK009(ta)002:104: 'dir go bde ba'i dbang gis spyi ltar 'chad na spyi dang bye brag gnyis so //
NK009(ta)002:105: dang po bstan pa spyi'i byung ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK009(ta)002:106: ye thog dang po'i sangs rgyas dpal kun bzang gdod
NK009(ta)002:107: ma'i mgon po nyid gzhi dbyings rig pa'i snying por
NK009(ta)002:108: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas /
NK009(ta)002:109: de'i rang rtsal 'gag pa med pa'i cho 'phrul bsam
NK009(ta)002:110: gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin chen po mnyam nyid yangs
NK009(ta)002:111: pa'i klong du bkod de gang 'dul gyi zhing sku'i
NK009(ta)002:112: snang ba 'byams klas pas mkha' khyab kyi 'gro ba'i
NK009(ta)002:114: yul dus 'di tsam gyis 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs
NK009(ta)002:115: kyi dbang du snang ba rnam 'dren kun las thugs
NK009(ta)002:116: bskyed pad+ma dkar po ltar 'phags pa /
NK009(ta)002:117: bdag cag gi ston pa sh+aakya thub pa 'di nyid kyis dang por thugs bskyed /
NK009(ta)002:118: bar du byang chub kyi spyod pa spyad /
NK009(ta)002:119: mthar mngon par sangs rgyas te mi mjed zhing 'dir
NK009(ta)002:120: mdzad pa chen po bcu gnyis ston pa mchog gi
NK009(ta)002:121: sprul pa'i sku'i tshul du bstan nas thun mong dang
NK009(ta)002:122: thun mong ma yin pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo mtha'
NK009(ta)002:123: yas pa zhig bskor bar mdzad pa las /
NK009(ta)002:124: thun mong gi gdul bya'i snang ngor sh+aakya'i rigs su
NK009(ta)002:125: 'khrungs nas sangs rgyas pa chags bral rab byung gi
NK009(ta)002:126: rnam pa can gyi sku dngos kyis yul w+aa ra
NK009(ta)002:127: na s+ai drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi gnas
NK009(ta)002:128: su lnga sde bzang po la bka' dang po bden
NK009(ta)002:130: rgyal po'i khab sogs su theg pa che chung gi
NK009(ta)002:131: dge 'dun sogs 'khor lha dang mi la sogs pa
NK009(ta)002:132: dpag tu med pa la bar pa mtshan nyid med
NK009(ta)002:134: yul pad+ma can sogs tha dad par tha ma nges
NK009(ta)002:135: pa don gyi chos 'khor te rnam pa gsum bskor
NK009(ta)002:136: zhing / gzhan yang rgyal po'i khab tu lha dang mir dge ba bcu'i chos 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:137: yul ma ga d+har rang rgyal la rten 'brel bcu
NK009(ta)002:138: gnyis kyi chos 'khor bskor ba sogs gang 'dul gdul
NK009(ta)002:139: bya'i skal ba dang rjes su 'tshams pa'i rol par
NK009(ta)002:140: 'char ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs so sor bstan pa
NK009(ta)002:142: don du de dag kyang chos 'khor rim pa gsum gyi khongs su mi 'du ba ma yin no //
NK009(ta)002:143: de las lha mi dang nyan rang gi theg pa rnam la theg pa thun mong ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:144: theg pa chen po la khyad par gyi theg pa zhes bya zhing /
NK009(ta)002:145: de la'ang rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis su mchis te /
NK009(ta)002:146: dbu sems kyi dgongs pa rnam par bzhag pa'i gzhung gi bka' rnams rgyu phar phyin dang /
NK009(ta)002:147: sngags phyi nang gi gzhung du gnas pa'i bka' rnams
NK009(ta)002:148: 'bras bu gsang ba sngags kyi theg pa zhes bya'o
NK009(ta)002:149: // theg chen mdo sngags kyi 'bras bu mthar thug
NK009(ta)002:150: sangs rgyas thob par 'dra yang lam zab mi zab
NK009(ta)002:151: kyi khyad par las 'bras bu mngon du byed pa
NK009(ta)002:152: la nye rig gi khyad shin tu che bas rgyu
NK009(ta)002:154: sngags la'ang phyi bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gsum las /
NK009(ta)002:155: bya rgyud la rig sngags kun gyi khog dbub dpung bzang gi rgyud sogs spyi rgyud drug /
NK009(ta)002:156: bye brag rigs gsum mgon po'i rgyud kyi skor sogs
NK009(ta)002:157: bya rgyud rnams ni thun mong gi gnas nee rany+dza
NK009(ta)002:158: na dang / khyad par gyi gnas lcang lo can
NK009(ta)002:159: la sogs par lha'i dbang po sogs kyi ngor ston
NK009(ta)002:160: pa nyid rigs gsum sems dpa' sogs kyi rnam par
NK009(ta)002:162: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud
NK009(ta)002:163: sogs spyod rgyud rnams ni snga ma dang yo ga'i
NK009(ta)002:164: rgyud dang khog mtshungs su ci rigs par gsungs /
NK009(ta)002:165: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud la rnal 'byor dang /
NK009(ta)002:167: shin tu rnal 'byor ram rnal 'byor mchog gi rgyud gsum du yod pa las /
NK009(ta)002:168: dang po thun mong gi gnas sum cu rtsa gsum
NK009(ta)002:169: dang khyad par gyi gnas 'og min du ston pa
NK009(ta)002:170: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyi rnam par gsang
NK009(ta)002:172: yo ga gzhung chen bam po sum brgya pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:173: lung chen rgyud bzhi sogs 'khor lha dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams la gsungs pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:174: 'di dag gi rnam bzhag gsang sngags gsar rnying bzhed
NK009(ta)002:175: pa thun mong du gnas pa las mi mthun pa'i
NK009(ta)002:176: khyad par chen po ma mchis so //
NK009(ta)002:177: rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams
NK009(ta)002:178: ni gtso bor tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad la
NK009(ta)002:179: 'dren tshul mi 'dra ba 'ga' re mchis kyang /
NK009(ta)002:180: chos kyi rgyal po klong chen rab 'byams kyi bzhed pa ltar na /
NK009(ta)002:181: sku'i sku rgyud glang po rab 'bogs /
NK009(ta)002:182: sku'i gsung rgyud glang po chur 'jug /
NK009(ta)002:183: sku'i thugs rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor te sku rgyud gsum /
NK009(ta)002:184: gsung gi sku rgyud ri bo brtsegs pa /
NK009(ta)002:185: gsung gi gsung rgyud pad+ma dbang chen /
NK009(ta)002:186: gsung gi thugs rgyud zla gsang thig le ste gsung rgyud gsum /
NK009(ta)002:187: thugs kyi sku rgyud rtse mo 'dus pa /
NK009(ta)002:188: thugs kyi gsung rgyud gcig las 'phros pa /
NK009(ta)002:189: thugs kyi thugs rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa ste thugs rgyud gsum /
NK009(ta)002:190: yon tan gyi sku rgyud sgron me 'bar ba /
NK009(ta)002:191: yon tan gyi gsung rgyud bdud rtsi sa ma ya 'bum sde /
NK009(ta)002:192: yon tan gyi thugs rgyud dpal mchog dang po ste /
NK009(ta)002:194: phrin las kyi sku rgyud dpal phreng dkar mo /
NK009(ta)002:195: phrin las kyi gsung rgyud ma mo rgyud lung /
NK009(ta)002:196: phrin las kyi thugs rgyud ta ma la 'bum sde ste phrin las kyi rgyud gsum /
NK009(ta)002:198: spyi'i gsung rgyud sa ma ya bkod pa /
NK009(ta)002:199: spyi'i thugs rgyud gsang ba sgyu 'phrul dang bco brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:200: de dag kun gyi rtsa ba ni gsang ba snying
NK009(ta)002:201: po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal
NK009(ta)002:202: po ste tshul te dag tu phyis nas mi las
NK009(ta)002:203: 'das pa'i skal ldan gyi rgyal po dzahl bshad nas
NK009(ta)002:204: rim par byon par gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:205: mdor na ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams ni ston
NK009(ta)002:206: pa nyid dpal chen po'am rnam par snang mdzad sogs
NK009(ta)002:207: su sprul nas / zhu ba po rdo rje 'dzin
NK009(ta)002:208: pa dang skal ldan gyi rgyal po dzah la sogs
NK009(ta)002:209: pa 'khor 'dus pa mchog rnams la gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:210: de'ang bsdu na thabs shes kyi rgyud gnyis su 'adu'o //
NK009(ta)002:211: rnal 'byor mchog gi rgyud la rdzogs pa a nu yo ga'i theg pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:212: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i theg pa gnyis las /
NK009(ta)002:213: dang po rgyal mo pu ri'i tshal du ston pa
NK009(ta)002:214: nyid dpal kun tu bzang po'am rdo rje sems dpar
NK009(ta)002:215: sprul pa la lang+ka'i bdag pos zhus nas mdo bzhi
NK009(ta)002:216: dems dang lngar bsdus te bka' stsal /
NK009(ta)002:217: a ti yo ga ni gnas rgyal po pu ri'i
NK009(ta)002:218: tshal dang za ma pu ri'i tshal du ston pa
NK009(ta)002:219: nyid dpal kun tu bzang po kun byed rgyal por
NK009(ta)002:220: sprul nas nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor rnams la
NK009(ta)002:221: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i
NK009(ta)002:222: rgyud sogs rdzogs pa chen po sems mchog gi skor
NK009(ta)002:223: la sogs pa gsungs pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:226: a ti gsum ni gsang sngags rnying ma kho na'i
NK009(ta)002:227: khyad chos te sngags gsar ma la ma grags shing
NK009(ta)002:228: / de dag las ches rmad du byung ba'i gnad lhag par mnga' ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:229: de ltar chos sgo rab 'byams gsungs pa de dag
NK009(ta)002:230: kyang 'dzam gling na gnas pa'i mi dang nyan rang
NK009(ta)002:231: byang sems kyi rigs can rnams la sh+aakya'i dbang po'i
NK009(ta)002:232: sku dngos kyis rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa rnams
NK009(ta)002:234: lha rnams dang rigs gsum mgon po sogs sems dpa'
NK009(ta)002:235: chen po rnams la kun tu rig pa snang mdzad
NK009(ta)002:236: chen por snang ba'i skus phyi rgyud sde gsum gsungs
NK009(ta)002:237: pa dang / rigs lnga sras bcas rnams la kun
NK009(ta)002:238: bzang du sprul nas nang rgyud yo ga gsum gsungs
NK009(ta)002:239: pa de dag kyang gdul bya'i blo stobs tha dad
NK009(ta)002:240: dang mthun par d+ha na ko sha /
NK009(ta)002:243: ri me ri 'bar ba sogs thun mong gi gnas dang /
NK009(ta)002:247: thar pa chen po'i gzhal med khang la sogs pa
NK009(ta)002:248: khyad par gyi gnas rnams su thun mong dang khyad
NK009(ta)002:249: par gyi ston pa sku so sor snang bas 'khor
NK009(ta)002:250: gyi gdul bya mchog phal la rgyu 'bras kyi chos
NK009(ta)002:251: 'khor bskor ba nyid du snang ba'i cho 'phrul 'ba'
NK009(ta)002:253: don du ston pa gcig nyid kyi gang 'dul sku
NK009(ta)002:254: dang ye shes mdzad phrin tha dad pa so sor
NK009(ta)002:255: snang bas gang 'dul der ston gyi rnam par 'phrul
NK009(ta)002:256: pa sna tshogs pas chos sgo bgrang du mi spyod
NK009(ta)002:257: par phyes pa dag rgyas par gsungs pa chos phung
NK009(ta)002:259: 'bring por bsdus te gsungs pa gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:260: bsdus te gsungs pa theg pa rim pa dgu zhes grags pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:261: gzhan yang rnam gzhag mtha' yas pa mnga' ba yin mod kyi /
NK009(ta)002:262: don du rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa rnam pa gnyis su nges pa 'adu'o //
NK009(ta)002:263: bka' de'ang zhal nas gsungs pa /
NK009(ta)002:265: rjes su gnang ba ste gsung tshul gyi sgo nas dbye ba gsum du bzhag go //
NK009(ta)002:266: de ltar bshad pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'i bka'
NK009(ta)002:267: de dag gsung dus kyi 'khor rnams las so so'i
NK009(ta)002:268: sdud pa po rnams kyi mi brjed pa'i gzungs su
NK009(ta)002:269: bzung ste yi ger btab nas 'jig rten gyi khams
NK009(ta)002:270: 'dir dar rgyas su mdzad pa yin te /
NK009(ta)002:271: rgyu phar phyin gyis theg pa thun mong ba rnams
NK009(ta)002:272: gnas brtan 'od srung chen po sogs kyis bka' bsdu
NK009(ta)002:273: bar mdzad nas mi nas mir brgyud de dar zhing
NK009(ta)002:274: / theg chen kha cig 'jam dpal sogs kyis bsdus
NK009(ta)002:275: nas byang sems phal mo che las brgyud de mi
NK009(ta)002:277: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa ni mi
NK009(ta)002:278: yul gyi gdul bya thun mong gi ngor sh+aakya'i rgyal
NK009(ta)002:279: po nyid kyi zhal nas mngon du ma gsungs par
NK009(ta)002:280: skal ldan dbang rab rnams kyi don du lkog chos
NK009(ta)002:281: su bstan par mdzad pas gdul bya dman pa dag
NK009(ta)002:282: gi ngor gsang sngags la the tshom bzlog pa'i don
NK009(ta)002:283: du skabs de'i gdul bya thun mong ba'i 'khor gyi
NK009(ta)002:284: snang ngor sh+aakya'i dbang po nyid kyi zhal nas gsang
NK009(ta)002:285: sngags kyi bstan pa 'di nyid gdod mi yul du
NK009(ta)002:286: 'byung ba'i tshul dngos su lung bstan par ltar mdzad
NK009(ta)002:287: de / mdo sde gadamagasa ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po las /
NK009(ta)002:289: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK009(ta)002:290: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK009(ta)002:291: rgyal po dzahyi khang thog tu //
NK009(ta)002:292: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK009(ta)002:293: lag na rdo rjes ston par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:294: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul dang mthun par /
NK009(ta)002:295: ston pa'i mthus rigs lnga'i rgyal ba dang rgyal tshab rnams la rjes su bskul bar mdzad de /
NK009(ta)002:296: 'bras bu'i chos 'di nyid gser gyi glegs bam la
NK009(ta)002:297: bee d+aur+ya'i yi ger bris nas thugs rje gcig tu
NK009(ta)002:298: mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul las rgyal po
NK009(ta)002:299: dzah'i khang steng du nam mkha' las rang babs kyi
NK009(ta)002:300: tshul du snang ba rgyal po dzahdang slob dpon ku
NK009(ta)002:301: ku r+aa dzas de'i don rnams rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK009(ta)002:302: mthus rtogs nas mi yul 'dir gsang sngags dar ba
NK009(ta)002:303: dang / gzhan yang 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis lha'i gnas dang /
NK009(ta)002:304: spyan ras gzigs kyis klu'i yul dang /
NK009(ta)002:305: phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin gyi gnas su snang bar mdzad /
NK009(ta)002:306: 'dzam gling 'dir kri ya w+aa ra na s+ai dang /
NK009(ta)002:307: yo ga rnams ri ma la ya'i rtse me ri 'bar ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:308: ma ha dang a nu rgyal po dzahnyida kyi gnas dang /
NK009(ta)002:309: a ti yo ga d+ha na ko sha'i gling du
NK009(ta)002:310: bshad cing sgrub par byas te rgya cher 'phel ba'o
NK009(ta)002:311: // gzhan yang lung bzhi dems dang lnga ni bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum gyi spyi rgyud dang /
NK009(ta)002:312: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad ni lta ba a ti dang
NK009(ta)002:313: spyod pa ma h+aar gtogs pas a nu'i rgyud du'ang
NK009(ta)002:314: gsungs te / bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gyi gnad bstan pa'i cha nas ji ltar bzhag kyang chog go //
NK009(ta)002:315: de dag gis ni bka' spyi'i byung ba gsang sngags
NK009(ta)002:316: rnying ma la grags pa gtso bo bzung ste mdor
NK009(ta)002:318: de dang rjes 'brel bstan bcos kyi byung ba'ang mdor bsdu na /
NK009(ta)002:319: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgya lhag
NK009(ta)002:320: tsam song ba'i 'og tu yul yangs pa can du
NK009(ta)002:321: nyan thos sde pa tha dad pa'i dgra bcom pa
NK009(ta)002:322: lnga brgya 'dus nas bstan bcos bye brag bshad mdzod
NK009(ta)002:323: chen mo bam po sum brgya pa mdzad pa bstan
NK009(ta)002:324: pa 'di'i bstan bcos kyi thog ma yin la /
NK009(ta)002:325: de nas bzung ste zab pa dang rgya che ba'i
NK009(ta)002:326: bka'i dgongs don 'grel ba'i shing rta chen po klu
NK009(ta)002:327: thogs gnyis la sogs 'dzam gling mdzes rgyan slob tshogs
NK009(ta)002:328: dang bcas pas brtsams pa'i bstan bcos rnams dang /
NK009(ta)002:329: sngags kyi lugs la byang chub sems 'grel skor gsum dang /
NK009(ta)002:330: grub pa sde bdun du grags pa sogs kyis mtshon
NK009(ta)002:331: grub chen rig 'dzin rnams kyis mdzad pa'i bstan bcos
NK009(ta)002:332: mtha' klas pa zhig byung zhing /
NK009(ta)002:333: bstan bcos kyi ngo bo rgyal ba'i bka'i rjes su
NK009(ta)002:334: 'brangs nas rtsom pa po mtshan nyid dang ldan pas
NK009(ta)002:338: lung don rig pa gsum mam /
NK009(ta)002:341: zab mo bkrol ba sogs sam /
NK009(ta)002:342: bka' spyi dang bye brag gi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i dbye ba yod pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:344: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK009(ta)002:345: chos rnams bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'du //
NK009(ta)002:346: legs par gsungs dang de yi dgongs 'grel ba //
NK009(ta)002:347: de yi dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa 'di //
NK009(ta)002:348: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:349: zhes gsungs pa ltar bstan pa spyi'i byung tshul mdo tsam smos zin nas /
NK009(ta)002:350: gnyis pa phur pa phrin las rol pa'i rgyud kyi byung ba bye brag tu 'chad pa la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:351: phrin las kyi rgyud byon tshul spyir bstan /
NK009(ta)002:352: rtsa dum dang 'brel ba'i mkhon lugs kyi bka' babs byung tshul bye brag tu dbye ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:354: sgrub pa bka' brgyad kyi gleng gzhi dang sbyar te bshad du yod kyang /
NK009(ta)002:355: 'dir rgyud sde ltar 'chad pa skabs su babs pas /
NK009(ta)002:359: sprul skus tshig brda sbyar nas bshad //
NK009(ta)002:360: ces gsungs pa ltar rgyal ba dgongs brgyud /
NK009(ta)002:362: gang zag snyan brgyud gsum gyis gsungs te /
NK009(ta)002:364: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang
NK009(ta)002:365: po tshad med pa'i thugs rje dang thabs la mkhas
NK009(ta)002:366: pa gang gis chos kyi dbyings spros pa med pa'i
NK009(ta)002:367: pho brang nas g.yo ba mi mnga' bzhin du rang
NK009(ta)002:368: bzhin thugs rje'i byin rlabs las /
NK009(ta)002:369: rang snang dag pa sku gsung thugs lhun grub 'og
NK009(ta)002:370: min stug po bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du rigs lnga'i
NK009(ta)002:371: sangs rgyas kyi rnam par bzhengs te /
NK009(ta)002:372: rang las gnyis su med pa'i 'khor rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK009(ta)002:373: rigs gsum mgon po la sogs 'bras bu'i sems dpa'
NK009(ta)002:374: rnams zab cing rgya che ba'i chos phun sum tshogs
NK009(ta)002:375: pa gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa gnyis med rang
NK009(ta)002:376: rig rang shar gyi tshul du gsungs te chos dang
NK009(ta)002:377: ston 'khor dbyer med dgongs pa'i klong chen po gcig
NK009(ta)002:378: tu 'khyil ba ni rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa
NK009(ta)002:380: rigs gsum mgon po de dag gis lha klu gnod
NK009(ta)002:381: sbyin gsum la bshad nas so so'i tshom bu 'bum
NK009(ta)002:382: sde dang bcas pa sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'tshob par
NK009(ta)002:383: gyur / de nas rim par brgyud de shar phyogs
NK009(ta)002:384: sa ho ra'i rgyal po dzahls o rgyan gyi mkhan
NK009(ta)002:386: slob dpon bi ma mi tra /
NK009(ta)002:387: slob dpon sh+ai la many+dzu ste mkhas pa mi gsum
NK009(ta)002:388: la brgyud pa'ang brda dang tshig tsam res grol ba
NK009(ta)002:389: thob ste dbyings dang ye shes zung 'jug gi ngo
NK009(ta)002:390: bo yi dam lha dang dgongs pa mnyam nyid du
NK009(ta)002:391: gyur pa dag ni rig 'dzin rig brgyud kyi dgongs
NK009(ta)002:394: dpal chos sku kun tu bzang po nas da lta'i
NK009(ta)002:395: bar snyan nas snyan du brgyud pa'i bka' zab mo
NK009(ta)002:396: ma nyams par byon pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:397: rgyas par shes 'dod na brgyud pa'i yi ge so so las rtogs par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:398: de ltar brgyud pa gsum gyis khyad par byas pa'i
NK009(ta)002:399: phur pa phrin las rol pa 'di nyid kyi lo
NK009(ta)002:400: rgyus la gsum / gdul bya ji ltar byung ba /
NK009(ta)002:401: 'dul byed gang gis btul ba'i tshul /
NK009(ta)002:402: 'dul thabs ji ltar mdzad pa'i tshul gsum gyis shes par bya ste /
NK009(ta)002:403: rgyas par rgyud dang gzhung 'grel gzhan du shes la /
NK009(ta)002:404: 'dir snying po tsam bsdus te 'chad na /
NK009(ta)002:406: phur pa myang 'das kyi rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:407: karma he ru kas khrag 'thung chen po la zhus pa /
NK009(ta)002:408: srin po ru dra gdug pa 'di //
NK009(ta)002:409: rgyu dang rkyen ni ci las byung //
NK009(ta)002:411: las skal spyod pa ci zhig byed /
NK009(ta)002:412: ma btul ba yi skyon ni ci //
NK009(ta)002:413: btul na yon tan ci zhig thob //
NK009(ta)002:415: khrag 'thung rdo rjes bka' stsal pa //
NK009(ta)002:416: log pa'i sems can chen po 'di //
NK009(ta)002:417: dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu las byung //
NK009(ta)002:418: rkyen ni bla ma spangs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:419: 'bras bu nyon mongs lnga ru smin //
NK009(ta)002:420: las skal chags sdang spyod la zhen //
NK009(ta)002:421: ma btul lha mi'i srid pa brlag /
NK009(ta)002:422: sangs rgyas zhing yang stongs par byed //
NK009(ta)002:423: btul na yon tan dpag med de //
NK009(ta)002:424: dug gsum rtsad gcod 'khor dong sprugs //
NK009(ta)002:425: zhes gsungs pa ltar rdo rje khros pa'i rtsa rgyud las kyang gsungs pa bzhin /
NK009(ta)002:426: sngon 'das pa'i dus bskal pa kun nas bkod pa
NK009(ta)002:427: zhes bya ba la yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK009(ta)002:428: rgyas mngon par 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i bstan pa'i
NK009(ta)002:429: dus su thar pa nag po'i g.yog dan 'bag ces
NK009(ta)002:431: de'i dus su dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu zhes
NK009(ta)002:432: bya ba'i drung nas thar pa nag pos gdams ngag
NK009(ta)002:433: log par go nas gsang sngags 'chol bar spyad pa
NK009(ta)002:434: sogs ma rungs pa'i las kyi rnam par smin pas
NK009(ta)002:435: ma rungs pa'i skye ba brgyud mar blangs nas khams
NK009(ta)002:436: gsum na che ba'i gdug pa can du gyur nas
NK009(ta)002:437: sems can thams cad bsad cing zos te de'i gnyen
NK009(ta)002:438: po 'jig rten na su'ang med pa'i ma tram ru
NK009(ta)002:439: dra zhes bya ba zhig byung ba ni gang gdul
NK009(ta)002:440: bya'o // gnyis pa de 'dul byed gang gis btul ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:441: de'i tshe karma he ru kas dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK009(ta)002:442: ba rnams bskul nas 'og min du bka' bgros te
NK009(ta)002:443: 'gro ba'i don du ru dra zhi ba'i sgo nas
NK009(ta)002:444: 'dul bar dgongs kyang ma thul nas /
NK009(ta)002:446: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK009(ta)002:447: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK009(ta)002:448: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo la //
NK009(ta)002:449: khro bo de bzhin gshegs kun mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:450: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK009(ta)002:451: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
NK009(ta)002:452: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis /
NK009(ta)002:453: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK009(ta)002:454: zhes bud+d+ha thams cad thugs rje chen po'i sgo nas
NK009(ta)002:455: bka' bgros te rdo rje rta'i tshogs sogs khro bo
NK009(ta)002:456: chen po rnams rim par spros te btul ba'i tshul
NK009(ta)002:457: mdzad pa ni 'dul byed kyi khyad par bstan pa'o
NK009(ta)002:458: // gsum pa 'dul thabs kyi khyad par ni /
NK009(ta)002:459: yang dus gsum gyi bud+d+ha thams cad bka' bgros nas
NK009(ta)002:460: sbyang gzhi dang sbyong byed la dgongs bzhin pas thabs
NK009(ta)002:461: kyi khyad par thun mong min pas 'dul bar dgongs
NK009(ta)002:462: te / dus gsum bud+d+ha thams cad kyi sprul pa
NK009(ta)002:463: gcig tu bsdus nas ru dra thar pa nag por
NK009(ta)002:464: te / sprul / de'i chung ma kro d+hi shwa
NK009(ta)002:465: ri ma la ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad
NK009(ta)002:466: nas srin mo'i lhums su zla dkyil la byang sems
NK009(ta)002:467: h'u gi rnam par phab ste bzhag /
NK009(ta)002:468: gzhan yang 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad sprul pas dbang du byas /
NK009(ta)002:469: de nas dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK009(ta)002:470: sprul pa dbyings su mi dmigs par mdzad nas rim
NK009(ta)002:471: gyis 'khor gtum mo dang srin mo rnams la'ang phag
NK009(ta)002:472: dang dom kyi mgo can la sogs pa'i ltas ngan
NK009(ta)002:473: mang po skyes / ru dra'i chung ma kro d+hi
NK009(ta)002:474: shwa ri l+aa'ang bu rdo rje gzhon nu dbu gsum
NK009(ta)002:475: mang po skyes / phyag drug pa / rdo rje'i gshog pas bar snang khyab pa /
NK009(ta)002:476: k+ai la ya'i sgra sgrogs pa dang bcas pa skyes
NK009(ta)002:477: 'dug pa ru dras mthong ma thag 'khor dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:481: rdo rje khros pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:482: khro chen rab tu khros pa mthong ba yis //
NK009(ta)002:483: skad cig tsam la ru dra dngangs shing skrag /
NK009(ta)002:484: phyogs bcu kun tu 'bros pa'i tshul yang bstan //
NK009(ta)002:485: sdug bsngal chen po de yi dus su myangs //
NK009(ta)002:487: de nas brgyal sangs pa dang langs nas 'khor rnams
NK009(ta)002:488: la bos te smre sngags mang du bton pas bdud
NK009(ta)002:490: mtshon cha'i char phab pa dang bstun ru dras kyang
NK009(ta)002:491: dbu gsum phyag drug tu byas pa dang rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:492: gzhon nus dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad par sprul te
NK009(ta)002:493: ba spu'i bu ga nas kyang de 'dra ba dpag
NK009(ta)002:494: tu med par sprul te ngag smra brjod dang bral
NK009(ta)002:496: ru dras kyang dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad par sprul
NK009(ta)002:497: pa'i gnyen por rdo rje gzhon nus dbu phyag stong
NK009(ta)002:498: stong / spyan bye ba stong du sprul /
NK009(ta)002:499: dbu dgu pa mang po ba spu'i bu ga nas kyang bkyes /
NK009(ta)002:500: khro bo bcu sprul nas phyogs skyong bcu gdan du bting /
NK009(ta)002:501: de nas rdo rje gzhon nu'i spyi gtsug nas ha sa ya ra hri ta na ya 'phros /
NK009(ta)002:502: ru dra'i spyi gtsug tu zhugs nas skyob pa'i lha dang phral /
NK009(ta)002:503: gzhan yang gab pa'i sngags drug rnams sku'i gnas so
NK009(ta)002:504: so nas spros te ru dra'i gnas so sor zhugs
NK009(ta)002:508: zhal du bstab pa sogs mdzad /
NK009(ta)002:509: bdud kyi 'khor rnams kyang so sor byer /
NK009(ta)002:510: dus der rdo rje gzhon nu la dus gsum gyi
NK009(ta)002:511: bud+d+ha thams cad kyis rdo rje srin po'i ngur dbyangs
NK009(ta)002:512: kyis bstod do // rdo rje rta'i tshogs kyis rta'i rngams dbyangs kyis dpa' bkong /
NK009(ta)002:513: de'i tshe rdo rje gzhon nus ru dra'i kha t+w+aam phrogs te phung po la thur ma btsugs te /
NK009(ta)002:514: a la la hohzhesa gsungs te zhal du gsol nas
NK009(ta)002:515: khyur mid mdzad de phyal du sbyangs pas skye ba
NK009(ta)002:516: grangs med pa'i lus blangs pa ni dran /
NK009(ta)002:517: las dge sdig mi bslu bar ni rig /
NK009(ta)002:518: dus der ru dras smre sngags brjod do //
NK009(ta)002:519: de nas rdo rje gzhon nu'i gsang ba nas bton
NK009(ta)002:520: te mdun du bzhag nas spyo ba brgyad kyi sgo
NK009(ta)002:521: nas spyos / 'khor sde brgyad kyis kyang bshags pa
NK009(ta)002:522: re byas nas rang rang gi mgo bo bcad de
NK009(ta)002:523: phul skabs der ru dras smras ba /
NK009(ta)002:524: bsnams nas bton pa thugs rje chung //
NK009(ta)002:527: ma dang sring mo bran mo rnams //
NK009(ta)002:529: dbus su mchis skal mi ldan gyi //
NK009(ta)002:531: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyi //
NK009(ta)002:532: lhag ma kha phrus bran la stsol //
NK009(ta)002:535: ru dra ma rungs de yi dus su btul //
NK009(ta)002:536: khro bo'i rgyal po rdo rje gzhon nu la //
NK009(ta)002:537: gzugs kyi phung po gdan du rab tu bting //
NK009(ta)002:538: rna ba'i dbang pos zhi ba'i chos kyang nyan //
NK009(ta)002:539: yid ni 'gyod pa'i smre bshags mang du byas //
NK009(ta)002:541: ru dra gtso bo'i gdan du gting /
NK009(ta)002:542: 'khor rnams kyis kyang phyogs skyong bcu la sogs pa pho kha sbubs /
NK009(ta)002:544: byin pa 'khril bar gdan du bting /
NK009(ta)002:547: ru dra 'di ma h+aa k+aa lar byas te sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa bsrungs nas /
NK009(ta)002:548: 'og phyogs kyi 'jig rten du bcom ldan 'das su lung bstan /
NK009(ta)002:549: kho'i thod mkhar rdo rje phur pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK009(ta)002:550: du byin gyis brlabs pa la brten nas rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:551: phur pa'i lha tshogs rten dang brten par bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:552: thams cad de ltar byung bar gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:553: don du sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs gnyis su med
NK009(ta)002:554: pa'i ye shes chen po rnam pa phrin las gang
NK009(ta)002:555: 'dul gyi rol pa thams cad rtags kyi phyag rgya'i
NK009(ta)002:556: gzugs su rang shar ba nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:557: de lta bu'i dpal rdo rje gzhon nu phur pa
NK009(ta)002:558: phrin las rol pa'i rgyud rnams he ru ka nyid
NK009(ta)002:559: kyis ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du rang byung
NK009(ta)002:560: rdo rje n+aang mi shigs ba'i sgra dbyangs su rang
NK009(ta)002:561: shar ba'i tshul gyis gsungs pa'i khongs su rgyud thams
NK009(ta)002:562: cad 'du ba'ang / spyir phyi rgyud sde gsum /
NK009(ta)002:563: nang rgyud gsum la'ang ma h+aa yo ga thabs pha'i rgyud /
NK009(ta)002:564: a nu yo ga shes rab ma'i rgyud //
NK009(ta)002:565: a ti yo ga gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sde'am
NK009(ta)002:566: theg pa gsum zhes bya ba'i rnam gzhag mdzad cing
NK009(ta)002:567: / yang pha rgyud la do ha skor dang /
NK009(ta)002:568: ma rgyud la sgyu 'phrul skor dang /
NK009(ta)002:569: gnyis med rgyud la sems phyogs skor zhes grags par
NK009(ta)002:570: gsungs pa de dag phyogs tsam gong du bstan pa'i
NK009(ta)002:571: spyi'i byung ba'i sa khongs su bstan zin la /
NK009(ta)002:572: bye brag tu slob dpon lang lab kyi bzhed pas
NK009(ta)002:573: rdo rje phur pa 'di la rang rkang tshugs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:575: rgyud chung bcu drug ces bzhed de /
NK009(ta)002:576: de la rang gzhung tshugs pa'i rgyud sum cu rtsa bdun ni /
NK009(ta)002:577: rtsa ba lta bu'i rgyud gsum /
NK009(ta)002:581: phyi ma'i phyi ma gsang ba sde drug /
NK009(ta)002:582: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa'i rgyud lnga /
NK009(ta)002:583: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa'i rgyud lnga /
NK009(ta)002:585: drag po rme thabs kyi rgyud gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:586: phrin las gtso bor ston pa 'bum skos dang sum cu rtsa bdun no //
NK009(ta)002:587: de ltar na bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga thabs
NK009(ta)002:588: kyi rgyud la tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad la
NK009(ta)002:589: sogs pa'i rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i nang
NK009(ta)002:590: nas phrin las rigs kyi phur bu'i rgyud lung man
NK009(ta)002:591: ngag thams cad o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma thod
NK009(ta)002:592: phreng rtsal la lhag par bka' babs shing /
NK009(ta)002:593: grub pa'i slob dpon chen po de nyid nges pa'i
NK009(ta)002:594: don du gdod ma'i rgyal po dpal chen rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:595: gzhon nu dang gnyis med mnyam pa'i klong du mngon
NK009(ta)002:597: tshur mthong rnams kyi snang ngor lhag pa'i lha mchog
NK009(ta)002:598: rdo rje gzhon nus sku'i sgo nas zhal dngos su
NK009(ta)002:599: bstan / gsung gi sgo nas phur pa'i rgyud rnams bka' stsal /
NK009(ta)002:600: thugs kyi sgo nas dbyings rig dbyer med du ngo
NK009(ta)002:601: sprad pas shes bya thams cad la ye shes chags
NK009(ta)002:603: gdul bya drang ba'i don du bka' babs kyi slob
NK009(ta)002:604: dpon pra b+ha hasti las phrin las phur pa'i chos
NK009(ta)002:605: skor thams cad bum pa gang byo'i tshul du gsan
NK009(ta)002:606: pa'i tshul bstan / gangs can ljongs su chos rgyal
NK009(ta)002:607: khri srong lde'u btsan gyis spyan drangs nas pheb pa'i
NK009(ta)002:608: lam bar na bod kyi lha srin ma rungs pa
NK009(ta)002:609: thams cad rdo rje phur pa'i skur bzhengs nas btul
NK009(ta)002:611: sa gzhi btul nas bsam yas gtsug lag khang bzhengs
NK009(ta)002:612: pa sogs dam pa'i chos kyi nyin byed thog mar
NK009(ta)002:613: 'char ba'i skabs su skal ldan gyi rje 'bangs rnams
NK009(ta)002:614: rdo rje theg pa'i lam zab so so'i skal ba
NK009(ta)002:615: dang 'tshams par gsang chos su 'chad pa'i skabs su
NK009(ta)002:616: bar chad sel ba'i lha mchog rdo rje gzhon nu'i
NK009(ta)002:617: chos skor rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa re gnang ba
NK009(ta)002:618: las phur pa rgyal po lugs /
NK009(ta)002:620: lcam lugs gtsos bka' nas bka' ru brgyud pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:621: phal cher gter du sbas pa phyis su rje 'bangs
NK009(ta)002:622: so so'i sprul pa rnams kyis rim par bton pa'i
NK009(ta)002:623: gter ma'i rigs shin tu mang pa mchis so //
NK009(ta)002:624: gnyis pa rtsa dum dang 'brel ba mkhon lugs kyi
NK009(ta)002:625: bka' babs byung tshul bye brag tu dbye ba ni
NK009(ta)002:626: / gong du ji skad bshad pa bzhin phrin las
NK009(ta)002:627: rdo rje gzhon nu dang dbyer med pa thod phreng
NK009(ta)002:628: rtsal 'chang chen pos sad mi mi bdun gyi ya
NK009(ta)002:629: gyal mkhon n+aa gen+d+ra rak+shi ta la rgyud lung man
NK009(ta)002:630: ngag dang bcas pa mnog chos su stsal ba de
NK009(ta)002:631: nas brtsams mkhon rigs sa skya par yang phur gnyis
NK009(ta)002:632: kyi bka' babs gzhan dang mi mnyam pas grub brnyes
NK009(ta)002:633: gser ri'i phreng ba bar ma chad pa byon pa
NK009(ta)002:634: / yin cing / mkhon dkon mchog rgyal pos dpe
NK009(ta)002:635: phal cher dus skabs der 'gro don mi 'byung bar
NK009(ta)002:636: dgongs te gter du sba bar brtsams pa na chos
NK009(ta)002:637: srung gis 'khu ldog byung ste rtsa ba tsam slar
NK009(ta)002:638: phyung ste rje btsun gong ma rnams lnga nas da
NK009(ta)002:639: lta'i bar thugs dam nyams bzhes mthar phyin mdzad cing
NK009(ta)002:640: / yin cing / / yig cha'i rigs kyang rgyas bsdus mang du bzhugs /
NK009(ta)002:641: rtsa rgyud bid+h+yot+ta ma 'bum sde'i nang nas gu ru
NK009(ta)002:642: pad+ma nyid kyis rdo rje rigs kyi le'u zur du
NK009(ta)002:643: phyung ba phur pa rtsa ba'i dum bu zhes bya
NK009(ta)002:644: ba 'di nyid snga 'gyur rnyid ma'i rgyud 'bum gral
NK009(ta)002:645: du bzhugs kyang / sngags gsar ma ba rnams kyis
NK009(ta)002:646: rnying rgyud khas mi len pas bag la zha ba'i
NK009(ta)002:647: skabs kyang chos rje sa skya pan chen nyid shangs
NK009(ta)002:648: sreg shing na bzhugs pa'i tshe mgo ban bdud rtsi
NK009(ta)002:649: rgyal po zhes bya ba'i sngags pa gcig gis dpe
NK009(ta)002:650: cha ser hrul zhig chos rje nyid la phul byung
NK009(ta)002:651: ba la gzigs pas phur pa rtsa dum gyi rgya
NK009(ta)002:652: dpe gu ru rin po che'i phyag dpe dngos su
NK009(ta)002:653: 'dug pa mkhyen nas bsu ba'i bkod pa dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:655: de nyid du bod skad la bsgyur bar mdzad pa
NK009(ta)002:656: 'di ni khungs btsun zhing bka' yin la lhad med
NK009(ta)002:657: pa kho na ste yid ches kyi gnas dam par
NK009(ta)002:659: 'di nyid kyi nye brgyud khyad par can ni /
NK009(ta)002:660: gangs can tsam na 'gran zla dang bral ba'i mkhas grub kyi rgyal po /
NK009(ta)002:661: 'phags pa'i yul gyi shing rta chen po rnams dang
NK009(ta)002:662: gnyis su ma dmigs pa bka' babs bdun gyi gsang
NK009(ta)002:663: mdzod la dbang thob par 'jigs bral rdo rje'i slob
NK009(ta)002:664: dpon chen po 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po kun
NK009(ta)002:665: dga' bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po zhes mtshan
NK009(ta)002:666: yongs su grags pa de la sa chen kun dga'
NK009(ta)002:667: snying po'i ye shes kyi skus lan gsum du rjes
NK009(ta)002:668: su bzung nas / lan gsum pa'i skabs rtsa dum
NK009(ta)002:669: 'di nyid kyi bka' lung gnang ste 'chad spel gyis
NK009(ta)002:670: shig pa'i rdo rje'i gsung gi rjes su gnang ba
NK009(ta)002:671: su bzung nas / thob pa bzhin / kho bo
NK009(ta)002:672: cag la bka' lung ljags bshad bcas legs par stsal
NK009(ta)002:673: te 'di la 'grel bshad cig kyang nges par gyis
NK009(ta)002:674: zhes bka'i gnang ba khyad par can nos pa lags
NK009(ta)002:675: su bzung nas / thob pa bzhin / so //
NK009(ta)002:676: gnyis pa mtshan nyid rnam pa gsum gyis don gyi
NK009(ta)002:684: bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:686: bri ba gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK009(ta)002:687: dang po chos nyid spyi'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK009(ta)002:688: chos kyi sku'i dkyil 'khor yum chen mo la sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:689: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i dkyil 'khor rnam par snang mdzad
NK009(ta)002:690: la 'khor sa bcu'i byang sems kyis bskor ba dang
NK009(ta)002:691: / sprul pa'i sku'i dkyil 'khor sh+aakya thub pa la 'khor rigs drug gis bskor ba dang gsum mo //
NK009(ta)002:692: gnyis pa chos can rang gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK009(ta)002:693: chos dbyings stong pa nyid la dkyil dang /
NK009(ta)002:694: rig pa ye shes la 'khor zhes brjod pa'i dbyings su zung 'jug rig pa'i phur bu bsgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:695: gsum pa bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK009(ta)002:696: rang gi rig pa lhar gsal ba dkyil dang /
NK009(ta)002:697: khro bo khro mor snang ba'i ni 'khor yin la /
NK009(ta)002:698: der thugs rje sprul pa'i phur pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:699: bzhi pa sbas pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK009(ta)002:700: yab yum gyi rdo rje pad+ma dkyil /
NK009(ta)002:702: der byang chub sems kyi phur pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:703: lnga pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:705: rigs bye brag pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK009(ta)002:712: dang po bsnyen pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:717: gru gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig pa //
NK009(ta)002:718: drag po gsad pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK009(ta)002:722: rtsibs brgyad zla gam lta bu ni //
NK009(ta)002:723: dbang gi dkyil 'khor yin par bshad //
NK009(ta)002:729: gnyis pa rigs bye brag pa'i dkyil 'khor la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:730: khro bo bcu la dkyil 'khor bcu /
NK009(ta)002:731: mgo brnyan nyi shu la dkyil 'khor nyi shu /
NK009(ta)002:732: phur srung bcu gnyis la dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:733: de bzhin du sing ha brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:735: dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad rnams la lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor gsang rgyud las gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:736: spyir ni dkyil 'khor thams cad gtso bo 'phos pa las 'gyur ba yin te /
NK009(ta)002:737: rigs bsdus kyi dkyil 'khor la lha lnga bcu rtsa
NK009(ta)002:738: gcig yod pas dkyil 'khor lnga bcu nga gcig la
NK009(ta)002:739: lha nyis stong phyed dang drug brgya nga gcig yod
NK009(ta)002:740: pa gtso bo 'phros pas dkyil 'khor gyi grangs kyang
NK009(ta)002:746: grub chen brgyad la sogs pa'i gang la bya ba'i
NK009(ta)002:747: las kyi grangs dang mtshungs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbye
NK009(ta)002:751: las rgyal mchog bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod do //
NK009(ta)002:752: gnyis pa sngags kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:754: rnam dbye bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK009(ta)002:762: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs gnyis su
NK009(ta)002:763: med pa'i ye shes rnam pa yig 'bru'i tshul du
NK009(ta)002:764: shar ba'am gnas pa yi ge nus pa mthu can
NK009(ta)002:765: du gyur pa ni sngags kyi ngo bo'o //
NK009(ta)002:767: byin rlabs mngon du myur bar 'byin pas na sngags so //
NK009(ta)002:772: rim pa bzhin lha pho'i sngags dang /
NK009(ta)002:774: spel ma'i sngags la bshad kyang /
NK009(ta)002:775: 'dir ni rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags /
NK009(ta)002:777: bzlas pa las kyi sngags gsum la ngos gzung ngo zhes gsungs /
NK009(ta)002:779: sngags dag pa'i don du btu ba /
NK009(ta)002:780: btus pa'i sngags kyi rnam dbye /
NK009(ta)002:781: nus pa mthar dbyung ba'i phyir bzla thabs so //
NK009(ta)002:782: de'ang sngags btu ba'i gzhi +aa li k+aa li /
NK009(ta)002:783: btu thabs k+aa li las lus btu /
NK009(ta)002:784: +aa li las yan lag btu ba /
NK009(ta)002:791: gnyis pa rnams par dbye ba la bdun te /
NK009(ta)002:799: gsum pa bzla thabs ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:800: rjes su dran pas bzla ba /
NK009(ta)002:802: rang dbang med par dkrugs te bzla ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:804: bzlog nas bzlas te bsad pa /
NK009(ta)002:805: so sor bzlas pa glod ma /
NK009(ta)002:806: bsdoms nas bzlas pa dril ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:807: bzlas pa'i skabs kyang sngon du dril la bzla /
NK009(ta)002:808: de nas rtags gang nye ba re la rkang thon du byed pa yin te /
NK009(ta)002:811: rtags dang sbyar bas shugs la song ba yin no //
NK009(ta)002:813: sdong po lta bu'i sngags kyi sbyor ba /
NK009(ta)002:820: chu bo lta bu'i sngags kyi sbyor bas bzla ba ste bzla thabs brgyad du'ang rgyud las bshad cing /
NK009(ta)002:822: rgyab ri dmag mi lta bu'i yig 'bru drug /
NK009(ta)002:826: brdung zhing rdeg pa'i yig 'bru drug /
NK009(ta)002:827: bzlog cing gshed dbab yig 'bru drug /
NK009(ta)002:829: ces d+h+aa ti ltar bsgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:831: yig 'bru drug po srung ba yin //
NK009(ta)002:832: yig 'bru dgu po mnan pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:834: bsad pa'i drag sngags 'bru lnga pa //
NK009(ta)002:835: gtub pa'i yig 'bru bcu gcig pa //
NK009(ta)002:836: rlag par byed pa bcu gnyis pa //
NK009(ta)002:837: zhes 'dus pa lta bur bsgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:838: spu gri'i 'khor los bsad pa ltar lus srog thal bar bsad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:839: sngags rkang brgyad kyi bar du bsad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:840: sngags rkang drug gis bsad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:841: sngags rkang gsum gyis bsad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:842: dregs pa rang gis rang bsad pa ste bsdu yig ltar bsgrubs par bshad de /
NK009(ta)002:843: 'di dag gi don zhib par rgyud dang /
NK009(ta)002:845: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i man ngag gi zhal lung las rtogs par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:847: gsum pa rdzas kyi mtshan nyid la bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:848: dang po rig pa ye shes kyi phur pa'i rdzas ni /
NK009(ta)002:849: nor bu chu dwangs lta bu rig pa chos nyid
NK009(ta)002:850: kyi gnas lugs dang glo bur dri ma'i rtog pa
NK009(ta)002:851: gnyis so sor 'byed par byed pa /
NK009(ta)002:852: gnyis pa thugs rje sprul pa'i phur pa'i rdzas ni /
NK009(ta)002:853: me long g.ya' dag pa la yi dam gyi sku'i
NK009(ta)002:854: snang ba 'char ba des rkyen byas nas 'ja' tshon
NK009(ta)002:855: lta bu'i nyams skyes te snang stong dbyer med du
NK009(ta)002:856: rtogs pa'o // gsum pa gsang ba byang chub sems kyi phur pa'i rdzas ni /
NK009(ta)002:857: phyag rgya mtshan ldan dgug pa'i rdzas /
NK009(ta)002:860: mi mthong bar sba ba'i rdzas so //
NK009(ta)002:861: bzhi pa 'dus byas rdzas kyi phur pa'i rdzas la lnga ste /
NK009(ta)002:862: bsnyen pa'i rdzas 'tsho ba'i zas la sogs pa /
NK009(ta)002:866: sgrub pa chen po'i rdzas nya bo /
NK009(ta)002:869: dgra bgegs bsad pa'i rdzas gab pa'i sngags drug dang /
NK009(ta)002:870: mnan sreg 'phang ba'i rdzas gsag pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:874: bkra shis pa'i rdzas bum pa bca' zhing sba ba sogs te /
NK009(ta)002:875: 'di dag kyang zhib par rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal
NK009(ta)002:876: lung man ngag gi lag len nyid las rtogs par
NK009(ta)002:877: bya dgos kyi / 'dir rgyas par ma spros so //
NK009(ta)002:878: gsum pa phur bu'i rgyu bzhis gang zag rnam bzhi mthar dbyung ba la /
NK009(ta)002:879: phur bu ngan sngags gtsug lag gi rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:880: phur pa rnam bzhi'i dgongs pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:881: gang zag rnam bzhi mthar dbyung ngo //
NK009(ta)002:882: rig pa ye shes phur bu ni //
NK009(ta)002:883: chos kyi dbyings kyi klong du gdab //
NK009(ta)002:884: thugs rje sprul pa'i phur bu ni /
NK009(ta)002:885: khams gsum sems can la gdab bo //
NK009(ta)002:886: gsang ba byang sems phur bu ni //
NK009(ta)002:887: yum gyi mkha' klong yangs par gdab //
NK009(ta)002:888: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:889: dgra dang bgegs la gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:891: gdab bya'i yul bzhi la 'debs byed kyi phur pa
NK009(ta)002:892: bzhi tshad dang ldan par btab nas thebs pa'i don
NK009(ta)002:893: 'bras bzhi mthar phyin pa'i lam nas dpal chen badz+ra
NK009(ta)002:894: ku m+aa ra'i dbyings dang ye shes mngon du gyur
NK009(ta)002:895: pa ni 'dir bshad bya bla na med pa'i srog
NK009(ta)002:899: rig 'dzin brgyud pa mkhas grub rnams kyi dgongs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:900: snying po mdo tsam bsdus te bshad pa la bzhi
NK009(ta)002:901: / nam mkha' lta bu'i gang zag gis rig pa
NK009(ta)002:902: ye shes kyi phur pa yul chos kyi dbyings su
NK009(ta)002:903: / gdab pa dang / ri bo lta bu'i gang
NK009(ta)002:904: zag gis thugs rje sprul pa'i phur pa'ang tshad med
NK009(ta)002:905: snying rje'i phur pa yul khams gsum gyi sems can
NK009(ta)002:907: bya ka lan+ta ka lta bu'i gang zag gis gsang
NK009(ta)002:908: ba byang chub sems kyi phur pa yum gyi mkha'
NK009(ta)002:910: tsan+dana lta bu'i gang zag gis mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa dgra bgegs gnyis la gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:911: de re re la'ang rten gyi gang zag /
NK009(ta)002:912: phur pa rang gi ngo bo /
NK009(ta)002:920: nyams su blang thabs dang don bcu bcu'i sgo nas
NK009(ta)002:921: rgyas par 'chad pa'i tshul ni gzhung gzhan du gsal
NK009(ta)002:923: 'dir don gyi mdo 'gag dril te cung zad bstan na /
NK009(ta)002:924: phur pa'i mtshan nyid rnam pa bzhis don gyi shan dbye ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:925: phur pa sgrub pa'i gang zag de'i snod kyi rim
NK009(ta)002:926: pa dang sbyar nas mthar dbyung tshul te gnyis las
NK009(ta)002:928: chos dbyings spros pa med pa dang rig pa rang
NK009(ta)002:929: gsal gyi ye shes gnyis su med pa rang byung
NK009(ta)002:930: gi ye shes chen po rang shar phyogs ris med
NK009(ta)002:931: pa ni rig pa ye shes kyi phur pa'i ngo
NK009(ta)002:932: bo ste / des chos thams cad la rgyas btab
NK009(ta)002:933: pas 'khrul snang thal 'byin du phug ste gnyis med
NK009(ta)002:934: ye shes chen po chos kyi sku thob pa yin
NK009(ta)002:935: bo ste / no // byang chub sems kyi phur pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:936: yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i stobs kyis zhu bde
NK009(ta)002:937: drangs ba'i bde ba chen po lhan skyes kyi ye
NK009(ta)002:938: shes ni de'i ngo bo yin la /
NK009(ta)002:939: des rtsa rlung thig le'i grong khyer la rgyas btab
NK009(ta)002:940: pas ma dag pa'i rlung sems dbyings su nub nas
NK009(ta)002:941: dag pa'i ye shes mngon du 'char bar byed cing
NK009(ta)002:942: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug longs
NK009(ta)002:944: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:945: snying rje chen pos sems can yongs su mi gtong ba yin la /
NK009(ta)002:946: des yul rigs drug gi sems can rnams la btab
NK009(ta)002:947: pas thugs rje'i dpyang thag gis zin nas 'khor ba'i
NK009(ta)002:948: gnas las sgrol zhing sprul pa'i sku 'thob par byed
NK009(ta)002:949: do // 'dus byas rdzas kyi phur pa la /
NK009(ta)002:950: mtshan ma rtags kyi phyag rgya rten dang bcas pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:951: 'di'i khongs su bskyed rim kyang 'du ba yin la /
NK009(ta)002:952: zhib par rtsa dum dngos 'chad pa'i skabs su 'ong bas 'dir mdo tsam bshad na /
NK009(ta)002:955: sras mchog gi phur pa dang gsum du yod cing /
NK009(ta)002:956: dang po la rang bzhin gyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:957: ting nge 'dzin gyi phur pa gnyis su dbyer yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:958: las bzhi'i phur pa ni phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i phur bu tshad ldan 'du bya ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:959: sras mchog gi phur pa bzhi'am bsdu na tshad dang
NK009(ta)002:960: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pas gdab pa'i
NK009(ta)002:962: 'di dag kyang 'og tu rim par 'byung ngo //
NK009(ta)002:963: gnyis pa gang zag snod kyi rim par sbyar nas nyams len mthar dbyung ba la /
NK009(ta)002:964: rig pa ye shes kyi phur pa ni nam mkha'
NK009(ta)002:965: lta bu'i gang zag gis mthar dbyung bar byed do
NK009(ta)002:967: blo yangs shing shes rab che la dbang po rno
NK009(ta)002:968: ba'i gang zag gang zhig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs dang
NK009(ta)002:969: ldan pa de la rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur
NK009(ta)002:970: te rang rig ye shes kyi phur pa'i ngo bo
NK009(ta)002:971: bstan pas lhang gis rtogs na phur pa thebs te
NK009(ta)002:973: byang chub sems kyi phur pas bya ka lan+ta ka lta bu'i gang zag mthar dbyung ste /
NK009(ta)002:974: 'dod chags che zhing brtson 'grus dang ldan pa'i gang
NK009(ta)002:975: zag bya ka lan+ta ka lta bu la yum bkra
NK009(ta)002:976: shis mtshan dang ldan pa gtad la gsang ba dang
NK009(ta)002:977: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur te lhag pa'i
NK009(ta)002:978: byang chub sems kyi phur pa gnyis su med pa'i
NK009(ta)002:979: bde chen gyi don bstan pas lhang gis rtogs na
NK009(ta)002:980: phur pa thebs te mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK009(ta)002:981: tshad med snying rje'i phur pas ri bo lta bu'i gang zag mthar dbyung ste /
NK009(ta)002:982: gang zag dad pa dang snying rje brtan pos gzhan
NK009(ta)002:983: don dang spros pa la dga' ba de la rang
NK009(ta)002:984: gzhan gyi don du tshad med bzhis blo sbyangs te
NK009(ta)002:985: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed du
NK009(ta)002:986: bcug la sngags kyi dbang bskur nas /
NK009(ta)002:987: tshad med bzhi'i dam bca' gzung zhing las kyi man
NK009(ta)002:988: ngag bstan pas lhang gis rtogs pa dang phur pa
NK009(ta)002:989: thebs nas mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK009(ta)002:990: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa dang brten nas tsan+dana lta bu'i gang zag mthar dbyung ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:991: gang zag gang zhig zhe sdang bas gdug pa dang
NK009(ta)002:992: gnag pa che la bstan pa srung bar blo phyogs
NK009(ta)002:993: pa de la dbang bskur nas rdo rje phur pa'i
NK009(ta)002:994: bsnyen sgrub las sbyor dang bcas pa'i sngags bstan pas
NK009(ta)002:995: snang srid phur bu'i dkyil 'khor du lhang gis rtogs
NK009(ta)002:996: nas phur pa thebs te mthar phyin par byed do
NK009(ta)002:997: // 'di rnams la gang zag gis phur pa'i don de mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:998: phur pa des gang zag de mthar dbyung ba gnyis don la 'dra zhing /
NK009(ta)002:999: sbyar lugs ji ltar byas kyang rung bar bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:1002: rig pa ye shes phur pa de //
NK009(ta)002:1003: gzung 'dzin med pa ngang du gdab //
NK009(ta)002:1004: lhang gis rtogs na thebs pa'i tshad //
NK009(ta)002:1007: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa de //
NK009(ta)002:1008: 'gro ba byams dang snying rjes gdab //
NK009(ta)002:1009: bdag gzhan gnyis med rtogs na thebs //
NK009(ta)002:1011: ma thebs ru dra srin por gol //
NK009(ta)002:1012: lhag pa byang sems phur pa de //
NK009(ta)002:1013: yum gyi mkha' klong yangs par gdab //
NK009(ta)002:1014: bde ba dngos med thebs pa'i tshad //
NK009(ta)002:1017: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa de //
NK009(ta)002:1018: zhi rgyas dbang drag phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:1020: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa la'ang /
NK009(ta)002:1026: las 'bras kyi sgo nas zhib par bshad kyang rgyud 'grel man ngag gzhan du gsal la /
NK009(ta)002:1028: gzhan yang 'di las 'phros pa'i rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:1030: bkod pa rdzas kyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:1031: phrin las mi zad pa'i phur pa nang gses dang
NK009(ta)002:1032: bcas pa bshad pas zhib par 'grel chen 'bum nag
NK009(ta)002:1033: sogs su blta'o // gong du bstan pa'i phur pa
NK009(ta)002:1034: bzhi po'ang sgrub rdzas bzhis so so'i gzhung tshugs dgos
NK009(ta)002:1035: sogs su blta'o // pa yin pas / rig pa
NK009(ta)002:1036: ye shes kyi phur pa lha phur dang shel lam
NK009(ta)002:1037: me long la rten bya ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1038: byang sems kyi phur pa thod pa dang rdo rje pad+ma'i 'du 'phrod la brten pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1039: snying rje'i phur pa las phur dang lha sngags ting 'dzin dang yul sems can la brten pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1040: rdzas kyi phur pa ni bsnyen dus phur pa dang nyungs kar /
NK009(ta)002:1041: sgrub pa'i dus 'khor lo dang ling+ga /
NK009(ta)002:1042: las rdzogs pa'i dus mnan sreg 'phang gsum la brten
NK009(ta)002:1043: te sgrub pa'i tshul bshad pa rnams kyang 'og tu
NK009(ta)002:1044: sgrub lugs chen po gsum gyis rgyud dngos 'chad pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1045: skabs su dngos shugs kyi tshul du bstan par shes
NK009(ta)002:1046: par bya'o // de rnams kyis rgyud kyi spyi don khog dbub kyi rim pa legs par grub //
NK009(ta)002:1047: da ni rgyud dngos 'chad pa la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:1058: badz+ra k+ai la ya m+au la tan+t+ra khan+da /
NK009(ta)002:1060: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu /
NK009(ta)002:1063: yul rgya che zhing chas gos dkar nag la gtsor
NK009(ta)002:1064: bton pa'i dbang gis rgya dkar nag gnyis su grags
NK009(ta)002:1065: pa las rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dngos su byon pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1066: yul rgya gar du phyogs bzhi'i yul gru rnams su
NK009(ta)002:1067: skad rigs mi gcig pa shin tu mang yang /
NK009(ta)002:1068: gtso bor skad rigs chen po bzhir grags pa las
NK009(ta)002:1069: sangs rgyas kyi gsung rab rnams samskri ta ste legs
NK009(ta)002:1070: par sbyar ba lha'i skad du gnas pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1072: cis kyang mi shigs pa'i don yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1073: 'dus byas rdzas kyi rdo rje la mi shigs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1074: chos bdun yod pa bzhin du dbyings spros bral stong
NK009(ta)002:1075: pa nyid la gzung 'dzin 'akhrusala snang gi chos gang
NK009(ta)002:1076: gis kyang mi shigs pa dang mi phyed pa la
NK009(ta)002:1077: sogs pa'i chos dang ldan pa'i don to //
NK009(ta)002:1078: k+ai la ya'i sgra ni 'debs par byed pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:1082: btab pa'i 'bras bu rnams thal 'byin gyi dgongs pa bzhin bstan pa'i don ltar ro //
NK009(ta)002:1083: yang na rdo rje phur pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:1084: rdo rje gnyis su med pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:1085: mi 'gyur chos kyi sku ru bshad //
NK009(ta)002:1086: phur pa ye shes gnyis med don //
NK009(ta)002:1087: dbyings dang ye shes 'brel bar bshad //
NK009(ta)002:1089: rdo rje ni gnyis su mi phyed cing 'gyur ba
NK009(ta)002:1090: mi mnga' bas spros pa dang bral bas dbyings chos
NK009(ta)002:1091: kyi sku dang / phur pa ni dbyings las gnyis
NK009(ta)002:1092: su med kyang gsal snang ye shes kyi rol rtsal
NK009(ta)002:1093: gang 'dul der snang cir yang 'char ba gzugs kyi
NK009(ta)002:1094: sku gnyis kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad par bstan pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1095: tshul las brtsams te spros na'ang chog go //
NK009(ta)002:1097: don gyi rgyud dpal chen po nas tshig don bar ma chad par byung ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1098: da lta lam nyams su blangs pas 'bras bu dpal
NK009(ta)002:1099: he ru ka'i go 'phang la sbyor bas gzhi lam
NK009(ta)002:1101: tshig gi rgyud kyang pi wang gi rgyud thag ltar
NK009(ta)002:1102: gcig nas gcig tu bar ma chad pa'i don de
NK009(ta)002:1103: / rgyud kyi rnam grangs ni gong du smos pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1104: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa phur pa gsang rgyud
NK009(ta)002:1105: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa phur pa myang 'das
NK009(ta)002:1106: kyi rgyud / gab pa'i sngags drug gtso bor ston pa 'khor lo nag po'i rgyud /
NK009(ta)002:1107: las sbyor gtso bor ston pa phur pa ngan sngags
NK009(ta)002:1108: gtsug lag gi rgyud rnams kyis thog drangs rgyud sde
NK009(ta)002:1109: mang po da lta'i bar du byung ba yin no
NK009(ta)002:1110: // m+au la khan+da ni rtsa ba'i dum bu'i don te /
NK009(ta)002:1111: rtsa rgyud de dag las gtso bor mtshan ma rdzas
NK009(ta)002:1112: kyi phur bu'i phrin las kyi dum bu khol du
NK009(ta)002:1114: phur bu gzhan gsum gyi don yang rdo rje'i tshig gi shugs las bstan pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:1116: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK009(ta)002:1117: zhes pa ni sgyur byed mkhan pos bzhed don 'grub
NK009(ta)002:1118: pa'i slad du lhag pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal ba
NK009(ta)002:1119: ste / de'ang rang sems gzhi'i rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)002:1120: bgrod pa lam gyi rdo rje gzhon nu //
NK009(ta)002:1121: rtogs pa 'bras bu'i rdo rje gzhon nu ste gzhi
NK009(ta)002:1122: lam 'bras gsum la khyab pa'i bcom ldan 'das rdo
NK009(ta)002:1123: rje gzhon nu zhes snang stong /
NK009(ta)002:1125: rig stong gi ngo bo gzhi dbyings stong pa'i ngang
NK009(ta)002:1126: las rig pa zung 'jug gi rdo rje mthar 'bras
NK009(ta)002:1127: lhun grub kyi sku gang zhig rdo rje'i sgras bstan
NK009(ta)002:1128: cing / de nyid skye 'gag gnas gsum sogs 'dus
NK009(ta)002:1129: byas kun rdzob kyi mtshan ma'i rtog pa thams cad
NK009(ta)002:1130: las grol ba'i phyir skye 'chi'i spros pas ma gos
NK009(ta)002:1131: par srid pa ji srid bar 'gro ba'i don du
NK009(ta)002:1132: nye bar bzhengs pas gzhon nu ste /
NK009(ta)002:1133: de nyid bcom ldan 'das kyang yin la rdo rje gzhon nu'ang yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:1134: de lta bu'i dpal chen po lhag pa'i lha la
NK009(ta)002:1135: rgyud kyi dum bu 'di sgyur ba'i thog mar phyag
NK009(ta)002:1137: gnyis pa gzhung dngos bshad pa la dum bu gnyis te /
NK009(ta)002:1138: stod las byang chub sgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1139: smad las dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i rim pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1141: rdo rje khro bos zhe sdang gcod //
NK009(ta)002:1143: phur pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)002:1146: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:1152: rgyud kyi thems sbyor bcu las bzhi pa /
NK009(ta)002:1155: bdun pa rnams kyis bstan pa'i don phrin las dang
NK009(ta)002:1156: sbyar na rgyud kyi khog dbub chen mo'i sa bcad
NK009(ta)002:1157: gsum pa rgyud kyi khog don nam chings drug dang
NK009(ta)002:1158: sbyar dgos kyang / rgyud kyi dum bu 'di la
NK009(ta)002:1159: phal cher shugs bstan tsam las dngos kyi tshig ris
NK009(ta)002:1160: sbyar dgos kyang / ma byung bas / 'dir med
NK009(ta)002:1161: du mi rung ba'i sa bcad mdor bsdus na bzhi
NK009(ta)002:1162: sbyar dgos kyang / ma byung bas / ste /
NK009(ta)002:1163: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa las kyi gzhi
NK009(ta)002:1164: sbyar dgos kyang / ma byung bas / ste /
NK009(ta)002:1165: gzung / dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum sngon du 'gro
NK009(ta)002:1166: ba dang bcas te don gyi khog dbub /
NK009(ta)002:1167: khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur te srog gi ye shes sems dpas srog la dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)002:1168: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing mchod cing bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud blang ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1169: dang po phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi gzung ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:1170: k+ai la ya me lce gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:1171: gnas dang bdag nyid 'khor rdzas dus //
NK009(ta)002:1172: phun sum tshogs pa sngar ldan na //
NK009(ta)002:1180: dang po sgrub pa po bdag nyid kyang /
NK009(ta)002:1181: rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1182: blo sbyangs rgyud goms ting 'dzin gsal //
NK009(ta)002:1183: theg dgu sde snod don la mkhas //
NK009(ta)002:1184: dad ldan thugs brtse bag tsha med //
NK009(ta)002:1185: rig 'dzin bla mar de bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:1186: zhes pa ltar rab yon tan brgyad ldan /
NK009(ta)002:1188: tha ma sum cha tshang ba dgos shing /
NK009(ta)002:1189: yang na yon tan gnyis te /
NK009(ta)002:1190: rab rgyud sde dang sde snod mtha' dag shes pa /
NK009(ta)002:1191: 'bring tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad shes pa /
NK009(ta)002:1192: tha ma rang rang gi skor legs par shes pa ste sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1197: sgrub pa la mos pa ste rang bzhin gyi yon tan dang ldan pa dang gnyis sam /
NK009(ta)002:1199: phur pa myang 'das kyi rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:1200: phun sum tshogs pa'i slob dpon gyis /
NK009(ta)002:1201: byams dang snying rje sngon btang la //
NK009(ta)002:1202: srid pa'i phur bu bsgrub par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:1203: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ni sgrub byed bdag nyid phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1206: grub pa thob pa bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK009(ta)002:1207: gzhung dang mthun pa sgrub thag nye ba'i gnas dang /
NK009(ta)002:1208: yid dang mthun pa nyams dga' ba'i gnas rnams te /
NK009(ta)002:1210: gnas kyi dam pa bstan pa la //
NK009(ta)002:1211: gzhung ldan bkra shis byin can dang //
NK009(ta)002:1212: nyams dga' ba yi gnas dang bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:1213: zhes pas bstan pa'i gnas la spyi dang bye brag
NK009(ta)002:1214: gi mtshan nyid gzhung 'grel man ngag gi yi ge
NK009(ta)002:1216: mdor na shan pa'am sdig can gyi khyim /
NK009(ta)002:1217: skye bo tha mal pa'i khyim /
NK009(ta)002:1218: sgo khang ngam srang kha lta bu ma yin pa'i sangs rgyas kyis zhabs kyis bcags pa /
NK009(ta)002:1219: grub thob rig 'dzin rnams kyis byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK009(ta)002:1220: gzhung nas bshad pa'i spyi bye brag gi mtshan nyid
NK009(ta)002:1221: tshang ba yid dang mthun la nyams dga' ba'i gnas
NK009(ta)002:1222: gang yin pa der bsgrub na dngos grub rnams pa
NK009(ta)002:1223: gnyis myur du 'thob pa rten cing 'brel 'byung gi
NK009(ta)002:1224: khyad par las grub pa ni gnas phun sum tshogs
NK009(ta)002:1227: dad ldan dam che gus la brtson //
NK009(ta)002:1228: shes rab gsum la blo sbyangs shing //
NK009(ta)002:1229: rtsa ba'i sngags zlos gtsang dme chung //
NK009(ta)002:1231: zhes pa'i yon tan kun tshang ba rab /
NK009(ta)002:1233: sum cha tshang ba tha ma ste gang rung dang /
NK009(ta)002:1237: sgrub pa po la dad pa rnams spyir 'khor ram grogs kyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK009(ta)002:1238: bye brag phyi nang brda sbyor /
NK009(ta)002:1239: rdul phyags skyes bu sogs so so'i mtshan nyid dang
NK009(ta)002:1240: bcas te gsungs pa rnams ni 'khor phun tshogs so
NK009(ta)002:1243: ra ba bzhi la bsnyen pa'i dus //
NK009(ta)002:1244: 'bring po bzhi la sgrub pa'i dus //
NK009(ta)002:1245: tha chung bzhi la las sbyor bya //
NK009(ta)002:1247: zla stod thams cad ldog pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:1248: zla smad thams cad thebs pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:1251: ra ba bzhi la gdab las ldog /
NK009(ta)002:1252: 'bring po bzhi la zor thun ldog /
NK009(ta)002:1253: tha chung bzhi la las dag bya //
NK009(ta)002:1257: dpyid zla gsum la brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:1258: nyer gnyis bcu drug bcu bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)002:1259: shar dang de bzhin shar lhor blta'o //
NK009(ta)002:1260: dbyar zla gsum la brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:1261: brgyad dang bco lnga dus drug tu //
NK009(ta)002:1262: nub byang byang shar kha blta'o //
NK009(ta)002:1263: ston zla gsum la brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:1264: nyi shu bco brgyad gnyis gsum la //
NK009(ta)002:1265: byang shar byang dang nub tu blta'o //
NK009(ta)002:1266: dgun zla gsum pa brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:1267: bcu gsum bcu drug nyi shu dgu /
NK009(ta)002:1268: byang dang lho ru blta ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1270: skar ma smal po dang mgo /
NK009(ta)002:1272: nyi ma bdud nyi drag po la las sbyor gnad che zhing /
NK009(ta)002:1273: mdor na 'di'i bsnyen sgrub las sbyor dang bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:1274: nam dga' dga' dang ci thod thod ma yin par
NK009(ta)002:1277: gza' sogs gtsug lag gi gzhung dang /
NK009(ta)002:1278: 'di nyid kyi rgyud nas basngagasa pa'i mtshan nyid 'dzom
NK009(ta)002:1279: pa'i dus su bsgrub par bya ba ni dus phun
NK009(ta)002:1280: sum tshogs pa'o // lnga pa rdzas dang yo byad ni /
NK009(ta)002:1285: dgra bgegs gsad pa'i yo byad de /
NK009(ta)002:1287: bza' bca' btung ba'i tshogs so //
NK009(ta)002:1288: gnyis pa la phyi'i rkyen dgra zlog pa'i yo byad sgrub khang btsan po brtsig pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1289: go cha dang mtshon cha la sogs pa /
NK009(ta)002:1292: nang gi rkyen 'du ba'i nad rlung mkhris bad kan sel ba'i sman sogs dang /
NK009(ta)002:1293: nyon mongs pa'i rkyen so so'i gnyen po'i rim pa
NK009(ta)002:1294: rnams la blo des pa'i gdeng dang ldan par bya
NK009(ta)002:1295: ste spang gnyen g.yul sprad do //
NK009(ta)002:1296: gsum pa gong du bshad pa'i sgrub gnas bzang po dang /
NK009(ta)002:1297: man ngag gi lag len dang ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgrub rdzas /
NK009(ta)002:1300: zhing chen gyi bla re la sogs pa'i skong rdzas gzhung mthun rnams so //
NK009(ta)002:1302: srog la 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1303: srog la ling+ga bca' ba sogs smad las mngon spyod
NK009(ta)002:1304: kyi chas spyi dang bye brag pa rnams yin par
NK009(ta)002:1306: des ni rdzas dang yo byad phun sum tshogs pa
NK009(ta)002:1307: ste lngas sgrub pa las kyi gzhi gzung ba bstan
NK009(ta)002:1308: zin to // spyi don gnyis pa dkyil 'khor rnam
NK009(ta)002:1309: pa gsum sngon du 'gro ba dang bcas pas don
NK009(ta)002:1310: gyi khog dbub pa la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:1311: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1314: rtsa dum gyi gzhung 'di'i tshig ris la dngos su
NK009(ta)002:1315: ma bstan kyang shugs la 'gro dgos pa'i dbang gis
NK009(ta)002:1317: phrin las kyi rnam bshad gzhan gyi dgongs pa ltar sa bcad tsam bsdus te bshad pa la bdun /
NK009(ta)002:1324: rnam pa gsum gyis byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1326: yan lag brgyad pa'am bdun pa /
NK009(ta)002:1327: tshad med bzhi sogs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK009(ta)002:1328: stong nyid spros bral ye shes kyi tshogs gsag pa
NK009(ta)002:1329: sogs 'byung yang phrin las sgom don dang sbyar ba'i
NK009(ta)002:1330: man ngag gi rim pa las 'ongs pas gzhan du
NK009(ta)002:1331: gsal gyi / 'dir rgyud don ltar mdo tsam bkral ba'i skabs su rgyas par ma bshad la /
NK009(ta)002:1332: gong gi sngon 'gro'i rim pa rnams ni zhi khro'i
NK009(ta)002:1333: phrin las spyi'i sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa yin
NK009(ta)002:1334: pas spyir gsal la rgyas par 'byung zhing /
NK009(ta)002:1335: 'dir 'bum nag gi dngos bstan mtshams gcod sogs kha skong ste cung zad 'chad pa la /
NK009(ta)002:1336: 'bar ba mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor gyis mtshams gcad pa la mdo gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1338: yan lag so gsum mchis pa'i dang po re re la don gsum gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1340: gang zag gang gis gcod pa /
NK009(ta)002:1342: bcad pa'i don gyi ngo bo /
NK009(ta)002:1343: mtshams kyi gzhung chen po gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1344: de gang nas bshad pa'i khungs /
NK009(ta)002:1348: dbye ba'i ldog cha nas yan lag sum cu rtsa
NK009(ta)002:1349: gsum du 'gyur tshul zhib par 'grel chen nyid dang
NK009(ta)002:1350: gzhung gzhan du gsal bas 'dir rgyas par ma spros
NK009(ta)002:1353: nga ni ye nas ngang gis khro //
NK009(ta)002:1354: mtshams gcod khro bos nam mkha' gang //
NK009(ta)002:1355: bgegs 'dul khro bo'i rol mtshams las //
NK009(ta)002:1356: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK009(ta)002:1357: ces 'byung ba dang tshul mthun par sngags dang phyag
NK009(ta)002:1358: rgya ting nge 'dzan gyi srung mtshams brtan por bcas
NK009(ta)002:1359: pas gnas skabs kyi dgos pa phyi mtshams bcad pas
NK009(ta)002:1360: g.yeng ba zhi / nang mtshams bcad pas bar chad zhi /
NK009(ta)002:1361: gsang mtshams bcad pas sems chos skur gnas pa 'byung ba yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1362: mthar thug gi dgos pa chos sku /
NK009(ta)002:1363: longs sku sprul sku gsum 'thob par 'gyur par bshad pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:1364: gnyis pa brda sgo dbye ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:1365: nyon shes kyi sgrib tshogs dang bcas pa'i bdag dang /
NK009(ta)002:1366: dag pa ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i
NK009(ta)002:1367: bar du gcod byed gzung 'dzin gnyis snang gi 'khrul
NK009(ta)002:1368: rtog gnyis med mnyam pa'i klong du dag pa gcig
NK009(ta)002:1369: 'grig gi ngo bor rang ngo shes pa mtshon byed
NK009(ta)002:1370: barda'am rnam pa'i sgo dkyil 'khor gyi shar gyi sgo
NK009(ta)002:1372: gtso bo nas sgo ma'i bar du bkra gsal ler mthong bar mos pa tsam ste /
NK009(ta)002:1374: bdag dang dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK009(ta)002:1375: ye'am gdod nas gnyis su med pa la //
NK009(ta)002:1376: bdag cag ma rig 'khrul pas bsgribs pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:1377: log rtog mtshan ma'i rtog pa'i sprin gyis bsgribs //
NK009(ta)002:1378: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs zhal yang ma mthong bas //
NK009(ta)002:1379: bdag 'jug dkyil 'khor sgo 'di dbye ru gsol //
NK009(ta)002:1380: ma rig mun pa'i tshogs kyis bar chod pa //
NK009(ta)002:1381: thugs rje nyi zla'i 'od kyi bsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)002:1384: gdod nas gnyis med mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du
NK009(ta)002:1385: phung khams skye mched dang bcas pa lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK009(ta)002:1386: nyid du dag pa chen po'i rang bzhin du ma
NK009(ta)002:1387: bcos babs kyi gshis lugs zab mo'i ngang du gnas
NK009(ta)002:1388: pa de nyid thabs kyi sgo nas rang ngo rig
NK009(ta)002:1389: ste rang zhal mjal ba'i lta ba mngon du gyur
NK009(ta)002:1390: pa nyid mtshon byed rnam pa brda dang tha snyad
NK009(ta)002:1391: tsam du phyag gis 'dud pa'i sgra sbyar ba ste
NK009(ta)002:1393: chos sku bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK009(ta)002:1394: longs sku phyogs bcur khro rgyal da la dang //
NK009(ta)002:1395: sprul sku 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK009(ta)002:1396: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum 'bar ba'i lha tshogs la //
NK009(ta)002:1397: rjes su yi rangs ngo mtshar che ba yi //
NK009(ta)002:1398: phyag rgya brda dang gar gyi sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK009(ta)002:1399: zhes pa'i tshig gis gsungs pa'i don to //
NK009(ta)002:1400: dpal gyi rtags gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:1401: dkyil 'khor chen po'i las rim dang gtso bor 'brel ba'i don yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1402: dgos ched ni lha dang dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i rigs
NK009(ta)002:1403: cig tu nges nas snying nye zhing dngos grub myur
NK009(ta)002:1404: ba'i dgos ched sogs dang ldan pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:1405: mched lcam gral du 'khod pa'i 'og tu ye shes
NK009(ta)002:1406: lha'i rtags su sna rtse mkhur tshos gnyis mthong bar
NK009(ta)002:1407: rak+ta'i thig le / spyi gtsug mgrin par thal chen
NK009(ta)002:1408: gyi tshom bu dpral bar rtse gsum ris su yong
NK009(ta)002:1409: rak+ta'i thig le / ba dang / snying gar zhag
NK009(ta)002:1410: gi zo ris rgya gram dbyibs su bkod par bya
NK009(ta)002:1411: ba ste sgrub pa chen po'i gzhung gi las rim
NK009(ta)002:1412: rnams su yong ba ltar ro //
NK009(ta)002:1413: nyams chag sgrib tshogs bshags pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:1416: yan lag sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi tshul du bshad pas zhib par 'grel chen nyid du blta zhing /
NK009(ta)002:1419: bshags bya'i sdig ltung ji ltar bshags pa'i thabs /
NK009(ta)002:1421: ma bshags pa'i nyes dmigs te man ngag khrid rim
NK009(ta)002:1422: rnams nas rgyas par 'byung ba ltar 'dir yang sbyar
NK009(ta)002:1423: te / don du rtog sgrib kyi bag chags rang
NK009(ta)002:1424: sar ma dag par mchog gi dngos grub rgyud la
NK009(ta)002:1425: mi thob pa'i gegs su che ba'i gnyen por sdig
NK009(ta)002:1426: ltung rtog sgriib la gnong 'gyod drag pos yi dam
NK009(ta)002:1427: lha'i dkyil 'khor 'khor dang bcas pa'i spyan sngar mthol
NK009(ta)002:1428: bshags 'gyod tshangs sme sngags kyi gdung ba drag pos
NK009(ta)002:1429: rtsa sbur la me lce bzhin spang bya'i nyes ltung
NK009(ta)002:1430: gnyen po'i stobs kyis ram smin 'byin pa'i nus bral
NK009(ta)002:1431: du byed pa ni 'di'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:1433: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma dpa' bo mkha' 'gro bcas pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1434: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dus gsum gyi bud+d+ha dang bcas pa /
NK009(ta)002:1435: rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshogs 'bum phrag yangs pa'i ma
NK009(ta)002:1436: mo mkha' 'gro'i 'khor dang bcas pa mngon sum bzhin
NK009(ta)002:1437: mdun mkhar gtibs pa las yab yum bde bar rol
NK009(ta)002:1438: pa'i sku'i gnas nas byin rlabs kyi ngo bo byang
NK009(ta)002:1439: sems bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas sgo gsum gyi dri
NK009(ta)002:1440: ma dag ste sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK009(ta)002:1441: dpag par dka' ba'i ye shes mchog gi byin rlabs
NK009(ta)002:1442: zab mo'i dngos grub mngon du gyur pa la blos
NK009(ta)002:1443: gsal gdab cing / byin rlabs skul ba'i tshig gdangs snyan cing brjod pa'i rta la drangs pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1444: rol mo'i rigs lhun chags par bskul /
NK009(ta)002:1445: gsur chen gyi dud pa gtibs pa sogs 'bebs byed
NK009(ta)002:1446: kyi rten 'brel rnams kyang tshogs par bya ba ste
NK009(ta)002:1447: / rtsa gsum rgya mtsho'i rdo rjee gsum gyi ye
NK009(ta)002:1448: shes kyis tha mal du snang ba'i sgo gsum sgrub
NK009(ta)002:1449: rdzas dang bcas pa dag mnyam spros pa med pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1450: dgongs klong zab mor tha mal gyi 'dzin rtog sbyangs
NK009(ta)002:1451: te lcags la gser 'gyur gyi rtsis thebs pa bzhin
NK009(ta)002:1452: rtsa ba gsum gyi ye shes rol pa'i klong du
NK009(ta)002:1453: byin gyis rlob par byed pa ni 'di'i mtshan nyid
NK009(ta)002:1454: / do // byin rlabs rnam pa gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la mdo gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1456: yan lag sum cu rtsa bdun gyi sgo nas shes par bya dgos pas /
NK009(ta)002:1458: byin rlabs re re la don gsum gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1460: gang gis byin rlob rnam pa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1461: gang du bsham pa'i snod gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1462: gang bsham pa'i dngos po gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1463: gang gis sbyong ba'i sbyong byed gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1464: gang bca' ba'i phyag rgya gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1466: byin gyis brlab pa phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1467: sngags gsum pos dzapa kyi grangs su gtong ba dang brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:1468: dang po byin gyis rlob byed gsum ni /
NK009(ta)002:1469: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing ste gtso bo'i zhal gsum gyi go rim ltar bdud rtsi g.yas /
NK009(ta)002:1471: gtor ma dbus su dgod pa'i go rim kyang bstan la /
NK009(ta)002:1472: byin gyis rlob byed kyang zhal gsum mo //
NK009(ta)002:1475: pho thod mo thod ma ning thod //
NK009(ta)002:1476: ba ling rak+ta bdud rtsir sbyar //
NK009(ta)002:1477: zhes pas ma ning thod par bdud rtsi /
NK009(ta)002:1479: mo thod du rak+ta bsham par bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:1480: bsham pa'i dngos po gsum ni /
NK009(ta)002:1481: gtsang phud la a mri ta sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1482: 'bru sna la dpal zan rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK009(ta)002:1483: khrag sna la sha sna dang bcas pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1486: ram yam kham gis bsregs sbyangs bkrus //
NK009(ta)002:1487: zhes pas ram gyis nyes skyon bsreg /
NK009(ta)002:1489: yam gyis gtor ba'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1492: 'bru gsum yi ges byin gyis brlab //
NK009(ta)002:1493: ces pas gyis bdud rtsi brlab /
NK009(ta)002:1495: h'u gis gtor ma brlab par yang bshad de don 'dra'o //
NK009(ta)002:1497: bdud rtsi la dung phor 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya /
NK009(ta)002:1498: gtor ma la gzhong pa 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya /
NK009(ta)002:1499: rak+ta la pad+ma 'khyil pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK009(ta)002:1501: bdud rtsi'i lbu ba las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK009(ta)002:1502: gtor ma'i 'od zer las khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK009(ta)002:1503: rak+ta'i rlangs pa las rta mgrin bskyed pas bsrung la bya'ang byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1504: byin gyis brlab pa gsum la'ang bdud rtsi phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1505: ba ling phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1506: rak+ta phyi nang gsang gsum gyi tshul du byin gyis brlab pa rgyas pa'i phyogs dang /
NK009(ta)002:1507: bsdu na lus kyi phyag rgya /
NK009(ta)002:1508: ngag tu sngags so sor bzla ba /
NK009(ta)002:1509: yid kyis de dag so sor bsam pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:1510: 'di dag sgom rim dang sbyar ba'i man ngag phrin
NK009(ta)002:1511: las kyi rim par song bas 'dir rgyas par spro
NK009(ta)002:1512: ma dgos shing / so so'i mtshan don dang dag
NK009(ta)002:1513: pa sogs rgyud dang gzhung gi dgongs pa rig 'dzin
NK009(ta)002:1514: brgyud pa'i zhal lung gzhan na zab cing rgya che
NK009(ta)002:1515: ba'i tshul du bzhugs pa dag las shes so //
NK009(ta)002:1516: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum bshad pa la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1517: gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi 'phro 'du bstan pa /
NK009(ta)002:1518: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa /
NK009(ta)002:1520: dang po gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi 'phro 'du bshad pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:1521: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK009(ta)002:1522: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK009(ta)002:1525: rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1526: de bzhin nyid dang kun tu snang //
NK009(ta)002:1527: rgyu yi ting 'dzin bsgom byas la //
NK009(ta)002:1530: rdo rje khro bos zhe sdang gcod //
NK009(ta)002:1531: mtshon chen sngon po cher 'bar ba //
NK009(ta)002:1532: nam mkha'i dkyil du thig le shar //
NK009(ta)002:1533: zhes pas bstan pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi /
NK009(ta)002:1537: rdo rje khro bos zhes pas bstan /
NK009(ta)002:1538: de la de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ni /
NK009(ta)002:1539: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK009(ta)002:1540: thams cad ye gdod nas rang bzhin gyis ma grub
NK009(ta)002:1541: pa'i stong nyid spros bral bde ba chen po rnam
NK009(ta)002:1542: pa kun gyi mchog dang ldan pa de la bya
NK009(ta)002:1544: ye nas stong pa'i rang bzhin yin pa la yin
NK009(ta)002:1545: par shes pas sgrub pa po'i blos de kho na
NK009(ta)002:1546: nyid bzhin du rtogs par bya ba'i don yin pas
NK009(ta)002:1548: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK009(ta)002:1549: sems can la rang chas su yod pa'i sems nyid gzhi'i chos nyid /
NK009(ta)002:1550: las dang po pas bsgom pa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:1552: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa 'joms pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1557: spros med sogs kyis bstan pa dag go //
NK009(ta)002:1558: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin des ma zin pa'i skyon ni /
NK009(ta)002:1559: chos thams cad stong nyid du ma rtogs pas lha'i sku mdog phyag mtshan /
NK009(ta)002:1562: sgrol ba rnams rang rgyud par bsgoms pas 'dod khams kyi lha /
NK009(ta)002:1566: sems can dmyal ba rnams su skye bar gsungs so //
NK009(ta)002:1567: ting nge 'dzin de'i phan yon ni /
NK009(ta)002:1568: chan la phab kyis thebs pa bzhin du chos thams
NK009(ta)002:1569: cad stong pa nyid kyi rtsis zin na gdab las
NK009(ta)002:1570: dang / mnan sreg 'phang gsum sogs byas tshad ye
NK009(ta)002:1571: shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur bar bshad pa ste spyir
NK009(ta)002:1572: shes par bya ba'i gnad yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1573: 'bru gnyer pa'i sgo nas bkrol na /
NK009(ta)002:1574: rdo rje khro bos zhes pa'i rdo rje la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1575: skye med don gyi rdo rje /
NK009(ta)002:1576: pha lam rdzas kyi rdo rje /
NK009(ta)002:1577: mtshan ma rdzas kyi rdo rje dang gsum las /
NK009(ta)002:1578: 'di skye med don gyi rdo rje yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1579: khros pa la gang khro na /
NK009(ta)002:1580: skye med don gyi rdo rje spros bral stong pa nyid de khros /
NK009(ta)002:1582: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa gzung 'dzin bdag rtog gi grong khyer la khros /
NK009(ta)002:1584: zhe sdang rang rgyud pas mi gshis ngan dgra la
NK009(ta)002:1585: khros pa lta bu ma yin par nyi ma 'char
