NK009(ta)002:1586: ba'i gzi brjid kyis mun pa'i smag rum mdun na
NK009(ta)002:1588: stong nyid rtogs pa'i yul na dngos 'dzin mtshan ma'i
NK009(ta)002:1589: spros pa thams cad mi gnas pa'i tshul gyis khros
NK009(ta)002:1590: pa'o // de nyams su len pa'i tshul yang las dang po pas sgra spyi tsam dang /
NK009(ta)002:1591: las goms pas don spyi'i sgo nas dang /
NK009(ta)002:1592: las smin pas don rang gi mtshan nyid du nyams su len pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1593: 'di'i don thun mong pa rnams rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK009(ta)002:1594: theg pa'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel las bstan pa dang
NK009(ta)002:1595: / thun mong min pa sngags kyi theg pa gong
NK009(ta)002:1596: 'og gi rim pas bla med spyi dang khyad par
NK009(ta)002:1597: rnams su bstan pa ltar nges pa bya la /
NK009(ta)002:1598: 'dir ting 'dzin rnam gsum sogs 'di'i gnad rnams rig
NK009(ta)002:1599: 'dzin grub pa'i slob dpon rnam gsum gyi dgongs pa
NK009(ta)002:1600: dril ba'i tshul du mdo tsam smos par zad do
NK009(ta)002:1601: // gnyis pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK009(ta)002:1602: 'di la'ang spyir shes par bya ba ngo bo ni /
NK009(ta)002:1603: chos thams cad kyi nang nas snying rje sgyu ma tsam de nyid yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1605: snying rjes gong 'og gnyis mtshams sbyar bas kun tu snang bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)002:1607: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje chen po /
NK009(ta)002:1608: sems can gyi khams na yod pa'i snying rje ste
NK009(ta)002:1609: phyogs can ni khra spyang sogs la'ang yod pa de
NK009(ta)002:1610: dang / las dang po pas don spyi la blos bsgom pa'i snying rje'o //
NK009(ta)002:1617: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:1618: de nyid med pa'i skyon ni /
NK009(ta)002:1620: 'khor ba mar lhung ste rnam pa thams cad du mtshams mi sbyor ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1622: snying rjes gong 'og mtshams sbyar nas stong nyid snying
NK009(ta)002:1623: rje'i snying po can zhes sangs rgyas thob pa'i lam
NK009(ta)002:1624: phyin ci ma log par 'gyur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1626: zhe sdang gcod ces pa kun snang snying rjes zhe sdang gcod pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:1627: dper na tsha reg gang na yod pa na grang reg med /
NK009(ta)002:1628: grang reg gang na yod pa na tsha reg med pa de bzhin du /
NK009(ta)002:1629: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la zhe sdang skyes tshe snying rje med /
NK009(ta)002:1630: snying rje skyes tshe zhe sdang med pa lhan cig mi gnas 'gal ba yin cing /
NK009(ta)002:1631: nus pa dang 'tshams par sems can la dmigs pa /
NK009(ta)002:1633: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje gang rung tshad du
NK009(ta)002:1634: phyin pa'i gnyen pos so so'i mtshan 'dzin dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:1635: pa'i sdang shugs rang bzhin gyis nyams pa ni chos
NK009(ta)002:1636: nyid yin la / 'dir stong nyid rdo rje lta
NK009(ta)002:1637: bu mngon du gyur pa'i ye shes dmigs med kyi
NK009(ta)002:1638: snying rje sgyu ma lta bu dang zung du 'jug
NK009(ta)002:1639: pas gong gi stong nyid kyi ngang las snying rje
NK009(ta)002:1640: rang shugs su skye bas srid rtsa'i zhe sdang thams
NK009(ta)002:1641: cad nags la me mched pa bzhin bcad cing bsregs
NK009(ta)002:1642: te skye ba'i yul med pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:1643: 'di nyid kyang theg pa chen po'i sde snod rin
NK009(ta)002:1644: po che dag las mang du 'byung ba dang gnad
NK009(ta)002:1645: gcig go // gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK009(ta)002:1647: chos thams cad kyi nang nas h'u sngon po yig 'bru'i rnam pa can de nyid yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1649: de nyid rten gzhal yas khang /
NK009(ta)002:1650: brten pa lha dang bcas pa thams cad bskyed pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1651: rgyu'am gzhir gyur pas na rgyu'i ming gis smos shing
NK009(ta)002:1653: sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes lnga ldan gyi h'u
NK009(ta)002:1654: sems can gyi rgyud la yod pa'i snying ga'i rtsa
NK009(ta)002:1656: las dang po pas rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h'u blos bsgom pa rnams so //
NK009(ta)002:1658: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor skyed par byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1663: skyed byed kyi ting nge 'dzin sogs su smos pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1664: de nyid ma bsten pa'i skyon ni /
NK009(ta)002:1665: bskyed rim cho ga dang mi ldan zhing rdzogs par mi 'gyur la /
NK009(ta)002:1667: bskyed rim cho ga yan lag dang bcas te rdzogs par 'gyur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1669: mtshon chen sngon po cher 'bar ba //
NK009(ta)002:1670: nam mkha'i dkyil du thig le shar //
NK009(ta)002:1671: zhes pa 'di la'ang rig 'dzin grub pa'i slob dpon
NK009(ta)002:1672: rnam gsum gyi dgongs pa'i mthil mi 'dra ba med
NK009(ta)002:1673: cing / tshig gi zur phyung lugs cung zad tha dad pa re byung yang /
NK009(ta)002:1674: dgongs pa dril nas bshad na /
NK009(ta)002:1678: pho mo'i mtshan ma la'ang 'jug mod kyi /
NK009(ta)002:1679: 'dir rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha bcas 'dis mtshon pa'i don yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1680: chen po ni ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gyur pa /
NK009(ta)002:1681: sngon po ni h'u gi kha dog /
NK009(ta)002:1682: cher 'bar ba ni de las yig 'bru dang 'od
NK009(ta)002:1683: zer rab tu mang po'i 'phro 'du lhag par mnga'
NK009(ta)002:1684: ba yin la / don du sangs rgyas thams cad
NK009(ta)002:1685: kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes zab gsal
NK009(ta)002:1686: dang bde stong sogs dbyer med kun khyab mnyam pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1687: rang bzhin dngos po med la dngos po kun gyi
NK009(ta)002:1689: rnam pa yi ge h'u gi gzugs su snang ba
NK009(ta)002:1690: de nyid gzung 'dzin mtshan mar snang bas snod bcud
NK009(ta)002:1691: rang rgyud du blta ba'i gnyen por thugs rje'i rtsal
NK009(ta)002:1693: dper na mtshon cha rnon pos lcugs phran gyi yal
NK009(ta)002:1694: ga la thebs pa bzhin gcod par byed pa'i tshul
NK009(ta)002:1695: dang mthun par / snod bcud dngos por zhen pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1696: rtsa ba bcad cing dag mnyam lha'i 'khor lor sbyor
NK009(ta)002:1697: bar byed pa'i rgyu yin pa'i cha nas mtshon cha
NK009(ta)002:1698: rnon po'i tshul du 'chad kyang rung bar sems so
NK009(ta)002:1699: dang mthun par / // nam mkha' la snang ba nam mkha' /
NK009(ta)002:1702: chos nyid nam mkha' rnams su mchis pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1703: 'dir chos nyid kyi nam mkha'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1704: dkyil ni mtha' dang dbus med pa spros pa kun gyis mi phyed pa'i klong zab mo nas /
NK009(ta)002:1705: mtshan rtog gi grwa zur med pa'i mnyam yangs gdal ba chen po'i thig le'am /
NK009(ta)002:1706: snga 'gyur du thig pa zhes 'byung ba ltar na /
NK009(ta)002:1707: don 'dril ba'i phyir thigs pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1708: don thog tu pheb pa'i phyir thigs pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:1709: de'ang rgyu'i h'u yig de la ye shes lnga dang ldan pas 'dril ba /
NK009(ta)002:1710: h'u de rten dang brten par bcas pa'i thog tu pheb pas thigs pa zhes bya la /
NK009(ta)002:1711: don du stong nyid snying rje'i rang rtsal las zung
NK009(ta)002:1712: 'jug rgyu'i yi ge sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi
NK009(ta)002:1713: ngo bo de nyid spros bral nam mkha'i dkyil nas
NK009(ta)002:1714: don thog tu pheb pa'i thig le'am tigs par rang
NK009(ta)002:1715: shar ba'i tshul gyis snod bcud dag pa lha'i 'khor
NK009(ta)002:1716: lor sgyur bar byed pa'i rgyur gyur pa nyid du
NK009(ta)002:1717: go bar bya'o // gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:1718: srog gi sgo ru shar ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:1719: snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK009(ta)002:1721: 'di la gu ru pad+ma'i dgongs pa gtso bor bzung na /
NK009(ta)002:1722: srog ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin yi ge h'u gi rnam pa can de nyid yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1723: sgor shar ba la'ang 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1724: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba gnyis su yod pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1725: dang po 'byung ba rim brtsegs la phyi nang gsang gsum du dbye /
NK009(ta)002:1728: yan lag sum cu tham pa'i tshul du gnas pa la /
NK009(ta)002:1732: phyi 'byung ba la ji ltar sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1733: nang phung po dang gang ltar sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1734: gsang ba nyon mongs dang ji ltar sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1735: gsal ba lha dang gang ltar sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1736: bde ba ye shes dang ji ltar sbyar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1737: stong pa chos nyid dang gang ltar sbyar ba zhes pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1738: de'ang srog ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h'u de nyid
NK009(ta)002:1739: yin la de las sa bon gyi yi ge'i 'phro
NK009(ta)002:1740: 'du'i cho 'phrul las srog gi yi ge nus pa
NK009(ta)002:1741: mthu can du gyur pa ni sgo ru shar ba'o
NK009(ta)002:1742: // de las 'gag pa med pa'i cho rol sna
NK009(ta)002:1743: tshogs pa'i tshul du so so'i gzhir gyur pa'i yi
NK009(ta)002:1745: chos kyi 'byung gnas nam mkha'i rang bzhin 'byams klas
NK009(ta)002:1746: pa phyi ltar na 'byung ba nam mkha'i rnam pa
NK009(ta)002:1748: gsang ba stong pa nyid sogs su mtshon pa /
NK009(ta)002:1749: de bzhin du rlung gi dal rgya gram phyi 'byung ba rlung gi gor shar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1750: nang lus kyi skyed byed sogs kyi ngo bo dang /
NK009(ta)002:1751: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pa phyi 'byung ba chu /
NK009(ta)002:1754: keng rus kyi ri rab dpag tshad brgyad khri mtho ba 'byung ba sa'i sgor shar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1756: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang sogs kyi ngo bo //
NK009(ta)002:1757: me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum 'byung ba me'i sgor shar ba /
NK009(ta)002:1759: nyon mongs pa nga rgyal sogs kyi rang bzhin du
NK009(ta)002:1760: bshad pa ni 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang
NK009(ta)002:1761: bcas pa'i sgor shar ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1762: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba'i tshul ni /
NK009(ta)002:1763: yang rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul las sa
NK009(ta)002:1764: bon yi ge dang bcas pa'i spro bsdu'i rol pa
NK009(ta)002:1765: gang las shar ba'i ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang
NK009(ta)002:1768: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor gzhu dbyibs sngo //
NK009(ta)002:1769: ram las me yi dkyil 'khor gru gsum dmar //
NK009(ta)002:1770: bam las chu yi dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum //
NK009(ta)002:1771: sum las sa dkyil gru bzhi ser //
NK009(ta)002:1772: kem las keng rus ri rab 'bar //
NK009(ta)002:1773: de steng b+h+r+aum las grub pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:1774: mdzes pa'i gzhal yas thod pa'i mkhar //
NK009(ta)002:1775: mchog phran dral phyam nyi zla'i mig /
NK009(ta)002:1777: ces gsungs pa'i drag po'i gzhal yas khang tshad dang
NK009(ta)002:1778: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa ye shes
NK009(ta)002:1779: rang snang gi bkod pa snod kyi 'jig rten sogs
NK009(ta)002:1780: rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo rang byung lhun grub
NK009(ta)002:1781: kyi pho brang chen po'i dbus su pad+ma nyi ma
NK009(ta)002:1782: ru dra pho mo ste gtso bo'i gdan dang /
NK009(ta)002:1783: 'khor lo'i rtsibs bcur phyogs skyong bcu pho kha sbub /
NK009(ta)002:1784: mo gan rkyal byin pa 'khril ba'i tshul du gnas pas khro bo bcu'i gdan /
NK009(ta)002:1785: sgo bzhir dri za sogs bzhi bsgyel ba'i gdan /
NK009(ta)002:1786: lha snam la phur srung rnams kyi gdan dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:1787: pa rgyu'i yi ge kho na'i cho 'phrul las spros
NK009(ta)002:1788: pa'o // nang bskyed pa'i rim pa dkyil 'khor rang lus la tshang ba'i tshul /
NK009(ta)002:1790: rkang pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor te //
NK009(ta)002:1792: gsus pa chu yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK009(ta)002:1793: pho ba sa yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK009(ta)002:1794: brang ni keng rus ri rab ste //
NK009(ta)002:1795: mgo bo b+han+ha klad pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK009(ta)002:1796: rtsa gnas dbus na lha tshogs bzhugs //
NK009(ta)002:1798: gsang ba bskyed pa'i rim pa'ang rang gi sems la
NK009(ta)002:1799: lha dang dkyil 'khor thams cad gdod nas dbyer med
NK009(ta)002:1800: du tshang zhing / de dag gi tshul dang /
NK009(ta)002:1801: gzhal yas khang gi rnam gzhag dang dag pa sogs
NK009(ta)002:1802: rgyud dang 'grel pa sgom don gyi man ngag rnams
NK009(ta)002:1803: las zhib tu 'byung bas 'dir rgyas par ma spros
NK009(ta)002:1804: so // snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK009(ta)002:1805: zhes pa ni sngar bshad pa'i rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK009(ta)002:1806: h'u yig gi rgyun de nyid rang gi snying gar
NK009(ta)002:1807: bar ma chad pa'i tshul du gsal snang 'don pa'am
NK009(ta)002:1808: / bskyed pa'i rim pa'i skabs su ting nge 'dzin
NK009(ta)002:1809: sems dpar bsgom pa'i don du bshad kyang de nyid
NK009(ta)002:1810: man ngag gi rim pa dang sbyar ba yin la
NK009(ta)002:1812: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi spro gzhi de nyid yin
NK009(ta)002:1813: pas de dag gi dkyil lam snying por bsgom pa
NK009(ta)002:1814: ni rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs zab gsal gnyis su
NK009(ta)002:1815: med pa'i ye shes bde stong gi phyag rgyas brtan
NK009(ta)002:1816: g.yo snod bcud kyi dngos po la gdab nas dag
NK009(ta)002:1817: mnyam chen po'i klong du 'ub chub par bya ba'i
NK009(ta)002:1818: don la skabs 'dir 'chad kyang 'gal ba med do
NK009(ta)002:1819: // spyi don gsum pa brten pa lha bskyed pa bshad pa la /
NK009(ta)002:1820: rgyud khu byug rol pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1821: drag po las kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK009(ta)002:1822: rnam pa gsum du rgyal bas gsungs //
NK009(ta)002:1823: bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK009(ta)002:1824: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK009(ta)002:1825: sras mchog phur bu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK009(ta)002:1826: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK009(ta)002:1827: gtso gzungs zung du 'brel ba ni //
NK009(ta)002:1828: bdag nyid chen po yin par bshad //
NK009(ta)002:1829: khro bo khro mo phra men tshogs //
NK009(ta)002:1830: phyogs mtshams khro bo zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:1831: sras mchog phur bu'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK009(ta)002:1832: k+ai la ya zhes rab tu grags //
NK009(ta)002:1833: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos sku'i ngo bo bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:1834: longs sku'i ngo bo phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:1835: sprul sku'i ngo bo phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:1836: dang po chos sku'i ngo bo bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa la bskyed pa dngos dang /
NK009(ta)002:1839: 'dir tshig zin la dngos su med kyang 'grel pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1840: dgongs pa ltar mdo tsam bsnyad pa la spyir shes
NK009(ta)002:1844: spyir rdo rje gzhon nu zhes pa la dngos brtags ma phye bar bshad na /
NK009(ta)002:1845: rang sems gzhi'i rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)002:1846: bgrod pa lam gyi rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)002:1847: rtogs pa 'bras bu'i rdo rje gzhon nu dang gsum yod /
NK009(ta)002:1849: gdod nas skye ba med pa'i sems nyid spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba nyid la 'jog /
NK009(ta)002:1851: thabs shes gnyis kyi sgo nas sku gsum ye shes
NK009(ta)002:1852: lnga rnam pa rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs su
NK009(ta)002:1853: gsal bar lta ba'i nyams len nyid yin la /
NK009(ta)002:1855: sangs rgyas kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes spros pa med pa nyid de /
NK009(ta)002:1856: rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK009(ta)002:1857: rang sems gzhi yi rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)002:1858: sa bon kun khyab til mar 'dra //
NK009(ta)002:1859: rtogs na sangs rgyas ngo mtshar che //
NK009(ta)002:1860: bgrod pa lam gyi rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)002:1861: thabs shes sku gsum ye shes lnga //
NK009(ta)002:1862: chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bya //
NK009(ta)002:1863: rtogs pa 'bras bu'i rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)002:1864: sku lnga ye shes dgu ldan te //
NK009(ta)002:1866: gzhi lam 'bras bu rtogs gyur na //
NK009(ta)002:1867: chos sku spros bral mngon du 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:1868: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzhi lam 'bras gsum la khyab
NK009(ta)002:1869: pa'i rdo rje gzhon nu de nyid rnal 'byor pas
NK009(ta)002:1870: lam nyams su blang ba'i sgo nas mngon du bya
NK009(ta)002:1871: dgos pa ni spyir shes par bya ba yin la
NK009(ta)002:1872: / bye brag bskyed thabs dngos bshad pa la'ang mang du gsungs te /
NK009(ta)002:1876: bskyed pa'i rgyu sems dpa' bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:1877: bskyed pa'i sku'i cha lugs bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:1885: lam khyer bzhir gsungs pa'i don 'dir tshig nyung ngus don gyi gnad tshang bar bstan na /
NK009(ta)002:1887: rdo rje gzhon nu dbu stong phyag stong spyan bye ba mnga' ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1889: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1890: rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa sogs nas /
NK009(ta)002:1891: rdo rje gzhon nu dbu gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:1892: k+ai la ya tan+t+ra bcu gnyis pa nas /
NK009(ta)002:1893: rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa rnams su bshad cing /
NK009(ta)002:1894: de'ang khro bo'i rnam pa can yin yang khro bo
NK009(ta)002:1895: zhes pas bdud dang srin po khros pa lta bu
NK009(ta)002:1896: yin la / thugs rje chen pos gdul bya 'dul
NK009(ta)002:1897: ba'i thabs su bstan pa gang zag yang rab rnams
NK009(ta)002:1898: snying rjes lhar bsgom pa yin par gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:1900: las dang po pas rang gi sems nyid lhar bskyed pa la dgongs nas /
NK009(ta)002:1901: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:1903: las goms pa pos bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa la dgongs nas /
NK009(ta)002:1904: sku yi gter du bdag skyed cig /
NK009(ta)002:1905: ces gsungs shing las smin pa pos phung po lhar bskyed pa la dgongs nas /
NK009(ta)002:1906: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK009(ta)002:1908: las mthar phyin pa po yul thams cad lha'i rol par blta ba la dgongs nas /
NK009(ta)002:1909: 'khor ba rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)002:1911: de nyid kyis sbyang gzhi gang sbyong ba'ang bdag nyid
NK009(ta)002:1912: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo yab yum gyis
NK009(ta)002:1913: skye srid dang / de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin gyis 'chi srid /
NK009(ta)002:1914: rgyu ting gi h'u nam mkha' las babs te gtso
NK009(ta)002:1915: bo gdan la 'khod pas bar srid sbyong bar gsungs
NK009(ta)002:1916: la / gzhan yang bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis rdzus skyes /
NK009(ta)002:1917: phyogs bcu'i khro bos mngal skyes /
NK009(ta)002:1918: mgo brnyan nyi shus sgong skyes /
NK009(ta)002:1919: dam can gyis drod gsher skyes sbyong bar bshad pa
NK009(ta)002:1920: ni gtso bor man ngag gi nges pa shugs che'o
NK009(ta)002:1921: // de la bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la
NK009(ta)002:1922: chos kyi sku'i ngo bo yin pa'i rgyu mtshan spros
NK009(ta)002:1923: pa dang bral bas chos sku /
NK009(ta)002:1924: rang nyid bsgom pa'i bdag nyid /
NK009(ta)002:1925: 'khor gyi lha thams cad 'di las 'byung bas rtsa ba rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum ni dkyil /
NK009(ta)002:1929: go cha'i lha rnams ni 'khor yin pas de skad ces brjod cing /
NK009(ta)002:1930: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor la phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK009(ta)002:1931: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyang tshang bas
NK009(ta)002:1932: na bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi bdag nyid
NK009(ta)002:1933: rtsa ba'i dakyila'akhora ni ye shes sems dpa' nyid yin
NK009(ta)002:1934: la / bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs
NK009(ta)002:1935: bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni sku gsung thugs kyi
NK009(ta)002:1937: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phur pa rdzas
NK009(ta)002:1938: kyi dkyil 'khor ni phyag gi phur pa nyid yin
NK009(ta)002:1939: la / bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phur srung ni ba spu'i khro chung rnams so //
NK009(ta)002:1940: de lta bu'i rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK009(ta)002:1941: dpal chen po yab yum la brten pa'i rnam dag
NK009(ta)002:1942: kyang / dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa bstan pa'i phyir yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK009(ta)002:1943: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pas sku mdog mthing nag /
NK009(ta)002:1944: sku gsum dang rnam thar gsum gyi ngo bo dbu gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1945: phar phyin drug gi ngo bo phyag drug /
NK009(ta)002:1946: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i zhabs bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:1947: phyag na theg pa rim dgu mtshon pa'i rdo rje rtse dgu /
NK009(ta)002:1948: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK009(ta)002:1949: nyon mongs pa sreg pa'i ye shes kyi me dpung /
NK009(ta)002:1950: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod phyir kha t+w+aam rtse gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1951: gdug pa mtha' dag 'dul phyir ri rab phur bu 'dril ba /
NK009(ta)002:1952: gzhan yang gzhi lam 'bras bu'i yon tan mtha' dag mtshon pa'i phyir byug pa'i rtsi gsum /
NK009(ta)002:1954: gdags pa'i rgyan gsum ste dur khrod kyi chas dgu /
NK009(ta)002:1957: thugs kyi gar gsum ste gar gyi nyams dgu la
NK009(ta)002:1958: sogs pas khyad par du byas pa'i khams gsum srid
NK009(ta)002:1959: pa gsum na 'gran gyi zla med pa'i che btsan
NK009(ta)002:1960: dpa' bo khams gsum dbang du sdud cing /
NK009(ta)002:1961: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i khro mchog kun gyi rgyal po'i rnam par snang ba gang zhig /
NK009(ta)002:1963: chad pa ma yin rig cing gsal //
NK009(ta)002:1964: rtag pa ma yin ngos gzung med //
NK009(ta)002:1965: snang stong dbyer med gtan la dbab //
NK009(ta)002:1966: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:1968: bskyed pa'i rim pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i mtshan
NK009(ta)002:1969: gzhi snang stong ngam gsal stong gdod nas dbyer med
NK009(ta)002:1970: zung 'jug gi dgongs par 'bab pa zhig la bshad
NK009(ta)002:1971: do // de ltar bskyed rdzogs gnyis la ldog pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1972: ngo bo sbyar na yan lag brgyad cu ru 'gyur
NK009(ta)002:1973: do // bar gsungs so // gnyis pa gsal gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:1974: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)002:1975: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:1976: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK009(ta)002:1977: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:1979: 'di bskyed rdzogs kyi don gnad shin tu zab pa'i rdo rje'i tshig ste /
NK009(ta)002:1980: grub pa'i rig 'dzin rnam gsum gyi zhal snga nas
NK009(ta)002:1981: dgongs pa'i gnad len lugs cung zad re dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:1982: te gsungs pa'i gnad 'gag gi snying po tsam dril
NK009(ta)002:1983: te cung zad rgyas par bshad na gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:1984: rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1987: bskyed pa'i rim pa dang sbyar ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:1988: rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang sbyar ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:1990: snying rjes zhes pa chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje ste /
NK009(ta)002:1991: de'ang dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs rje chen po'i rang
NK009(ta)002:1992: bzhin las rang shar ba'i sku dpal chen rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:1993: gzhon nu'i rtags kyi phyag rgya'i gzugs sgyu ma lta
NK009(ta)002:1994: bu'o // bsgral ba'i zhes pa dang dpal rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:1995: gzhon nur shar ba des tha mal du 'dzin pa'i
NK009(ta)002:1996: phung khams skye mched dbang shes yul dang bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:1997: rtog pa med cing dag par byed pa la bsgral
NK009(ta)002:1998: bu'o // zhes bya'o // dam tshig ni zhes pa
NK009(ta)002:1999: shes rab stong pa'i rang 'od yum dam tshig gi
NK009(ta)002:2000: bu'o // zhes bya'o // phyag rgya'o // yang na /
NK009(ta)002:2001: sa ma ya zhes pa'i sgra las mi 'da' ba'i phyir dam tshig ste /
NK009(ta)002:2002: lha'i skur gsal pa'i snang ba de las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2003: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:2005: tha mal gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa med par byas
NK009(ta)002:2006: pa de'ang nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gis bsad cing
NK009(ta)002:2007: gti mug gis mnan pa lta bu ma yin te
NK009(ta)002:2009: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK009(ta)002:2010: zhes pas phung khams skye mched rnams gdod nas lha'i
NK009(ta)002:2011: ngo bo dang dbyer mi phyed par dag mnyam dgongs
NK009(ta)002:2012: pa'i gzer gyis gdab pa'i phyir rdo rje mi phyed
NK009(ta)002:2013: pa chen po'i bdag nyid du gdod nas gnas pa
NK009(ta)002:2014: la yin lugs gsal yang yang du btab pas gsos
NK009(ta)002:2016: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:2018: tshogs brgyad kyi 'phro gzhi kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK009(ta)002:2019: pas mtshon sgo lnga'i rnam shes 'khor dang bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:2020: ye shes rdo rje lnga sogs kyi bdag nyid du
NK009(ta)002:2021: gnas gyur dag pa'i rang bzhin du gdod nas gsal
NK009(ta)002:2022: bar grub pa las tha mal mtshan rtog gi 'khrul
NK009(ta)002:2023: pa 'khor ba'i rgyur shar ba thams cad dag mnyam
NK009(ta)002:2024: gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje lha dang lha mo
NK009(ta)002:2026: sems dpa' dang sems ma'i ngo bor nges pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:2028: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bsgom pa la bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:2029: gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang sbyar na /
NK009(ta)002:2030: snying rjes zhes pa dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ste /
NK009(ta)002:2031: de'ang chos thams cad spros pa dang bral ba'i stod nyid mnyam pa chen po'i rang bzhin dang /
NK009(ta)002:2032: bsgral ba'i zhes pa spros bral des dngos po dang
NK009(ta)002:2033: mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa med pa'am dag par
NK009(ta)002:2034: byas pa la bsgral ba zhes bya ba la /
NK009(ta)002:2035: dam tshig ni zhes pa spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK009(ta)002:2036: dgongs pa zab mo de las mi 'da' ba dang
NK009(ta)002:2037: / bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:2039: dngos 'dzin gyi rtog tshogs de'ang zhe sdang dang gti
NK009(ta)002:2040: mug gis bsad cing mnan pa lta bu nyid ni
NK009(ta)002:2041: ma yin te / thabs mkhas zab mo'i khyad par /
NK009(ta)002:2042: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK009(ta)002:2044: phung po lhar shes pas de'ang stong pa nyid kyi
NK009(ta)002:2045: rdo rje'i bdag nyid dang dbyer mi phyed par byed
NK009(ta)002:2047: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom /
NK009(ta)002:2049: de ltar stong par lta bar byed pa'i rnam par
NK009(ta)002:2050: shes pa de nyid kyang de'i ngo bor ma grub
NK009(ta)002:2051: par shes pa'i mtha' bral zab mo'i lta ba bde
NK009(ta)002:2052: stong thabs shes dbyer med snang stong mnyam pa chen
NK009(ta)002:2053: po zung 'jug gi rdo rje mi phyed pa chen
NK009(ta)002:2054: po nyid du bcings pa'i don no //
NK009(ta)002:2055: gnyis pa thugs rjes gzhan bsgral ba dang sbyar na /
NK009(ta)002:2056: snying rjes zhes pa sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje ste /
NK009(ta)002:2057: de'ang spyir khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa dang ldan cing /
NK009(ta)002:2058: 'bras bu sdug bsngal la spyod pa'i yul rnams dang /
NK009(ta)002:2059: bye brag bsgral ba'i zhing bcu la sogs pa la snying brtse ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2060: bsgral ba'i zhes pa 'di nas pha rol du bsgral zhing /
NK009(ta)002:2061: pha rol nas myang ngan las 'das pa'i sar bsgral ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2063: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:2064: zhes bsgral ba'i dam tshig zhe sdang drag pos bsad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2065: nga rgyal gyi dbang gi sa 'og tu mnan cing bcings pa lta bu ma yin par /
NK009(ta)002:2067: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid du //
NK009(ta)002:2068: zhes bsgral bya'i phung po khams dang skye mched dang
NK009(ta)002:2069: bcas pa rnams rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs kyi
NK009(ta)002:2070: bdag nyid du gnas bsgyur bas so //
NK009(ta)002:2071: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:2072: zhes bsgral bya'i rnam par shes pa de nyid yi
NK009(ta)002:2073: ge h'u gi rnam par byas te rdo rje gzhon
NK009(ta)002:2074: nu'i sras su byas la de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye
NK009(ta)002:2075: shes rdo rje dang dbyer med par byas pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2077: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:2079: phung po rdo rje'i bdag nyid du //
NK009(ta)002:2082: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK009(ta)002:2083: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK009(ta)002:2084: zhes par bsgyur ba gnyis don ni gong du bshad pa dang 'dra'o //
NK009(ta)002:2085: de ltar rgyud gzhung rdo rje'i tshig 'di ni shin
NK009(ta)002:2086: tu zab mo'i gnas yin pas gong du bshad pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2087: don 'di dag gu ru gsum gyi dgongs pa bsdus
NK009(ta)002:2088: pa'i lugs su 'chad par sems shing /
NK009(ta)002:2089: lha sku gsal gdab kyi skabs su 'dir bskyed rim dang gtso bor 'brel ba'i dbang du byas la /
NK009(ta)002:2090: de'ang snying rjes bsgral ba'i zhes pas gtso bo rdo rje gzhon nu nyid gsal ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2091: dam tshig ni zhes pas yum /
NK009(ta)002:2092: bsad cing mnan pa nyid min te //
NK009(ta)002:2093: phung po rdo rje bdag nyid du //
NK009(ta)002:2094: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:2095: zhes pas rang nyid nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i lha sku sems dpa' gsum dang bcas pa /
NK009(ta)002:2096: ba spu'i bu ga'i khro chung rnams bcas lhag par gsal gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2097: de dang rjes 'brel gsang ba sngags kyi sgo nas bskyed pa'i gzhi bshad pa la /
NK009(ta)002:2098: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2099: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2101: slob dpon gsum gyi dgongs pa bsdus te bshad pa /
NK009(ta)002:2102: rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar bshad pa /
NK009(ta)002:2107: badz+ra dus gsum 'dus ma byas pa /
NK009(ta)002:2108: k+ai li lha dang phur pa gso ba /
NK009(ta)002:2109: k+ai la ya phur pa 'debs pa /
NK009(ta)002:2112: bam h'u dbang du sdud pa /
NK009(ta)002:2114: gu ru bi ma la'i dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:2115: thugs rje ye shes lnga ldan /
NK009(ta)002:2118: k+ai la ya skye med 'gag med /
NK009(ta)002:2119: sarba nyon mongs ye shes su sgyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:2120: big+h+n+aana ye shes kyis nyon mongs gzir zhig /
NK009(ta)002:2123: phata nyon mongs sregs shig dang /
NK009(ta)002:2124: gu ru bal po sh+ai las /
NK009(ta)002:2129: big+h+n+aana phur bu'i ri rab kyis mnan pa /
NK009(ta)002:2132: phata spro ba'i don du 'chad do //
NK009(ta)002:2133: gnyis pa rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar na gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:2134: lha dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK009(ta)002:2135: chos nyid dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK009(ta)002:2136: byang sems dgongs pa dang sbyar te bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2138: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags h'u ngo //
NK009(ta)002:2139: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK009(ta)002:2140: bskul ba las kyi sngags sarba big+h+n+aana /
NK009(ta)002:2141: bzlas pa las kyi sngags bam h'u phata ces pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2143: dzapa dgongs dang sbyar ba badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2144: chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa /
NK009(ta)002:2145: gsal la ngos gzung med pa /
NK009(ta)002:2146: sgra grags stong du bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2148: rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku //
NK009(ta)002:2149: badz+ra dbyings gting mtha' med pa /
NK009(ta)002:2150: k+ai li k+ai la ya phur bu las 'od zer 'phros pas bsgral /
NK009(ta)002:2152: big+h+n+aana yab kyi mkha' bam mkha' dbyings sbyor ba /
NK009(ta)002:2153: h'u bud+d+ha'i thugs ye shes lnga /
NK009(ta)002:2154: phata khro bo khro mo spro ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2155: gsum pa thams cad 'dus lugs ni /
NK009(ta)002:2157: ni dpal chen yab yin te //
NK009(ta)002:2158: badz+ra shes rab yum yin no //
NK009(ta)002:2159: k+ai ni ye shes khro bo la //
NK009(ta)002:2160: li ni dbyings kyi khro mo bcu //
NK009(ta)002:2161: k+ai ni thabs kyi mche ba can //
NK009(ta)002:2162: la ni shes rab gshog pa can //
NK009(ta)002:2163: ya ni sras mchog phur pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:2164: h'u ni phyag brnyan sgo ma bzhi //
NK009(ta)002:2166: big+ha dgra dang bgegs yin no //
NK009(ta)002:2167: n+aan ni dgra dang bgegs mnan no //
NK009(ta)002:2168: bam ni dbang du bsdus pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:2169: h'u ni brlag par byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2170: phata ni bsgral ba'i phrin las rdzogs //
NK009(ta)002:2172: 'di lta bu'i sngags gcig pu 'di la lha thams cad kyi gsang sngags 'dus pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:2173: spyir k+ai la ya la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum las /
NK009(ta)002:2175: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2178: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hohmh'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2179: ces pa'i 'bru bcu gsum pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2180: rgyas pa ni sngar bshad pa 'di nyid yin par
NK009(ta)002:2181: gsungs pa des gtso bo yab kyi snying po'i bskyed
NK009(ta)002:2182: gzhi bstan cing / yum gyi bskyed gzhi'i gsang sngags /
NK009(ta)002:2183: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2187: ha na ha na bsnun bsnun zhes pa ste 'khor
NK009(ta)002:2188: lo 'bar ba bsnun bsnun zhes pa'i don du 'gyur
NK009(ta)002:2189: bar bshad la / man ngag sgom rim rnams su
NK009(ta)002:2190: 'di'i sngags don gyi dbang gis yum gyi phyag g.yas
NK009(ta)002:2191: pa drag po'i 'khor lo bsnams par bskyed par yang
NK009(ta)002:2192: bar bshad la / snang la / don du lus
NK009(ta)002:2193: dang grib ma'i tshul du yab yum thabs shes 'du
NK009(ta)002:2194: 'bral med par mnyam nyid yangs pa'i klong du lhan
NK009(ta)002:2195: cig skyes pa'i don gyis k+ai la ya dang lhan
NK009(ta)002:2196: cig tu gsungs par bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:2197: des bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan zin nas /
NK009(ta)002:2198: gnyis pa longs sku'i ngo bo phyogs bcu khro bo'i
NK009(ta)002:2199: dkyil 'khor bstan pa la bshad rgyud kyi gleng gzhi
NK009(ta)002:2200: ltar 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK009(ta)002:2201: gong du dpal chen po'i gleng gzhi las bshad pa
NK009(ta)002:2202: ltar rdo rje khrag 'thung he ru ka yab yum
NK009(ta)002:2203: gyis ru dra bsgral ba'i gnas skabs su ru dra'i
NK009(ta)002:2204: snying khrag mtheb long tsam gnyis yar ba las /
NK009(ta)002:2205: ru dra'i sras drag byed ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2206: yum drag mo ral gcig ma zhes bya ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2207: drag mo srid pa 'khor byed ma zhes bya ba gnyis dang ldan te /
NK009(ta)002:2208: de gnyis las sras phyogs bcur dam sri chen po bcu byung ste /
NK009(ta)002:2209: steng gi phyogs su yab nyi ma 'bar gsal /
NK009(ta)002:2211: bu pho nyi ma phag gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2212: bu mo zla ba rmigs bu'am rtsangs pa'i mgo can nas /
NK009(ta)002:2213: 'og tu sa bdag gzhan stobs 'joms dang /
NK009(ta)002:2214: sa bdag mo rlung gi gzugs 'dzin ma /
NK009(ta)002:2215: bu dred dam dom gyi mgo can /
NK009(ta)002:2216: bu mo byi la'am byi ba'i mgo can gyi bar
NK009(ta)002:2217: du byung ste khams gsum gyi srog la rngam pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2218: ma rungs gdug pa'i tshogs de dag gi gnyen por
NK009(ta)002:2219: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yab yum gyi gang
NK009(ta)002:2220: 'dul thugs rje chen po'i cho 'phrul las rang shar
NK009(ta)002:2221: ba'i tshu la gyis mkha' gsang nas 'od kyi gong
NK009(ta)002:2222: bu bcu steng 'og phyogs mtshams su spros pa las
NK009(ta)002:2223: khro bo bcu yab yum khra thabs dang bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:2224: phyogs bcur spros nas gdug pa'i dam sri bcu gdan
NK009(ta)002:2225: du byas / de'i tshe sems can thams cad sdug
NK009(ta)002:2226: bsngal dang bral zhing bdud bzhi rang sar zhi bar
NK009(ta)002:2228: 'dir rnal 'byor pas nang gi nyams len du sbyar
NK009(ta)002:2229: ba'i thabs mkhas gsang ba zab mo'i gnad rnams spyi
NK009(ta)002:2230: shes par bya ba la rgyud dang man ngag rnams
NK009(ta)002:2231: la thos bsam gyi mig yangs par bsgrub pa'i sgo
NK009(ta)002:2233: 'dir de dag zhib rgyas bkral ba la yi ges 'jigs shing /
NK009(ta)002:2234: gzhung don tshig tsam bkrol ba la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:2238: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK009(ta)002:2239: 'khor ba rdo rjer sgrub par mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:2240: 'khor ba rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)002:2241: ye shes khro bo grub bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:2243: de'ang rdo rje ni stong pa nyid dang snying rje dbyer mi phyed pa'i sku yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2245: rdo rje mi phyed ces byar brjod //
NK009(ta)002:2247: gzhon nu ni de lta bu'i don la 'gres rgud dang bral ba'i ngo bo ste /
NK009(ta)002:2248: mdor na dpal chen po nyid yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2250: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2251: rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa'i don //
NK009(ta)002:2252: nyon mongs spangs phyir gzhon nu la //
NK009(ta)002:2255: rig 'dzin ni spyir rdo rje'i rigs kyi rig 'dzin /
NK009(ta)002:2263: lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin bzhir yang bshad la /
NK009(ta)002:2264: don du gtso bo rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig pa 'dzin pa khro bo bcu'o //
NK009(ta)002:2265: 'khor ba'am srid pa ni phyi'i srid pa khams gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2266: nang gi srid pa lus ngag yid gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:2267: 'khor ba'am srid pa de dag don dam par skye
NK009(ta)002:2268: ba med pa'i rdo rjer sgrub par mdzod cig ces
NK009(ta)002:2269: dang / 'khor ba'am srid pa de dag kun rdzob
NK009(ta)002:2270: tu rdo rje phur pa'i lha tshogs su bsgrub pa
NK009(ta)002:2271: dang / dang / de'ang 'jig rten zhi ba'i rang
NK009(ta)002:2272: bzhin du gnas pa rnams kyang ye shes khro bo'i
NK009(ta)002:2273: rang bzhin nyid du sgrub par mdzod cig ces chos
NK009(ta)002:2274: nyid kyi rang sgras bskul bas /
NK009(ta)002:2275: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor las phyogs bcu khro
NK009(ta)002:2276: bo'i dkyil 'khor thugs rje 'gag pa med pa'i cho
NK009(ta)002:2277: 'phrul gyi sprin 'phro ba'i ched du gsol ba 'debs
NK009(ta)002:2278: pa'i don du 'grel chen 'bum nag gi dgongs pa
NK009(ta)002:2279: bzhin / 'jam mgon a mes zhabs kyang bzhed la /
NK009(ta)002:2280: 'grel chen du phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i 'og tu 'di nyid kyi tshig byung yang /
NK009(ta)002:2281: 'dir stabs bde zhing 'gal ba'ang med pas khro bo'i
NK009(ta)002:2282: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i gsol gdab kyi phyir 'dir 'brel
NK009(ta)002:2284: gnyis pa phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor spro ba dngos ni /
NK009(ta)002:2285: badz+ra kro d+ha ka ra h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2287: byang du khra'i mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2289: de la'ang byang sems rgyu'i khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2290: bskyed pa'i ye shes kyi khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2291: gdul bya sprul pa'i khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2292: drag po 'dul ba gsung gi khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2293: ye shes rtse gcig thugs kyi khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2295: sku mdog nges ma nges bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2296: phyag mtshan nges ma nges bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2297: rnam dag nges ma nges bcu'i sgo nas zhib par shes dgos kyang /
NK009(ta)002:2298: 'dir de dag gi dgongs pa'i snying po bsdus pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2299: tshul gyis tshig nyung ngu'i sgo nas 'chad pa la
NK009(ta)002:2300: spyi'i don dang / gzhung gi don gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:2302: spyir khro bo zhes pa thugs chos nyid las g.yo
NK009(ta)002:2303: ba med pa'i ngang nas thugs rje'i rtsal rab tu
NK009(ta)002:2304: phyung ba la khro bo dang /
NK009(ta)002:2305: snying rjes sems can gyi don mdzad pas shugs kyis khro bas shugs khro dang /
NK009(ta)002:2306: nyon mongs rnam rtog dang lhan cig mi gnas par rang bzhin khro ba dang bcas pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2307: zhi bas mi thul ba rnams 'dul ba'i phyir gdul
NK009(ta)002:2308: bya'i dbang gis sku gsung thugs kyi rnam par khro
NK009(ta)002:2309: bar bcos pas na khro bo zhes bya ste /
NK009(ta)002:2310: k+ai la ya tan+t+ra bcu gnyis pa'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:2311: ngang khro shugs khro khro bar bcas dang bcos //
NK009(ta)002:2314: gong du bstan pa'i byang sems rgyu'i khro bo bcu
NK009(ta)002:2315: ni dpal chen yab yum bde stong mnyam par rol
NK009(ta)002:2316: pa'i thugs rje'i rtsal ma 'gags pa'i cho 'phrul las
NK009(ta)002:2317: sbyor mtshams nas h'u yig sbrel ma bcu /
NK009(ta)002:2318: thig le dkar dmar bcu bcu ste bzhi bcu dang /
NK009(ta)002:2319: dzahmh'u bam hohste yig 'bru bzhi bcas phyogs bcu sgo
NK009(ta)002:2320: bzhi dang bcas pa la spros pa'i cho 'phrul nyid
NK009(ta)002:2321: la bya / bskyed pa'i ye shes kyi khro bo
NK009(ta)002:2322: bcu ni bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags bcus lha rang
NK009(ta)002:2323: rang krong nger byon pa la bshad /
NK009(ta)002:2324: gdul bya sprul pa'i khro bo ni khro bo yab yum /
NK009(ta)002:2326: sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa rnams sku mdog cha lugs sna tshogs su shar ba la ngos 'dzin /
NK009(ta)002:2327: drag po 'dul ba gsung gi khro bo bcu ni /
NK009(ta)002:2328: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra zhes pa nas /
NK009(ta)002:2329: ma h+aa ba la'i bar dang /
NK009(ta)002:2330: bzlas sngags ha na ha na sogs dang /
NK009(ta)002:2331: pa tsa pa tsa zhes sogs thog 'dril ba lta
NK009(ta)002:2332: bu'i rno ngar drag rtsal bzod du med par 'bar
NK009(ta)002:2333: ba'i mthu ldan ngos 'dzin par bshad /
NK009(ta)002:2334: ye shes rtse gcig thugs kyi khro bo bcu ni khro bcu'i phur pa sor bcu gnyis pa /
NK009(ta)002:2335: mgo brnyan gyi phur pa sor brgyad pa /
NK009(ta)002:2336: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa sor bzhi pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2337: lha phur byugs bdug brabs pas gzi byin bskyed pa rnams yin par gsungs so //
NK009(ta)002:2338: grangs nges pa ni khro bo bcu 'ba' zhig yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2339: rgyu mtshan lam phar phyin bcu bgrod pa'i phyir dang /
NK009(ta)002:2340: 'bras bu stobs bcu la mnga' mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK009(ta)002:2341: spang bya mi dge ba bcu dag pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2342: gdul bya phyogs skyong bcu 'dul ba la mang ba
NK009(ta)002:2343: dang nyung bas don du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir na'o
NK009(ta)002:2344: // steng 'og dang phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo rnams
NK009(ta)002:2345: gong 'og dang phan tshun go sa bsnol na'ang don
NK009(ta)002:2347: so so'i gdul bya de dang de yi gnyen por
NK009(ta)002:2348: lhag par shar bas na gdul bya'i gnyen po gang
NK009(ta)002:2349: yin de las gzhan du go sa spos na 'gal
NK009(ta)002:2350: bar gsungs la / khro bo de dag sku mdog kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK009(ta)002:2352: h+aum ka ra sngo skya dang /
NK009(ta)002:2353: rnam rgyal dkar por bshad pa sogs dang /
NK009(ta)002:2354: gzhan yang khro bo thams cad dmar por bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2356: khro bo 'di dag ni yab rdo rje gzhon nu'i cha dang mthun pas mthing nag go //
NK009(ta)002:2357: zhes thams cad mthing nag tu gsungs pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2358: k+ai la ya tan+t+ra bcu gnyis pa las /
NK009(ta)002:2359: dper na tshon sngon kha dog la //
NK009(ta)002:2360: tshon gzhan dag gis bsgyur du med //
NK009(ta)002:2361: de bzhin khro rgyal mthing nag kyang //
NK009(ta)002:2362: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags //
NK009(ta)002:2364: gzhan yang sku mdog gi nges pa mang du yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2365: phyag mtshan kyang ma nges te /
NK009(ta)002:2366: gdul bya gnyen po'i phyag mtshan phyogs skyong bcu'i phyag mtshan gyi rnam pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2367: rig pa rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK009(ta)002:2368: gzhan yang rbod gtong phra men gyi phyag mtshan la sogs pa mang du gsungs shing /
NK009(ta)002:2369: rta mchog rol pa las kyang /
NK009(ta)002:2370: lcags kyu phur pa thogs pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:2371: bdag nyid chen po de yi 'khor //
NK009(ta)002:2372: pho nya'i tshogs dang bcas pa bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:2375: phyag mtshan ni lcags kyu dang phur pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2377: phrin las phur pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di nyid la rtsa
NK009(ta)002:2378: ba dang yan lag gi lha'i dbye ba'ang rtsa ba'i
NK009(ta)002:2380: yan lag gi lha sum cu rtsa drug yod par bshad cing /
NK009(ta)002:2381: don du gtso bo yab yum /
NK009(ta)002:2382: khro bo yab yum nyi shu /
NK009(ta)002:2384: sras mchog ste nyi shu rtsa bdun ni rtsa ba'i lha yin la /
NK009(ta)002:2385: sprul pa phyag brnyan nyi shu /
NK009(ta)002:2386: dam can bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa drug ni yan lag gi lha ste /
NK009(ta)002:2387: bsdoms pas drug cu rtsa gsum 'byung ba'ang /
NK009(ta)002:2388: phur pa rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:2389: snang srid thams cad drug cu rtsa gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du gyur to //
NK009(ta)002:2391: de dag gi rnam par dag pa'i tshul yang /
NK009(ta)002:2392: h'u ka ra 'dod pa'i skyon spangs skye la mnga' mdzad pa nas /
NK009(ta)002:2393: byang sgor khra'i mgo can btang snyoms dag pa'i ngo
NK009(ta)002:2394: bo'i bar du gsungs pa'i gnad shes pa gal che'ang
NK009(ta)002:2395: / 'dir yi ge mang ba'i 'jigs pas ma spros pa /
NK009(ta)002:2397: grub pa'i rig 'dzin rnam gsum gyi dgongs pa 'grel chen 'bum nag sogs su gsal lo //
NK009(ta)002:2398: gnyis pa gzhung don dngos bshad pa la /
NK009(ta)002:2399: dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa'i dpal he
NK009(ta)002:2400: ru ka rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyi bde
NK009(ta)002:2401: ba chen po'i rol rtsed sgyu ma lta bu'i mkha'
NK009(ta)002:2402: gsang nas gang 'dul thugs rje'i rol pa khro bo
NK009(ta)002:2404: yab kyis sprul pa'i mche ba can dang yum gyis
NK009(ta)002:2405: sprul pa'i gshog pa can te za gsod sprul pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2407: 'gugs 'ching sdom myos kyi las byed sgo ma bzhi
NK009(ta)002:2408: dang bcas pa bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags rnams dang
NK009(ta)002:2409: / h'u yig sbrel ma dang thig ler shar ba'i
NK009(ta)002:2410: cho 'phrul sprul pa'i tshul du rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK009(ta)002:2411: gyi steng 'og phyogs mtshams su steng tshangs pa nas
NK009(ta)002:2412: 'og sa bdag gi bar gyi rang rang gi gdul
NK009(ta)002:2413: byar gyur pa'i phyogs skyong ba pho mo rnams bsnol
NK009(ta)002:2414: ba'am kha sbub gan rkyal du gnas pa'i steng du
NK009(ta)002:2415: mig 'phrul bzhin lam ste shar ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:2416: de'ang gdan re re'i steng du khro bo yab yum
NK009(ta)002:2417: khra thabs gnyis dang bzhi re 'phros pa ni tshad
NK009(ta)002:2419: des na yab yum gyi mkha' gsang nas /
NK009(ta)002:2422: ces pa'i bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags las khro bo chen po h'u mdzad dang /
NK009(ta)002:2423: h'u las khro mo rdo rje sgra 'byin ma /
NK009(ta)002:2424: gardzasa phag gi mgo can g.yas dang /
NK009(ta)002:2425: yang gardzasa rmigs bu'am rtsangs ba'i mgo can g.yon du phyung ste steng phyogs tshangs pa'i gdan la 'khod /
NK009(ta)002:2430: h'u ka ra h'u mdzad de /
NK009(ta)002:2431: mdor na rdo rje'am ye shes khro bo h'u mdzad ces bya bar 'gyur la /
NK009(ta)002:2432: h'u zhes pa yum gyi sa bon /
NK009(ta)002:2433: gardza gardza zungs zungs zhes pa yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2434: sprul pa bkye ba'i sngags su'ang gsungs la /
NK009(ta)002:2436: h'u thugs kyi sa bon khro bo thams cad kyi snying po dang /
NK009(ta)002:2438: drag po'i las la bskul ba'i don du'ang 'jug par bshad cing /
NK009(ta)002:2441: spro ba sogs du ma la 'jug mod kyi /
NK009(ta)002:2442: mdor na h'u phata ces pa drag po'i sngags kyi mjug sdud du gsungs so //
NK009(ta)002:2443: badz+ra kro d+h+ai d+ai pa ya ti h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2446: d+ai pa ya ti sgra 'byin ma /
NK009(ta)002:2448: badz+ra su ka ra mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2452: badz+ra i shu pa mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2454: i shu pa rmigs bu'am rtsangs pa'i gdong can ma zhes par 'gyur la /
NK009(ta)002:2455: yab las sprul pa'i za byed kyi pha bcu ni g.yas dang /
NK009(ta)002:2456: yum las sprul pa'i gsod byed kyi ma bcu g.yon du 'khod pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2457: de bzhin du shar phyogs dri za'i gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2458: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2459: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2460: ces pa'i sngags cha bzhir bgos te rnam rgyal yab
NK009(ta)002:2461: yum phra thabs dang bcas pa spro ba sngar gyi
NK009(ta)002:2462: rigs 'gre ste 'og ma rnams la'ang shes par bya
NK009(ta)002:2463: zhing / badz+ra kro d+h+ai l+aa s+ya ki h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2464: zhes pa de'i yum rdo rje lha mo sgeg mo dang /
NK009(ta)002:2465: badz+ra b+y+aa kri mu kha h'u gis sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma stag gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2466: badz+ra grid+h+ra mu khi h'u gis bya rgod mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2467: shar lhor me lha'i gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2468: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2469: ha na ha na h'u phata kyis dbyug sngon 'chang ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2470: badz+ra kro d+h+ai t+ai ra h'u gis yum rdo rje sder mo dang /
NK009(ta)002:2471: badz+ra tsa ma ra mu kha h'u gis phra men g.yag mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2472: badz+ra ta n+aa mu khi h'u gis bya rog gi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2474: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2475: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata las khro bo gshin rje mthar byed dang /
NK009(ta)002:2476: badz+ra kro d+h+ai sh+ma sha na ba ti h'u las lha mo dur khrod kyi bdag mo dang /
NK009(ta)002:2477: de bzhin ha ri na mu kha las phra men ma ri dwags sam sha ba'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2478: +au lu ka mu khi las 'ug pa'i mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2479: lho nub tu srin po'i gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2480: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2481: ban+d+ha ban+d+ha h'u phata kyis khro bo mig g.yo mgon po dang /
NK009(ta)002:2482: badz+ra kro d+h+ai mu ha las lha mo gtun khung ma dang /
NK009(ta)002:2483: badz+ra t+ya ki mu kha dang /
NK009(ta)002:2484: badz+ra pe ta mu khi las rdo rje phra men gzig dang /
NK009(ta)002:2487: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai ba h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2488: hu lu hu lu h'u phata las khro bo rta mgrin dang /
NK009(ta)002:2489: badz+ra kro d+h+ai dza ya ti h'u las rdo rje khro mo gtum mo dang /
NK009(ta)002:2490: badz+ra pi t+aa la mu kha dang /
NK009(ta)002:2491: badz+ra pak+shi ta mu khi las rdo rje lha mo phra men ma byi la dang /
NK009(ta)002:2492: pu shud kyi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2493: nub byang du rlung lha'i gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2494: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2495: tish+tha tish+tha h'u phata kyis khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2496: badz+ra kro d+h+ai sa bya ti h'u gis rdo rje khro mo mda' snyems ma dang /
NK009(ta)002:2497: badz+ra sri ga la mu kha dang /
NK009(ta)002:2498: badz+ra pany+tsa ra na mu khi las rdo rje phra men spyang ki dang /
NK009(ta)002:2500: byang du gnod sbyin gyi gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2501: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da l+ai h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2503: ces pa las khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2504: h'u badz+ra kro d+h+ai sa bya mi ti h'u las rdo rje lha mo sgra mdzad ma dang /
NK009(ta)002:2505: badz+ra sim ha mu kha dang /
NK009(ta)002:2506: badz+ra ti ti la mu khi las rdo rje phra men ma seng ge dang /
NK009(ta)002:2507: pha wang gi mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2508: byang shar du bgegs kyi gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2509: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2511: ces pa las khro bo 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2512: badz+ra kro d+h+ai m+aa ra ya h'u las rdo rje lha mo gsod byed ma dang /
NK009(ta)002:2513: badz+ra rak+shi sa mu kha dang /
NK009(ta)002:2514: badz+ra na ku la mu khi las rdo rje lha mo phra men ma dred dang /
NK009(ta)002:2516: 'og phyogs sa bdag gi gdan la /
NK009(ta)002:2517: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2518: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:2519: ces pa las khro bo stobs po che dang /
NK009(ta)002:2520: badz+ra kro d+h+ai mun+de mam h'u las rdo rje lha mo rig byed ma dang /
NK009(ta)002:2521: badz+ra rak+sha sa mu kha h'u dang /
NK009(ta)002:2522: badz+ra ka shi ka mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2523: zhes pa dag las so sor sprul pa'i lha mo phra men ma dom gyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2525: de bzhin dzahmh'u bam hohzhesa pa'i yig 'bru dang /
NK009(ta)002:2526: badz+ra yak+sha sa da h'u dzah zhes spros pa la
NK009(ta)002:2527: shar du 'gugs byed kyi sgo ma snying rje'i ngo
NK009(ta)002:2528: bo pu shud kyi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2529: badz+ra bee ra be h'u h'u /
NK009(ta)002:2530: zhes lhor byams pa'i ngo bo 'ching byed kyi sgo ma bya rog gi mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2531: badz+ra a mri ta h'u bam /
NK009(ta)002:2532: zhes nub du dga' ba'i ngo bo sdom byed kyi sgo ma srin bya'i mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2533: badz+ra ma ra ni h+aum hoh zhes spros pa las
NK009(ta)002:2534: byang du btang snyoms kyi ngo bo myos byed gyi
NK009(ta)002:2535: sgo ma khra'i mgo can no //
NK009(ta)002:2536: 'di dag gi khyad par gong du h'u ka ra'i skabs su cung zad bshad pas mtshon nus la /
NK009(ta)002:2537: so so'i sngags don sogs ni blo ldan rnams kyis rtogs par sla bas ma spros la /
NK009(ta)002:2538: shes par 'dod na 'jam mgon a mes zhabs kyi
NK009(ta)002:2539: dkyil chog rnam bshad sogs su blta bar bya zhing
NK009(ta)002:2540: / lha snam gyi khor yug tu srung ma dam
NK009(ta)002:2541: can bcu drug gi tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa'ang gsal
NK009(ta)002:2542: / bar bshad cing / so so'i sku mdog phyag
NK009(ta)002:2543: mtshan rgyan cha lugs rnams kyang so sor rgyas pa
NK009(ta)002:2544: man ngag sgom don phrin las kyi rim pa rnams
NK009(ta)002:2545: su 'byung bas 'dir smos ma dgos so //
NK009(ta)002:2546: 'di'i sngags rnams kyang snga 'gyur dang mi mtshungs pa 'ga' zhig 'dug kyang /
NK009(ta)002:2547: chos rje sa pan nyid kyis bsgyur ba 'di bzhin mi 'gal bar shes par bya la /
NK009(ta)002:2548: rgyu mtshan zhib par brjod na yi ge'i las su che bas ma spros so //
NK009(ta)002:2549: 'dir khro bcu khra phyag rnams kyi don rtags kyang /
NK009(ta)002:2550: khro bcu mi dge ba bcu dag pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2551: gdul bya phyogs skyong bcu'i gnyen po dang /
NK009(ta)002:2552: 'bras bu phar phyin bcu'i ngo bor shar ba'i tshul gong du mdo tsam bstan la /
NK009(ta)002:2553: de dag gi phyag mtshan gyi don yang thams cad
NK009(ta)002:2554: kyis rdo rje dang b+han dmar thogs pa ni rig
NK009(ta)002:2556: phyogs skyong bcu'i phyag mtshan rang rang gi phyag bar
NK009(ta)002:2557: pas bsnams pa ni rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi phyag
NK009(ta)002:2558: mtshan / kun kyang tha mas ri rab phur bu
NK009(ta)002:2559: 'dril ba ni phrin las don rtags 'byin pa'i phyag
NK009(ta)002:2560: mtshan / mtshan te / za byed yak+sha 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:2561: rdo rje b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang ba ni //
NK009(ta)002:2562: skye med 'dus ma byas pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK009(ta)002:2563: srid rtsa sdug bsngal rak+ta zhal du gsol //
NK009(ta)002:2564: gnyis med bde chen sbyor ba'i lam la bkod //
NK009(ta)002:2565: phyogs skyong bcu btul phyag mtshan bar mar bsnams //
NK009(ta)002:2566: rgyal byed dpa' rtags zhes su de la grags //
NK009(ta)002:2567: ri rab phur ba tha mar 'dril ba ni //
NK009(ta)002:2568: phrin las don rtags 'byin pa'i phyag mtshan no //
NK009(ta)002:2570: drag po lha srin sde brgyad 'dul ba'i phyir 'jigs
NK009(ta)002:2571: byed dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan par gsungs so
NK009(ta)002:2572: // phra men rnams kyi don rtags la 'grel pa
NK009(ta)002:2573: 'bum nag sogs dang snga 'gyur phur pa yak+sha 'bar
NK009(ta)002:2574: ba'i rgyud sogs las ci rigs par 'byung zhing /
NK009(ta)002:2575: 'dir de dag gi dgongs pa phyogs mtshon tsam du bsdu na /
NK009(ta)002:2576: spyir phra men zhes pa la dpe'i phra men /
NK009(ta)002:2578: rtags kyi phra men gsum las /
NK009(ta)002:2580: dper na gser skyogs la dngul gyi phra bcug pa
NK009(ta)002:2581: la phra men gyi yol go zer ba lta bu
NK009(ta)002:2582: dang / don gyi phra men ni /
NK009(ta)002:2583: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med du 'dres pa la 'jog par gsungs /
NK009(ta)002:2585: mgo lus mi gcig pa la phra men zhes pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2586: 'dir rnam pa lha'i gzugs la srog chags sna tshogs
NK009(ta)002:2587: kyi mgo can du yod pas phra men zhes pa
NK009(ta)002:2589: lcam dral nyi shu po la phra phyag gi rnam dbye so sor phye na /
NK009(ta)002:2590: g.yas kyi mche ba can bcu la yab kyi phyag brnyan dang /
NK009(ta)002:2591: g.yon gyi gshog pa can bcu la yum gyi phra men gyi tha snyad kyang mdzad cing /
NK009(ta)002:2592: 'di rnams kyi don zhib par brjod pa zhig ma mthong bas 'dir cung zad dbye na /
NK009(ta)002:2593: de'ang srin po lha chen bcu btul ba'i phyi rol
NK009(ta)002:2594: na zhe sdang gdug pa'i gcan gzan drug gnas pa
NK009(ta)002:2595: ni / za byed za ba 'gying ba'i stag dang /
NK009(ta)002:2597: myur mgyogs kyi byi la dang /
NK009(ta)002:2598: gsod la dga' ba'i spyang ki dang /
NK009(ta)002:2599: zil gyis gnon pa'i seng ge dang /
NK009(ta)002:2600: gtum pa'i dom dang drug gnas te /
NK009(ta)002:2601: de drug ni pha'i zhe sdang las bskyed pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2602: zhe sdang gi snyigs ma rus pa /
NK009(ta)002:2603: rus pa mthar rgyas pa mche ba ste yab las bskyed pa'i za byed mche ba can zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:2604: de dag 'dul ba'i phyir khro bo rnams kyi sprul
NK009(ta)002:2605: pa yab kho nas bskyed de yum drug dang ma
NK009(ta)002:2606: chags thabs kyis rol pa las pha ye shes kyi
NK009(ta)002:2607: khro bo yin pas lus lhar byas /
NK009(ta)002:2608: ma gdug pa byol song du byung ste sprul pa'i phra men ma zhes grags so //
NK009(ta)002:2609: bu de drug la mkhyen pa'i ye shes ni sdug
NK009(ta)002:2610: gis nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal dpa' bar 'joms pa
NK009(ta)002:2611: dang / gzig gi mgo can gyis shes bya thogs med kyi ye shes gsal ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2612: byi la'i mgo can ni rtsol sgrub thams cad zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2613: spyang ka'i mgo can ni sbyor sgrol dbyings su dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK009(ta)002:2614: seng ge'i mgo can ni zhe sdang skyon gyis mi 'jigs pa'i ye shes dang /
NK009(ta)002:2615: dom gyi mgo can ni gdug gtum thams cad byams
NK009(ta)002:2616: pa'i sbyor ba'i ye shes dang khyad par drug gis
NK009(ta)002:2617: zhe sdang gnas su dag cing khyad par du 'joms
NK009(ta)002:2618: par byed pa'o // yang 'dod chags sdug bsngal 'dab
NK009(ta)002:2619: chags brgyad gnas te 'jug skem sha zan gyi bya
NK009(ta)002:2620: par byed pa'o // rgod dang / rmang rtse rol pa'i bya rog dang /
NK009(ta)002:2622: sgrib g.yogs phag tu bkol ba khwa ta dang /
NK009(ta)002:2623: 'jol 'phur rgod nas 'jab kyi pu shud dang /
NK009(ta)002:2624: bya gcan thams cad 'dul ba'i hor khra dang drug ni ma 'dod chags las bsten pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2626: khrag mthar rgyas pa gshog pa ste yum las gsod
NK009(ta)002:2627: byed gshog pa can de rnams kyi gnyen por khro
NK009(ta)002:2628: mo rnams las sprul pa'i sras drug byung ste pha
NK009(ta)002:2629: ye shes kyi khro bo yin pas lus lhar byung
NK009(ta)002:2630: / ma 'dod chags gdul bya'i byol song yin pas mgo byar byung ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2631: bu de drug la mkhyen pa'i ye shes ni 'gro
NK009(ta)002:2632: ba'i don la thogs pa med pa'i bya rgod mgo
NK009(ta)002:2633: can dang / chos nyid mi 'gyur ba bya rog mgo can /
NK009(ta)002:2634: mi shes mun pa gzigs pa'i 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK009(ta)002:2635: sdug bsngal dbyings su snyol ba'i kha ta /
NK009(ta)002:2636: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i pu shud /
NK009(ta)002:2637: nyon mongs dbyings su 'joms pa'i hor khra ste ye
NK009(ta)002:2638: shes khyad par drug gi 'dod chags gnas su dag
NK009(ta)002:2639: cing khyad par 'dod chags kyi gnyen po'o //
NK009(ta)002:2640: yang gti mug pa'i za gsod drug ste /
NK009(ta)002:2641: gti mug dur phag phra mos sems can thams cad
NK009(ta)002:2642: gsod par byed pa nyon mongs gtsor 'dzin gyi mche
NK009(ta)002:2643: ba can dang / gti mug gi dug sha nag
NK009(ta)002:2644: po ltas ngan don la 'dzin pa'i mche ba can
NK009(ta)002:2645: ba can dang / dang / gti mug gi dug
NK009(ta)002:2646: g.yag kham pa ro la za ba'i mche ba can
NK009(ta)002:2647: ba can dang / dang / dang / gti mug
NK009(ta)002:2648: gi dug bya rmigs bu rtag 'dzin thob pa'i gshog
NK009(ta)002:2649: ba can dang / dang / dang / pa can
NK009(ta)002:2650: dang / gti mug gi dug sre mong dug rtsal
NK009(ta)002:2651: che ba'i gshog pa can dang /
NK009(ta)002:2652: gti mug gi dug byi ba rku la dga' ba'i
NK009(ta)002:2653: las byed gshog pa can dang drug gi gnyis med
NK009(ta)002:2654: gti mug las bskyed pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2655: gti mug gi snyigs ma sha /
NK009(ta)002:2656: sha mthar rgyas pa las byed mi shes pa ni
NK009(ta)002:2657: yab yum gnyis cha las bskyed pa'i de rnams 'dul
NK009(ta)002:2658: ba'i phyir khro bo rnams kyi thugs las sprul pa
NK009(ta)002:2659: mkha' las bskyed de yum drug dang sbyor ba las
NK009(ta)002:2660: yab lha yin pas lus lhar byung /
NK009(ta)002:2661: ma byol song yin pas mgo yang der byung ste
NK009(ta)002:2662: de la sprul pa'i phra men ma zhes bya zhing
NK009(ta)002:2663: / de drug la mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang phag
NK009(ta)002:2664: ni ye shes gtsang dme med pas rnam rtog 'joms
NK009(ta)002:2665: / / g.yag ni chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i don la 'joms /
NK009(ta)002:2666: sha ba ni ye shes rgyas pa'i mtshan ma'i bag chags 'joms /
NK009(ta)002:2667: rmigs bu ni ye shes thogs med 'khor ba'i zhen pa 'joms /
NK009(ta)002:2668: sre mong gi rnam rtog bya rlag skye med dbyings su grol /
NK009(ta)002:2669: byi ba ni cir snang thams cad gzung 'dzin mtha' las grol /
NK009(ta)002:2670: ye shes kyi khyad par de dag drug gis gti mug gnas su dag /
NK009(ta)002:2671: khyad par du gti mug gi gnyen po'o //
NK009(ta)002:2672: dug gsum cha snyoms pa'i dred dang pha wam gnyis
NK009(ta)002:2673: ni shar dang nub kyi mthar gnas pa zhe sdang
NK009(ta)002:2674: rus pa'i mtha' la mche ba rgyas /
NK009(ta)002:2675: 'dod chags khrag gi mtha' la bya gshog rgyas /
NK009(ta)002:2676: gti mug sha'i mtha' las smra mi shes pa de
NK009(ta)002:2677: dag gi gnyen por yab yum snyoms pa las sprul
NK009(ta)002:2678: pa'i dred mo la shes byar ma rmongs rtogs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2679: ye shes mnga' / pha wang mgo can la gti mug gi lam stor bas nyin par mi rgyu /
NK009(ta)002:2680: dug gsum 'joms pa'i gshog rlabs dang ldan /
NK009(ta)002:2681: ma rig mun pa sel ba'i ye shes mnga' ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2682: de dag gi sku mdog phyag mtshan kyang /
NK009(ta)002:2684: g.yas g.yon zhal las shes par bya //
NK009(ta)002:2685: gtso bo rnams kyi bar ma sbyin //
NK009(ta)002:2686: zhes pas phra phyag rnams kya sku mdog rang rang
NK009(ta)002:2687: gi gtso bo'i zhal g.yas g.yon gyi kha dog las
NK009(ta)002:2689: phyag mtshan rnams ni gtso bo rang rang phyag bar
NK009(ta)002:2690: ma'i mtshon cha g.yas g.yon gyi phra phyag gnyis la
NK009(ta)002:2692: g.yon thams cad du rig pa rang rtags kyi phyag
NK009(ta)002:2693: mtshan phur bu 'dril zhing dgra la 'debs pa bshad
NK009(ta)002:2695: phra men rnams kyi don rtags 'di rigs rgyud gzhan
NK009(ta)002:2696: dang gzhan na cung zad tha dad pa'i rnam 'gyur
NK009(ta)002:2697: re gsungs pa yod kyang 'dir phur bu za byed
NK009(ta)002:2698: yak+sha 'bar ba'i rgyud las bstan pa ltar cung zad
NK009(ta)002:2699: bstan zin gyi / thams cad kyi dgongs pa gnad
NK009(ta)002:2700: gcig tu 'babs pas gang ltar bshad kyang rung ngo
NK009(ta)002:2701: bstan zin gyi / // de ltar ru dra'i gleng
NK009(ta)002:2702: gzhi dang sbyar nas dkyil 'khor 'di nyid kyi byung
NK009(ta)002:2703: ba smos pa dag rnal 'byor pa'i nyams len du
NK009(ta)002:2704: sbyar na gtso bor bskyed rim gyi phyag rgya bstan
NK009(ta)002:2705: bstan zin gyi / // pa yin la / 'dir
NK009(ta)002:2706: shes dgos pa'i gnad khyad par ba ni ma h+aa
NK009(ta)002:2707: yo ga tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad kyis bstan
NK009(ta)002:2708: don rgyud sde dang sgrub sde gang yin kyang de'i
NK009(ta)002:2709: dgongs pa ni lta ba kun rdzob kyi chos thams
NK009(ta)002:2710: cad dag pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du lta zhing /
NK009(ta)002:2711: de dag don dam par gdod ma'i chos dbyings dang
NK009(ta)002:2712: gnyis su med par bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod
NK009(ta)002:2713: yul dang bral ba gtan la 'bebs cing /
NK009(ta)002:2714: bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum yan lag
NK009(ta)002:2715: dang bcas pa'i tshul gyis snang srid lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK009(ta)002:2716: du 'char ba'i bskyed rim la gtso bor lam du
NK009(ta)002:2717: byed pa dang / spyod pa gang shar blang dor
NK009(ta)002:2718: med pa'i ngang nas thabs la mkhas pa'i spyod pa
NK009(ta)002:2719: khyad par can sbyor sgrol la sogs pa dang du
NK009(ta)002:2720: byed pa dang / len pa dang / 'bras bu
NK009(ta)002:2721: tshe 'di la rig 'dzin bzhi'i lam bgrod nas yi
NK009(ta)002:2722: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa la sangs rgyas
NK009(ta)002:2724: de'ang gsang sngags kyi gzhung na lha bsgom pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2727: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa bslab pa'i mtha' bcu
NK009(ta)002:2728: po thams cad spros bcas kyi sgo nas nyams su
NK009(ta)002:2729: len pa'i gang zag snang ba yul gyi blo can
NK009(ta)002:2730: rnams kyis gtso bor bskyed rim la brten te bsgyur
NK009(ta)002:2731: cing / bskyed pa'i rim pa ting 'dzin brtan po'i
NK009(ta)002:2732: sgo nas rdzogs rim drangs te bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug
NK009(ta)002:2733: gi tshul la 'jug pa rnams kyi lam gnad thams
NK009(ta)002:2734: cad bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i snang ba lhar
NK009(ta)002:2735: bsgrub pa'i gnad la thug pa yin gyi /
NK009(ta)002:2736: de dang mi ldan na lam gyi gzugs brnyan du
NK009(ta)002:2737: 'gyur bas na 'di tshul zhib mor sgyu 'phrul rtsa
NK009(ta)002:2738: rgyud gsang ba'i snying po nyid las 'byung ba ltar
NK009(ta)002:2739: shes par bya ba'i gnad che shos shig yin la
NK009(ta)002:2740: / snang ba lhar bsgrub kyi dgongs pa 'di la
NK009(ta)002:2741: mi 'thad pa'i sgro skur smra ba dag yod mod
NK009(ta)002:2742: / kyi / de ni rtog ge'i blo gros khab
NK009(ta)002:2743: kyi bu gar zab gsang gi dgongs pa nam mkha'
NK009(ta)002:2744: lta bu ma chud pa'i smre sngags tsam du zad
NK009(ta)002:2745: pas snying po yod pa ma yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:2746: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i rig 'dzin skal ldan rnam
NK009(ta)002:2747: dpyod can rnams kyis ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud kyi
NK009(ta)002:2748: dgongs zab snang ba lhar bsgrub pa'i lung rigs seng
NK009(ta)002:2749: ge'i sgra chen pos zab cing gsang ba'i gnad mi
NK009(ta)002:2750: nyams slar yang spel ba'i phrin las la g.yel ba
NK009(ta)002:2751: med pa'i thugs rtsol gnang bar rigs so zhes 'phros
NK009(ta)002:2752: su smos pa'o // de dag gis ni chos sku'i
NK009(ta)002:2753: ngo bo dpal chen po bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK009(ta)002:2755: khro bo rnams longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i ngo bor gsungs pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2756: phyogs skyong bcu 'dul ba'i phyir du gnas phyogs bcur bzhugs shing /
NK009(ta)002:2759: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mdo tsam bshad zin to //
NK009(ta)002:2760: gsum pa sprul pa'i sku'i ngo bor phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:2764: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK009(ta)002:2765: rdo rje'i de nyid rang bzhin las //
NK009(ta)002:2766: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK009(ta)002:2767: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK009(ta)002:2768: sku yi gter du bdag skyed cig /
NK009(ta)002:2770: 'di la rig 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi dgongs pa'i don mdor bsdu na /
NK009(ta)002:2771: ma rig pa'i mun pa mtha' dag sangs shing mkhyen
NK009(ta)002:2772: pa'i ye shes pad+ma ltar rgyas pa'i bdag nyid dus
NK009(ta)002:2773: gsum kun tu gshegs pa'i 'dus ma byas pa rdo
NK009(ta)002:2774: rje ye shes kyi sku can nam /
NK009(ta)002:2775: sangs rgyas chos sku'i rten du gyur pa'am nyon mongs
NK009(ta)002:2776: pa lnga sangs shing ye shes lnga rgyas pa'i ye
NK009(ta)002:2777: shes la'ang rang byung gi ye shes /
NK009(ta)002:2779: gnas gyur gyi ye shes rnams kyi bdag nyid /
NK009(ta)002:2780: yon tan de dang de dag gi rten byed pa'i cha nas sku'i tha snyad 'jug pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2781: chos kyi sku rdo rje'i mtshan nyid can de nyid
NK009(ta)002:2782: kyi rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings sam chos sku'i ngang
NK009(ta)002:2783: las / chos kyi dbyings ka nas dag pa de
NK009(ta)002:2784: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi rnam 'phrul las gzhan
NK009(ta)002:2785: du g.yo ba med pa'i gang 'dul thugs rje'i rtsal
NK009(ta)002:2786: dang rol pa ma 'gags pa'i rnam char shar ba
NK009(ta)002:2787: las / / gdug pa can 'dul ba la mthu stobs lhag par 'bar ba'am /
NK009(ta)002:2788: gar nyams dgu'i gzi byin 'bar ba'i khro bo sras
NK009(ta)002:2789: mchog k+ai la ya dpal chen po'i mthu rtsal phrin
NK009(ta)002:2790: las kyi ngo bo lhag par bskyed pa las byung
NK009(ta)002:2791: bas bzod par dka' ba'i gzi byin gyis mi bzad
NK009(ta)002:2792: 'jigs rung drag po'i sku'i gter ram dbyig ste /
NK009(ta)002:2793: yon tan thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid
NK009(ta)002:2794: du skyed par mdzod cig ces bskul zhing gsol ba'o
NK009(ta)002:2795: // gnyis pa bskyed pa dngos la /
NK009(ta)002:2796: sku gsum gyi klong nas bskyed pa la chos gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2797: sku gsung thugs ye shes rtse gcig tu byin gyis rlob pa la yig 'bru gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2798: chu srin rnam grol gyi phyag rgyas blang ba la dgos pa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2799: rigs lngas dbang bskur ba la rdzas gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2800: sku gsung thugs byin brlab la sngags gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2801: gu gul gyis gdug pa la nus pa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2802: yungs kar gyis brab pa la ting 'dzin gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2803: rak+tasa byugs pa la ngar gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2804: sras mchog gi rnam dbye mu bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:2805: phur pa'i rnam dbye la chos bdun te don bcu'i sgo nas shes par bya dgos la /
NK009(ta)002:2806: 'dir de dag gi don tshang bar tshig nyung ngus bstan na /
NK009(ta)002:2807: spyir rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba ni sras mchog rigs lnga yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2808: 'di nyid 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i sras dang chos mthun sbyar nas bshad dgos par gsungs pas /
NK009(ta)002:2809: dper na 'khor sgyur gyi sras de nyid pha'i rgyud kyis dag pa /
NK009(ta)002:2810: ma'i rgyud kyis dag pa ste rigs rus cho 'brangs dang ldan pa dgos pa ltar /
NK009(ta)002:2813: gsum pa sprul sku dbu gsum phyag drug pa'am /
NK009(ta)002:2815: sku smad phur bu'i dbal gyi rnam pa can de nyid sku gsum gyi klong nas shar ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:2817: 'dir ni dbu gsum phyag drug dang //
NK009(ta)002:2818: zhal gcig phyag kyang bzhi pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:2819: de las mang ba ngas ma bshad //
NK009(ta)002:2822: lte ba man chad sku smad ni //
NK009(ta)002:2823: sngo bsangs mi bzad 'joms pa'i tshul //
NK009(ta)002:2825: de ltar 'khor sgyur gyi sras de skyes bzang yang
NK009(ta)002:2826: 'khor dang longs spyod med na rgyal por mi tshud
NK009(ta)002:2828: 'dir sras mchog kyang sku gsum gyi klong nas bskyed
NK009(ta)002:2829: kyang lha tshogs rdzas dang 'dra ba ma tshang na
NK009(ta)002:2831: lha tshogs kyang 'di la tshang dgos te /
NK009(ta)002:2832: ji ltar gsal zhing tshang ba'i tshul yang /
NK009(ta)002:2834: sku gcig ngang las dkyil 'khor thams cad rdzogs //
NK009(ta)002:2835: logs brgyad rang bzhin khro bo brgyad //
NK009(ta)002:2836: zur brgyad 'byung ba'i khro mo brgyad //
NK009(ta)002:2837: steng 'og lnga yi rang bzhin no //
NK009(ta)002:2838: zhes gsungs pa ltar dkyil 'khor thams cad 'di la tshang ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:2839: de ltar rgyal po de 'khor longs spyod dang ldan
NK009(ta)002:2840: yang gzi brjid chung na rgyal por mi tshud pa
NK009(ta)002:2841: ltar / sras mchog 'di la'ang phur pa'i lha tshogs
NK009(ta)002:2842: tshang yang de dag sku gsung thugs ye shes rtse
NK009(ta)002:2843: gcig tu ma brlabs na sras mchog mi 'gyur bas
NK009(ta)002:2844: ltar / / dbal gyi zur gsum la h'u gsum dang /
NK009(ta)002:2846: rtse mor a yig gis mtshan par gsal bas ye shes rtse gcig gi ngo bor gyur pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:2848: logs na phata gsum bzhag pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:2849: zur gsum h'u gsum bzhag pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:2851: de ltar rgyal po gzi brjid dang ldan yang rgyal
NK009(ta)002:2852: por dbang ma bskur na rgyal sar mi tshud pa
NK009(ta)002:2853: bzhin / sras mchog 'adi'ang rigs lngas dbang ma bskur na sras mchog tu mi 'gyur bas /
NK009(ta)002:2856: lag g.yas mthil du nyi dkyil las //
NK009(ta)002:2857: kun bzang 'od dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK009(ta)002:2858: g.yon gyi a las zla dkyil du //
NK009(ta)002:2859: kun tu bzang mo a las bskyed //
NK009(ta)002:2860: gung mo rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK009(ta)002:2861: mthe bong la ni mi bskyod pa //
NK009(ta)002:2862: mdzub mo'i rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK009(ta)002:2863: srin lag don yod grub pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:2864: mathe'u chung snang ba mtha' yas so //
NK009(ta)002:2865: g.yon pa lnga la yum lnga'o //
NK009(ta)002:2866: thabs dang shees rab snyoms 'jug dus //
NK009(ta)002:2867: sor mo cung zad bsnol bar bya //
NK009(ta)002:2868: phur pa 'dril bar bya ba yin //
NK009(ta)002:2869: ces gsungs pa ltar bdag nyid chen por dbang bskur
NK009(ta)002:2870: te rigs thams cad pa'i khro bor yang dbang bskur
NK009(ta)002:2871: ba bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor las sprul pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2872: khro bo'i zhal nas h'u phata kyi sgra dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:2873: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros te sras mchog
NK009(ta)002:2874: la thim par khams gsum dus gcig tu sgrol nus
NK009(ta)002:2875: pa'i mthu rtsal dang ldan par gyur pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2876: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid du dbang bskur ba'i
NK009(ta)002:2877: phyir chu srin rnam grol gyi phyag rgyas blangs la
NK009(ta)002:2878: / rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyi byang sems
NK009(ta)002:2879: las phyag mtshan phra mo grangs med pa spros te
NK009(ta)002:2880: sras mchog la thim pas bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon
NK009(ta)002:2881: nu dang sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya gnyis sku
NK009(ta)002:2882: gsum gcig tu gyur pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2883: de ltar rgyal por dbang bskur kyang bsod nams tshad
NK009(ta)002:2884: med pa dang mi ldan na rgyal por mi tshud
NK009(ta)002:2886: sras mchog 'adi'ang sku gsum du byin gyis brlab dgos pas /
NK009(ta)002:2887: rgyal ba thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bor byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2888: gzhan yang rgyal po de nyid dmag la chas pa'i tshe go cha bgo ba ltar /
NK009(ta)002:2889: sras mchog la yungs dkar nag gis brabs pas sku
NK009(ta)002:2890: lus thams cad khro chung gis go mtshams med par
NK009(ta)002:2891: gtams nas dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las la mngags pa
NK009(ta)002:2893: khros pa'i rgyal po bskul ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)002:2894: yungs kar byin brlabs khro chung bskyed //
NK009(ta)002:2896: yang rgyal po de dmag la chas pa na go
NK009(ta)002:2897: gyon pas ma tshad mtshon rnon po thogs dgos pa
NK009(ta)002:2898: bzhin / 'dir yang gu gul gyis bdug pas gdug
NK009(ta)002:2899: pa'i dpal dang ldan la mi bzad pa'i ngar dang
NK009(ta)002:2902: gu gul bdug cing yungs kar brdeg /
NK009(ta)002:2903: byin brlab dbang bskur shin tu gces //
NK009(ta)002:2905: yang rgyal po des mtshon rnon po dgra la thebs dgos pa dang mtshungs par /
NK009(ta)002:2906: 'dir yang rak+tasa byugs te phur bu dmar nag dud
NK009(ta)002:2907: ka reg pas 'joms pa gcig tu gsal ba ste
NK009(ta)002:2909: gdug pa brlag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)002:2910: ra khyi phag pa'i khrag gis byug /
NK009(ta)002:2912: yang rgyal po de phas kyi g.yul las rgyal te dgra'i yul mkhar thob dgos pa dang 'dra bar /
NK009(ta)002:2913: 'dir yang dgra bgegs kyi snying dkar nag mtshams su 'debs par bya ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:2915: gnad chen thams cad 'dus pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:2916: dkar nag mtshams su gdab par bya //
NK009(ta)002:2918: de ltar 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang rnam
NK009(ta)002:2919: grangs du ma'i sgo nas chos mtshungs pa'i sras mchog
NK009(ta)002:2920: de la grangs kyi sgo nas bud+d+ha /
NK009(ta)002:2924: karma ste lngar nges sam snyam na ma yin te /
NK009(ta)002:2925: sras mchog rab brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:2927: tha ma badz+ra 'dus pa gcig tu gsungs pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:2930: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya /
NK009(ta)002:2931: sras mchog ces kyang bya ste /
NK009(ta)002:2932: de la bsnyen phur ni bsnyen pa'i nus pa thams cad 'di la gsag pa'i phyir dang /
NK009(ta)002:2933: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor zhes pa nor longs
NK009(ta)002:2934: spyod mang du tshogs pa la spyi ming du rdzas
NK009(ta)002:2936: 'di la'ang lha dang byin rlabs thams cad 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)002:2937: sras mchog ces pa ni dpal chen po'i thugs las sprul pa'i sras yin pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2938: dkyil 'khor lus la rdzogs pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2939: phrin las thams cad byed pa'i mchog yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK009(ta)002:2940: gzhan rnams ni gtso bo mchog yin kyang sras ma yin zhing /
NK009(ta)002:2941: khro bo bcu sras yin kyang sras mchog ltar gyi
NK009(ta)002:2942: phrin las thams cad mi mdzad pas mchog ma yin
NK009(ta)002:2943: la / dam can rnams sras kyang ma yin /
NK009(ta)002:2944: mchog kyang ma yin pa'i phyir te /
NK009(ta)002:2946: rtsa ba'i thugs las bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK009(ta)002:2947: sgrol byed sras su bshad pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:2948: gdug pa can rnams 'dul ba la //
NK009(ta)002:2949: mngags pas mchog tu bshad pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:2950: phrin las kun rdzogs rgyal po ste //
NK009(ta)002:2951: sras mchog chen po zhes byar brjod //
NK009(ta)002:2953: de lta bu'i sras mchog de la shes par bya ba gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)002:2954: sras mchog gzhal yas khang du shes pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2958: rtse mo zur gsum nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum /
NK009(ta)002:2959: logs gsum zla gam rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:2960: rgya mdud 'og ma dang dbal gyi bar ni zlum po chu'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:2961: rgya mdud 'og ma gru bzhi sa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)002:2962: 'od dang 'od zer me'i dkyil 'khor te 'byung ba rim brtsegs dang /
NK009(ta)002:2963: rgya mdud gnyis kyi bar gyi gcum gzhogs brgyad 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:2964: rgya mdud gong ma rgya phibs sam bad kyi tshul du 'dug pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2966: dbus kyi khong seng du dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum /
NK009(ta)002:2967: gcum gzhogs brgyad la khro bo brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:2968: rgya mdud gong ma la h'u ka ra /
NK009(ta)002:2970: 'og ma'i logs bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:2971: zur bzhi la dam can gyi sde rnams so //
NK009(ta)002:2973: lha thams cad kyi phyag na phur pa re bsnams pa'ang sras mchog 'di kho na yin pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:2974: 'di kho na la'ang dkyil 'khor gsum rang bzhin gyis tshang ba nyid yin par gsungs so //
NK009(ta)002:2975: phur pa'i rnam gzhag la'ang gnyis te /
NK009(ta)002:2976: spyir gang zag rnam bzhi mthar dbyung bar byed pa phur bu'i rgyu bzhir dbye ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:2977: bye brag tu mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa cung zad phye ste bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:2981: bya ka lan+ta ka lta bu /
NK009(ta)002:2982: tsan+dana gyi sdong po lta bu'i gang zag bzhis rim pa bzhin rig pa ye shes kyi phur ba /
NK009(ta)002:2983: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:2984: byang chub sems kyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:2985: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa so sor nyams su blangs nas mthar dbyung ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:2986: de re re la'ang rten gyi gang zag /
NK009(ta)002:2992: 'bras bu ste de dag gi sgo nas shes par bya ba ni 'di'i srog gnad yin la /
NK009(ta)002:2993: 'di tshul gong du spyi'i don rnam par bzhag pa'i
NK009(ta)002:2994: sa bcad gsum pa'i skabs su cung zad bstan zin
NK009(ta)002:2995: la rgyas pa rgyud gzhung 'grel pa gzhan na shes
NK009(ta)002:2996: par bya'o // gnyis pa mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa bye brag tu bshad pa la drug ste /
NK009(ta)002:3005: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)002:3006: zhi ba chos kyi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)002:3007: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)002:3008: yon tan rgyas pa'i phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)002:3009: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)002:3010: gsung mchog dbang gi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)002:3011: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)002:3012: drag po las kyi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)002:3016: phur ni skye ba med pa'i dbyings //
NK009(ta)002:3017: pa ni 'gag pa med pa'i don //
NK009(ta)002:3018: phur ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK009(ta)002:3019: pa ni rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK009(ta)002:3020: gnyis su med pas mya ngan 'das //
NK009(ta)002:3021: sems kyi sems nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3022: chos kyi chos nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3023: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3024: gsal bar bsgoms na bskyed pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3025: gnyis su med na sbyor ba yin //
NK009(ta)002:3026: lhangs kyis rtogs na thebs pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3027: nyams 'og tshud na bsgral ba yin //
NK009(ta)002:3031: sor bzhi 'byung ba bzhi yi tshad //
NK009(ta)002:3032: sor brgyad rnam shes brgyad kyi tshad //
NK009(ta)002:3033: bcu gnyis skye mched bcu gnyis tshad //
NK009(ta)002:3034: bco brgyad tshad du bstan pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3035: khams ni bco brgyad 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK009(ta)002:3036: nas gang tshad du bstan pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3037: byang chub sems mchog tshad du bstan //
NK009(ta)002:3040: don dam gyi phur pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3043: phur pa'i don ni rig pa'i ye shes te //
NK009(ta)002:3044: de yi yul ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK009(ta)002:3047: lcags sna lnga dag shing sna bzhi'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:3049: sa lcags gnam lcags khro chu dang /
NK009(ta)002:3050: mi rta bsad pa'i mtshon rtse bzhi //
NK009(ta)002:3051: phal pa'i lcags dang lnga la bya //
NK009(ta)002:3055: rgya mdud gong ma chos sku ste //
NK009(ta)002:3056: gnyis pa longs spyod rdzogs pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3057: rtse mo sprul pa'i sku yin pas //
NK009(ta)002:3058: mgo dang rtsa ba ma nor bar //
NK009(ta)002:3059: zur gsum pa ru rnam par bzhog /
NK009(ta)002:3063: tsan+dana dkar po'i phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:3064: nad rnams ma lus zhi bar byed //
NK009(ta)002:3065: skyer pa'i phur pa zur bzhi yis //
NK009(ta)002:3066: tshe dang longs spyod rgyas par byed //
NK009(ta)002:3067: seng ldeng phur pa zla gam gyis //
NK009(ta)002:3068: thams cad dbang du sdud par byed //
NK009(ta)002:3069: bswe shing phur pas rigs rgyas byed //
NK009(ta)002:3070: gser gyis byang chub sems rgyas byed //
NK009(ta)002:3071: tsan+dana dmar po'i phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:3072: bu mo dbang du sdud par byed //
NK009(ta)002:3073: mdzo mos blon po dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)002:3074: bswe shing dmangs rigs dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)002:3075: zangs kyis rgyal po dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)002:3076: shing gis gdon rnams dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)002:3079: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK009(ta)002:3080: zhes sogs kyis bstan pa'i mthar thug phur bzhi'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3081: des sprul pa'i sku'i ngo bor phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor mdo tsam bstan zin te /
NK009(ta)002:3082: spyi don gnyis pa dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum sngon
NK009(ta)002:3083: du 'gro ba dang bcas pas don gyi khog dbub
NK009(ta)002:3084: pa tshar ro // spyi don gsum pa khams gsum
NK009(ta)002:3085: gyi srog la dbang bskur zhing srog gi ye shes
NK009(ta)002:3086: sems dpas srog la dbang bskur ba bshad pa la
NK009(ta)002:3087: pa tshar ro // gnyis / gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3090: thabs kyis spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK009(ta)002:3091: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK009(ta)002:3092: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs par mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:3093: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK009(ta)002:3095: 'di la rig 'dzin grub pa'i rgyal po rnam pa
