NK009(ta)002:3096: gsum gyi dgongs pa'i zur thams cad tshang bar mdo
NK009(ta)002:3097: tsam bsnyad na / sems can gyi don du thabs
NK009(ta)002:3098: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang thabs la mkhas pa
NK009(ta)002:3099: thams cad kyi spyod pas zin par bsam pa byams
NK009(ta)002:3100: tsam bsnyad na / pa dang / lag len snying rje ni spyir theg chen dang /
NK009(ta)002:3101: khyad par gsang sngags la gal che ba'i snying po gcig tu gyur pa'i phyir /
NK009(ta)002:3102: de lta bus khyad par du byas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi phrin las kyi ngo bor bskyed rdzogs /
NK009(ta)002:3103: nges tshig sangs rgyas kyi phrin las gang zag gi las su bya ba /
NK009(ta)002:3104: dbye ba phrin las bzhi dang /
NK009(ta)002:3105: yang na ma rig pa sangs shing ye shes rgyas pa la phrin las rdzogs par byas pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3106: zhi rgyas dbang drag gang 'dul gyi phrin las thams
NK009(ta)002:3107: cad rdzogs par mdzad pa'i don du phyi dbang snang
NK009(ta)002:3109: nang dbang snang srid sems su shes pa /
NK009(ta)002:3110: gsang dbang snang srid stong par rtogs par byin gyis
NK009(ta)002:3111: rlabs kyi phrin las rdzogs par stsol cig pa'i don
NK009(ta)002:3112: du spyir shes par bya zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3113: don dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum gyi srog la dbang
NK009(ta)002:3114: bskur bas sangs rgyas kyi phrin las thams cad rdzogs
NK009(ta)002:3115: pa des khams gsum gyi srog gam snying po la
NK009(ta)002:3116: thebs nas snang grags rig pa lha sngags bde ba
NK009(ta)002:3117: chen po'i rang bzhin nyid du 'char bas srog gi
NK009(ta)002:3118: ye shes sems dpa' gang gis srog gam snying po'i
NK009(ta)002:3120: rgyal ba kun gyi phrin las dus gcig tu sgrub
NK009(ta)002:3121: nus pa'i mthu dang dbang chen po brnyes pa'i phyir
NK009(ta)002:3123: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK009(ta)002:3124: de ltar gsol ba btab pa dang sangs rgyas rigs
NK009(ta)002:3125: lnga spyi bo'i thad du spyan drangs te gshegs pas
NK009(ta)002:3130: dbus nas ming gi dbang bskur ba dang bcas pa ni bum dbang /
NK009(ta)002:3131: rigs lnga yab yum gyi byang sems kyi rgyun bdag
NK009(ta)002:3132: gtso bo'i spyi bo nas zhugs te thim pa gsang
NK009(ta)002:3133: dbang / dbang lha thams cad 'od du 'dus te spyi bo nas thim pa sher dbang /
NK009(ta)002:3134: de'i dus kyi bde stong gi nyams rgyud la skyes pa dbang bzhi pa /
NK009(ta)002:3135: de nas rigs lnga cig car du yar log nas dbur brgyan pa ni dbang rtags so //
NK009(ta)002:3136: de lta bur gyur pa ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3137: dbang de lta bu'i ye shes s+pha ra na phata kyis khams gsum gyi sems can la phog /
NK009(ta)002:3138: de rnams rigs drug so so'i sa bon gyi ngo bor gyur /
NK009(ta)002:3139: de 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum gyis bsregs gtor sbyangs pas thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum gyi skur gyur /
NK009(ta)002:3140: de nas 'od kyi snang ba tshur 'dus sam ha
NK009(ta)002:3141: ra na h'u gis snying ga'i rta mgrin la 'dus
NK009(ta)002:3142: / dbang bskur bas bkrag dang gzi brjid dpal du 'bar ba ni des srog la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3143: des bskul te rta mgrin yab yum zag med bde
NK009(ta)002:3144: chen gyi rol pa'i byang sems ye shes sems dpa'
NK009(ta)002:3145: la thim nas dbang bskur bas de nyid bkrag dang
NK009(ta)002:3146: ldan par gyur pa'i gzi brjid ye shes kyi bcud
NK009(ta)002:3147: thams cad rdo rje'i lte ba'i thugs srog rnam par
NK009(ta)002:3148: mi rtog pa'i ye shes h'u yig la phog /
NK009(ta)002:3149: bkrag dang gzi mdangs 'od du 'bar ba ni ye shes sems dpas srog la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3150: de nas dkyil 'khor gsum gyi gnas gsum du sku
NK009(ta)002:3151: gsung thugs kyi ngo bo'i yig 'bru gsum gyi spro
NK009(ta)002:3152: bsdu las spyi bor rnam snang /
NK009(ta)002:3154: snying gar mi bskyod pas brgyan par gsal ba ni dbang gi rtags su bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:3155: 'di'i skabs srog ces pa la gnyug ma rang bzhin gyi srog /
NK009(ta)002:3159: mi ma yin pa so so'i srog yig sogs kyi rnam gzhag mang du 'byung yang /
NK009(ta)002:3160: skabs don 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs gnyis
NK009(ta)002:3161: su med pa'i ye shes kyis khams gsum gyi snod
NK009(ta)002:3162: bcud lha yis dkyil 'khor du srog gam snying po'i
NK009(ta)002:3164: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes srog gam snying po'i
NK009(ta)002:3165: tshul du bdag gi snying gar bzhugs pa'i srog gi
NK009(ta)002:3166: ye shes sems dpa' dpa' bo rta mgrin gyi rnam
NK009(ta)002:3167: par snang ba des thugs srog gi ngo bo la
NK009(ta)002:3168: mthu dang yon tan gzi brjid kyi mdangs rab tu
NK009(ta)002:3169: phyung ba la go bar bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:3170: spyi don bzhi pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan
NK009(ta)002:3171: drangs shing mchod cing bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud
NK009(ta)002:3176: 'khor ba phur bu bsgrub don du dbang dang byin rlabs stsol ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)002:3177: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)002:3178: ye shes khro bo gshegs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)002:3179: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3180: phur pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)002:3182: spyan 'dren gyi tshig 'di'i shugs las gzhan rnams kyang go dgos pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3183: srid pa'am 'khor ba'i khams kyi snod bcud dag dang
NK009(ta)002:3184: mnyam pa'i rang bzhin ma mthong ste tha mal rang
NK009(ta)002:3185: rgyud pa dang dngos po mtshan mar bzung bas sdug
NK009(ta)002:3186: bsngal rnam pa du mas sha thang chad pa 'di
NK009(ta)002:3187: dag / ye gdod ma nas rnam par dag pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3188: phur pa mnyam yangs gdal ba chen po chos sku
NK009(ta)002:3189: thig le nyag gcig gi rnam rol las rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:3190: gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor rnam gsum sku gsum gyi bdag
NK009(ta)002:3191: nyid chen por bsgrub pa'i phyir ram don du /
NK009(ta)002:3192: khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur zhing srog gi
NK009(ta)002:3193: ye shes sems dpas srog la dbang bskur bas stong
NK009(ta)002:3194: srog chos sku'i klong du dbyer med chen por 'pho
NK009(ta)002:3195: 'gyur gzhom zhig med par gnyug ma don gyi srog
NK009(ta)002:3196: pa rtsa myur du tshugs pa'i dbang dang byin rlabs
NK009(ta)002:3197: kyi rim pa ma lus pa zhu ba'am stsol ba'i
NK009(ta)002:3198: phyir du / dbyings dang gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK009(ta)002:3199: shes kyi rol pa'i khro rgyal chen po gnas 'dir
NK009(ta)002:3200: ma thogs myur ba'i thugs rje'i shugs kyis gshegs su
NK009(ta)002:3201: phyir du / gsol na / ye shes pa'i khro
NK009(ta)002:3202: bo chen po gshegs nas kyang dngos nyams rmi lam
NK009(ta)002:3203: gyi rtags dang mtshan ma bzang pos ye shes kyi
NK009(ta)002:3204: khro bo grub pa'i mtshon byed du bstan pa dang
NK009(ta)002:3205: phyir du / gsol na / / phur pa'i dngos
NK009(ta)002:3206: grub ma lus pa mchog dang thun mong gi tshul
NK009(ta)002:3207: du stsal bar mdzad du gsol zhes dam tshig gi
NK009(ta)002:3208: 'khor los 'og min na bzhugs pa'i ye shes kyi
NK009(ta)002:3211: ye shes pa spyan drang ba /
NK009(ta)002:3212: de la mchod pa brgyad dbul ba /
NK009(ta)002:3214: bstod cing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3216: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka'i 'od kyis 'og min chos
NK009(ta)002:3217: kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas rang dang mtshungs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3218: dkyil 'khor gsum mdun mkhar spyan drang ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3219: gnyis pa de la mchod pa dbul ba la brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:3227: tshogs dang bstod pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3229: nam mkhar bzhugs par gsal ba'i ye shes pa la a ti pu hoh sa phyag btsal ba la /
NK009(ta)002:3230: ye shes pas pra ti dza hohzhesa lan du dngos grub kyi bcud stsol ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3231: gnyis pa bstims nas lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pa la /
NK009(ta)002:3232: sgo bzhi'i yi ges dgug gzhug bcing myos kyi bya ba byas te dam ye bsre ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3233: de'i 'bru don cung zad bshad na /
NK009(ta)002:3234: gang nas spyan drang na 'og min nas spyan drang /
NK009(ta)002:3235: gang du na ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sgrub gnas dang bcas par drang /
NK009(ta)002:3236: sgrub pa'i gnas kyang drag po'i dbang du byas nas kha ral srin po'i gnas /
NK009(ta)002:3238: drag po gnod sbyin gyi gnas /
NK009(ta)002:3240: dur khrod ma mo mkha' 'gro'i gnas sogs mang du gsungs kyang /
NK009(ta)002:3241: 'dir rnal 'byor pa sgrub pa gang du byed pa'i gnas de nyid du'o //
NK009(ta)002:3242: gang gis spyan drang na dam tshig pas /
NK009(ta)002:3243: gang spyan drang na dkyil 'khor gsum gyi ye shes pa rnams drang ba yin /
NK009(ta)002:3244: dgos pa 'khor ba gsum mam srid pa gsum gyi
NK009(ta)002:3245: sems can thams cad rdo rje phur bu bsgrub pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3246: phyir dang / dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i don du spyan drang /
NK009(ta)002:3247: dbang gang len na rtogs pa chos nyid kyi dbang /
NK009(ta)002:3250: drag po las kyi dbang rnams blang ba'i don du'o //
NK009(ta)002:3251: dngos grub ci len na rab sangs rgyas /
NK009(ta)002:3253: tha ma mig sman la sogs pa'am /
NK009(ta)002:3254: yang na 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub blang ba'i phyir du yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3255: spyan drangs bya'i lha de dag la ye shes khro bo zhes pa'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK009(ta)002:3256: ye shes ni ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3257: de dang ldan pa ni ye shes pa /
NK009(ta)002:3258: khro bo ni rngam zhing brjid pa ste ye shes
NK009(ta)002:3259: pa yin la khro bo ma yin pa zhi ba'i
NK009(ta)002:3261: ye shes pa min pa la khro bo yin pa bdud dang srin po lta bu dang /
NK009(ta)002:3262: ye shes pa'ang ma yin la khro bo'ang ma yin
NK009(ta)002:3263: pa rigs drug gi sems can lta bu ni 'dir
NK009(ta)002:3265: ye shes kyang yin la khroo bo'ang yin pa rdo
NK009(ta)002:3266: rje gzhon nu phrin las phur pa rol pa'i lha
NK009(ta)002:3267: tshogs rnams spyan 'dren pa yin pas na 'di dag
NK009(ta)002:3268: la ye shes khro bo zhes 'jog cing /
NK009(ta)002:3269: spyan drangs nas byed las gang byed na rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa'i byed las mdzad de /
NK009(ta)002:3271: 'bring phur bu nam mkhar lding ba /
NK009(ta)002:3276: mtshan ma ni mi rtog pa'i ye shes skye ba
NK009(ta)002:3277: rnams yin par gsungs pa'i gnad 'di dag 'di tsam
NK009(ta)002:3278: du ma zad spyir go ba gal che'o //
NK009(ta)002:3279: gsum pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3280: dam tshig chen pos gtso bo dang /
NK009(ta)002:3281: sprul pa chen pos phyogs bcu khro bo la /
NK009(ta)002:3282: phyag brnyan chen mos mgo brnyan nyi shu la /
NK009(ta)002:3283: shwa na'am khyi'i gdong can gyis shwa na bzhi la /
NK009(ta)002:3284: bdag nyid chen mos re ma til /
NK009(ta)002:3285: sa bdag gis bswe mo bzhi la /
NK009(ta)002:3286: khyed kyi dam tshig gis ling ga dbul ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3287: bzhi pa sman mchod la lnga ste /
NK009(ta)002:3288: sman gyi che ba brjod pa /
NK009(ta)002:3292: smon lam ste don de dag gis snang srid bdud rtsi dag pas dgyes pa bskyed pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3293: lnga pa rak+ta tshar gsum ni //
NK009(ta)002:3294: dang po bka' nyan par byed pa'i don du 'bul /
NK009(ta)002:3295: gnyis pa dam can gnad la dbab pa'i phyir du 'bul /
NK009(ta)002:3296: gsum pa mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i ched du 'bul ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3297: gzhan yang dug lnga dug gsum gyi mchod pa rnams kyang shugs las shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:3298: drug pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3299: sbyor ba khro bo yab yum rnams snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3300: sgrol ba ni dgra bgegs bsgral ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:3301: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun
NK009(ta)002:3302: dang tho bas dgra bgegs bkug cing rol pa'i stabs
NK009(ta)002:3303: kyis rdung / byang sems me lces sreg /
NK009(ta)002:3304: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gi ngo bo sha
NK009(ta)002:3305: khrag rus gsum lhag med du gtso 'khor sprul pa
NK009(ta)002:3306: yang sprul dang bcas pa'i zhal du sbyor bas thugs
NK009(ta)002:3307: rgyud mnyes pa'i bzhad sgra dang bcas te tha mal
NK009(ta)002:3308: pa'i 'dod chags zhe sdang gi sa bon dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:3309: pa rtsad nas brlag pa ni 'di'i ngo bo'o //
NK009(ta)002:3310: bdun pa 'dod don gsol gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3311: dam tshig chen po'i sogs kyis bstan don /
NK009(ta)002:3312: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis byang chub sgrub pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3313: bdud dang bar gcod gnyis 'dzin log par rtog pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3314: 'khrul pa'i rang gzugs kyi snang ba thams cad dbyings
NK009(ta)002:3315: su thim nas / nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lngar dag /
NK009(ta)002:3316: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las 'das pa'i sdig can
NK009(ta)002:3317: gnod par byed pa rnams kyi khong nas me 'bar
NK009(ta)002:3318: ba'i bka' 'das kyi chad pa drag pos mnar ba
NK009(ta)002:3319: chos nyid bzhin sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod
NK009(ta)002:3320: cig / rig pa 'dzin pa'i sgrub pa po rnams
NK009(ta)002:3321: la mchog thun dngos grub kyi dbyig mi zad pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3322: gter chen po'i gru char kyi dpyid 'jo bas don
NK009(ta)002:3323: gnyis lhun gyis grub par mdzod cig ces bskul ba
NK009(ta)002:3324: cig / ste / 'di la'ang gu ru gsum gyi
NK009(ta)002:3325: dgongs pas mang du bshad kyang don mdor bsdus pa'o
NK009(ta)002:3326: cig / ste / // de nas dkyil 'khor gsum
NK009(ta)002:3327: gyi lha tshogs de dag gi che ba'i yon tan
NK009(ta)002:3328: brjod byar byas pa'i rjod byed kyi glu dbyangs snyan
NK009(ta)002:3329: cing brjid la zil che zhing byin chags pa'i bstod
NK009(ta)002:3330: pa he ru ka lhag par dgyes pa'i dpal chen
NK009(ta)002:3331: rngams pa'i sgra dbyangs lce rkan byed rtsol gyi 'du
NK009(ta)002:3332: shes las 'das pa'i rang byung n+aa da mi shigs
NK009(ta)002:3333: pa'i rang sgrar gsal bas kyang dgyes pa bskyed do
NK009(ta)002:3334: cig / ste / // // brgyad pa bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud blang ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:3335: bsnyen dzapa ste de la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:3340: dam tshig bzhir dbye ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3341: bar du dzapa bzla ba la /
NK009(ta)002:3345: de re re la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las ltar bzla ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:3346: 'di dag gi rnam gzhag rgyas par 'grel ba dang gzhan na gsal bas 'dir bsdus so //
NK009(ta)002:3348: bzlas grangs rdzogs pa dang stong tshig gi mchod bstod dbul ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3349: brgyad pa tshogs kyi mchod pa ga na tsakra'i cho ga la brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:3358: dang po tshogs pa gsum ni /
NK009(ta)002:3361: 'byor ldan longs spyod kyi tshogs so //
NK009(ta)002:3362: de'ang dang po lha mthun pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3363: gnyis pa dam tshig rtsa ba gcig pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3364: gsum pa yo byad gya nom pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3365: gnyis pa gsag pa gsum ni /
NK009(ta)002:3366: gnas dur khrod lta bur grub thob kyi bla ma gsag /
NK009(ta)002:3367: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i rnal 'byor gyi pho mo gsag /
NK009(ta)002:3368: 'dod yon lnga'i longs spyod gsag pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3373: bzhi pa sbyang ba gsum ni /
NK009(ta)002:3374: ram yam kham gi sa bon las byung ba'i me rlung chus dme btsog sbyang ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3376: h'u +aah gsum zhu thim pa las bdud rtsi'i rang
NK009(ta)002:3377: bzhin sngo dmar dkar ba'i mdangs ldan du brlab pa'o
NK009(ta)002:3379: mchod pa'i dus su 'dod yon lnga /
NK009(ta)002:3380: bshags pa'i dus su ye shes lnga /
NK009(ta)002:3381: bstab pa'i dus su dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag don snying du gsal ba'am shes pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3383: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams dang /
NK009(ta)002:3384: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang /
NK009(ta)002:3385: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro rnams la dbul lo //
NK009(ta)002:3390: mi 'bral ba gsum bshad pa sogs gzhan na gsal zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3393: bgegs bskrad byin brlab spyan drangs dang //
NK009(ta)002:3394: mchod dang bskang dang bzlog pa dag /
NK009(ta)002:3395: stod kyi las su shes par bya //
NK009(ta)002:3396: bstab dang dbul ba bshags pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3397: smon lam rgya chen gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3398: smad kyi las su shes par bya //
NK009(ta)002:3399: ces bshad pa ltar lag tu len cing /
NK009(ta)002:3400: rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos zas lhag bsdus te byin
NK009(ta)002:3401: gyis brlabs nas sgo drung nyul ba'i 'byung po lhag
NK009(ta)002:3402: sdud ging lang 'bar ma dbang phyug sogs la bka'i
NK009(ta)002:3403: pham phab kyi tshul du btang nas zab mo'i smon
NK009(ta)002:3404: lam dang rdo rje'i glus rig pa gzengs bstod pa
NK009(ta)002:3405: sogs lag len las kyi byang bu dang sgom don
NK009(ta)002:3408: de ltar na de dag ni /
NK009(ta)002:3410: sa man dzahya zhes gsol bas //
NK009(ta)002:3411: phyag rgya bzhi yis spyan yang drang //
NK009(ta)002:3413: dgyes pa chen pos phyag btsal zhing //
NK009(ta)002:3414: mchod pa'i rim pa sngon 'byung bzhin //
NK009(ta)002:3415: des ni las rnams ma lus 'grub //
NK009(ta)002:3417: gzhan yang gsang sngags rnying ma spyi'i 'gros su dam
NK009(ta)002:3418: can srung ma spyi dang bye brag la phrin las
NK009(ta)002:3419: gzhol ba'i gtang rag phud dang gtor ma dbul ba
NK009(ta)002:3420: / rtsa gsum rab 'byams dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lha
NK009(ta)002:3421: tshogs la thugs rje'i thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba
NK009(ta)002:3422: / / bka' dang dam la gnas pa'i rgyud gsum
NK009(ta)002:3423: dregs pa'i tshogs la bka'i chad tho'i tha tshig bsgrag
NK009(ta)002:3424: / / pa / bood yul mtha' dbus kyi so
NK009(ta)002:3425: kha bsrung zhing mtha' bzhi'i kla klo gdug pa'i rgyu
NK009(ta)002:3426: lam bkag par snang srid zil gnon mtsho skyes rgyal
NK009(ta)002:3427: bas bka' bsgos pa bdud dang gnod sbyin sman mo'i
NK009(ta)002:3428: tshul du snang ba'i brtan ma chen mo bcu gnyis
NK009(ta)002:3429: la sngon gyi tha tshig gnyan po bskul ba'i las
NK009(ta)002:3430: kyi gnyer zan du bshal chu'i bdud rtsis stob pa
NK009(ta)002:3432: dang dam sri gtor gzhong ri rab tu gsal ba'i
NK009(ta)002:3433: 'og tu ldang med mnan pa'i rgyas gdab pa /
NK009(ta)002:3434: dngos grub rnam gnyis kyi bcud blang ba /
NK009(ta)002:3435: dkyil 'khor la slar yang mchod cing bstod pa /
NK009(ta)002:3438: bskyed rim gyi dkyil 'khor rtags mtha' bsal phyir 'od gsal du bsdu zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3439: chad mtha' spang phyir lha'i skur ldang ba /
NK009(ta)002:3440: dge tshogs gzhan don du theg pa chen po'i bsngo ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3441: zab rgyas kyi don la smon lam bzang por brgyan pa /
NK009(ta)002:3442: shis pa'i tshig gi dbyangs snyan sa gsum du khyab
NK009(ta)002:3443: par spel bas dge legs gong 'phel du byed pa
NK009(ta)002:3444: rnams cho ga'i mjug don du 'ong ba yin mod
NK009(ta)002:3445: / 'dir rgyud don 'dir rgyud don rgyud ltar 'chad
NK009(ta)002:3446: pa skabs su bab pas bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i rtsa
NK009(ta)002:3447: ba rdo rje'i tshig gis dngos shugs su bstan pa
NK009(ta)002:3448: tsam tshig nyung ngus bkral ba'i skabs su de dag
NK009(ta)002:3449: smos pa'i spros pa ma byas la /
NK009(ta)002:3450: zhib par 'jam mgon a mes zhabs kyi dkyil chog rnam bshad dang /
NK009(ta)002:3451: gzhan yang sgom don phrin las kyi rim pa rnams su 'byung ba ltar ro //
NK009(ta)002:3452: de dag gi sgo nas rgyud kyi thems sbyar bcu'i sa bcad dang po /
NK009(ta)002:3455: khog don drug gi nang nas sa bcad bzhi ste
NK009(ta)002:3456: bdun gyis stod las byang chub sgrub pa'i dum bu
NK009(ta)002:3457: dngos shugs kyi tshul du cung zad bshad zin to
NK009(ta)002:3459: // // dus mtha'i me dpung bye bas mi skrun pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:3460: mthu rtsal gzi ldan rdzas kyi phur bu yis //
NK009(ta)002:3461: brnag pa'i dgra dang bgegs la thebs pa'i mod //
NK009(ta)002:3462: phur bzhi'i dgongs pa rtol byed mngon spyod che //
NK009(ta)002:3463: mthu stobs rdo rje'i thog chen gyis //
NK009(ta)002:3464: gdug pa'i snying la bsnun pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:3466: sngags shes rnams kyis ci mi skor /
NK009(ta)002:3467: da ni mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur bu brnag pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3468: dgra bgegs la gdab pa'i rim pa smad las drag
NK009(ta)002:3469: po sgrol ba'i dum bu nyid 'chad par byed pa
NK009(ta)002:3470: la gnyis / spyi don rnam par gzhag pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3474: gang gis sgrol byed slob dpon /
NK009(ta)002:3475: tshul ji ltar bsgral ba'i thabs /
NK009(ta)002:3480: nyams pa bdun dang ldan pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3483: phur bu myang 'das kyi rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:3484: srog don bka' dam las kyis nyams //
NK009(ta)002:3485: mtshan mas nyams par 'gyur ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:3487: bsgral ba'i dmigs kyi dam par bshad //
NK009(ta)002:3489: de dag so so'i mtshan nyid kyang /
NK009(ta)002:3491: de yi so so'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK009(ta)002:3492: pha ma mkhan po slob dpon gsod //
NK009(ta)002:3493: rdo rje nang dme byed pa dag /
NK009(ta)002:3494: nam yang dmyal bar ltung byed pas //
NK009(ta)002:3495: bsgral ba'i dmigs ni dam pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3496: srog las nyams pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:3497: slob dpon bka' bslu ngan dpya sems //
NK009(ta)002:3498: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun gcod dang //
NK009(ta)002:3499: gsang ba'i man ngag spel byed na //
NK009(ta)002:3500: de yang bsgral ba'i dam pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3501: don las log pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:3505: de yang bsgral ba'i dam pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3506: bka' las log pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:3507: bya ru mi rung sna tshogs byed //
NK009(ta)002:3508: rdzas dang lag cha mngon par ston //
NK009(ta)002:3509: sbyor sgrol phrin las 'chol bar spyod //
NK009(ta)002:3510: lta ba chos nyid rgyab tu 'dor //
NK009(ta)002:3511: log pa'i spyod pa dang du len //
NK009(ta)002:3512: nga rgyal gtum khro rang gar gtong //
NK009(ta)002:3513: man ngag don bstan log par go //
NK009(ta)002:3514: pha rol don la log chos spyod //
NK009(ta)002:3515: don ni phyin ci log la mkhas //
NK009(ta)002:3516: bka' gzhung bor nas log par brtsams //
NK009(ta)002:3517: spyod pas log pa mtha' dag byed //
NK009(ta)002:3518: ru dra dngos ka de yin te //
NK009(ta)002:3519: dngos su bsgral yang mi skyon no //
NK009(ta)002:3521: 'dod pas nyams pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:3522: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pa'i don 'dir mdor bsdu na /
NK009(ta)002:3523: dang po srog las nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3524: rang gi pha ma mkhan po slob dpon rnams gsod pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3525: rdo rje spun gyi nang du dme byas pa rnams yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3526: gnyis pa don las nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3527: gong du bshad pa'i yul de dag la skur pa 'debs pa'i gzhi byed pa /
NK009(ta)002:3531: bka' phyin ci log tu dkrugs pa la mkhas pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3532: gsum pa bka' las nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3533: gsang sngags tshul bzhin du spyod pa la 'khu ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3537: 'khor rnams log par 'khrid pa sogs yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3538: bzhi pa dam las nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3539: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bka' bslus te ngan sems byed pa /
NK009(ta)002:3540: gsang sngags dang phyag rgya'i rgyun gcod pa /
NK009(ta)002:3541: gsang chos rgyud ma smin pa la spel ba rnams yin par bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:3542: lnga pa las kyis nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3543: las kyis sngon chad mkhon pa'i gzhi med par nyes
NK009(ta)002:3544: med gzhan la rgol zhing bzhin bzlog par bdag gis
NK009(ta)002:3545: nyes pa ma bstan yang bdag la mthu rtsal gyis
NK009(ta)002:3546: 'debs par byed pa rnams yin zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3547: drug pa mtshan mas nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3548: gnyis med don la phyogs char 'dzin pa /
NK009(ta)002:3549: sgro skur gnyis kyis ras chod byed pa /
NK009(ta)002:3550: skye med kyi chos la mtshan mar gzung ba /
NK009(ta)002:3551: lha srin ma lus pa bran du ma 'khol bzhin
NK009(ta)002:3552: nga nyid dpal chen po yin no zhes 'jig rten
NK009(ta)002:3553: blun po rnams bslu ba'i rdzun chen po smra ba
NK009(ta)002:3554: / gzhan la khro zhing 'tshe bar byed pa rnams yin par gsungs /
NK009(ta)002:3555: bdun pa 'dod pas nyams pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3556: shes rab rnam gsum gyi rtsal med par mthu stsal
NK009(ta)002:3557: chen por 'dod pas las kyi gtso bo mtshan mar
NK009(ta)002:3558: spyod pa / 'jig rten las ma 'das pa'i lha
NK009(ta)002:3559: 'dre la gsol ba btab cing rang gi gdong khrag
NK009(ta)002:3560: gis byugs pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas spyod pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3562: mi 'tshams pa'i spyod ngan tho co barlanga por spyod
NK009(ta)002:3563: pas bka' dang gzhung lugs smad nas bza' btung 'dod
NK009(ta)002:3564: pas sgrub pa'i longs spyod brku ba rnams yin par
NK009(ta)002:3565: bshad do // gzhan yang khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:3566: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3567: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smad pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3569: theg chen chos la smod pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3570: bla ma'i sku la bsdo ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:3571: rdo rje'i nang dbyen byed pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3572: sgrub la bar chad byed pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3573: gang zhig dam las log pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3574: snying rje med pa'i srin po dang //
NK009(ta)002:3575: mu stegs log ltar gtong ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:3576: sgrub pa po la do bsdo ba //
NK009(ta)002:3577: 'di rnams bsgral ba'i zhing bcu yin //
NK009(ta)002:3578: zhes gsungs pa ltar bya ba ma yin par barlanga
NK009(ta)002:3579: por spyod pa'i las ngan can gyi bsgral ba'i zhing
NK009(ta)002:3580: du gyur pa rnam pa bcur gsungs pa de dag
NK009(ta)002:3581: ste / gdul bya gdug pa can rnams mngon spyod
NK009(ta)002:3582: kyi sgo nas bsgral te srog 'phrog par bya ba
NK009(ta)002:3583: ni sngags kyi phrin las thams cad kyi nang na
NK009(ta)002:3584: phul du byung ba yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3585: rgyu mtshan thugs rje'i dpyang thag gis gzung zhing sngags
NK009(ta)002:3586: kyi phrin las 'jug pa'i yul sems can gyi ris
NK009(ta)002:3591: las nyon srab cing dkon mchog la gus pa rnams
NK009(ta)002:3592: ni chos bstan pa sogs thugs rje zhi ba'i thabs
NK009(ta)002:3593: kyis thar ba'i gnas su bsgral ba'i skal pa dang
NK009(ta)002:3594: ldan pa yin pas gdul bar sla zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3595: gnyis pa 'dir bstan gyi mtshan nyid can las nyon
NK009(ta)002:3596: shugs drag pos rang dbang med par mnar ba gang
NK009(ta)002:3597: zhig dkon mchog gsum la rgyab kyis phyogs shing bstan
NK009(ta)002:3598: pa dang sems can la rnam pa kun tu gnod
NK009(ta)002:3599: pa / zhi ba'i thabs gang gis kyang 'dul bar mi nus pa /
NK009(ta)002:3600: bla med rgyud sde ltar na rdo rje dmyal ba'am /
NK009(ta)002:3601: phar phyin dang thun mong ba ltar na mnar med
NK009(ta)002:3602: pa'i sems can dmyal ba chen po sogs ngan song
NK009(ta)002:3603: gi 'gro bar shin tu mu mtha' med par 'khyams
NK009(ta)002:3604: pa de dag ni drag po'i shugs kyis sgrol ba'i
NK009(ta)002:3605: phrin las 'jug pa'i yul khyad par can yin no
NK009(ta)002:3606: // gnyis pa gang gis sgrol byed slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK009(ta)002:3607: spyir gong du phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i dang po
NK009(ta)002:3608: bdag nyid dam ston pa phun tshogs kyi mtshan nyid
NK009(ta)002:3609: bshad pa'i skabs su bstan pa thams cad tshang bar
NK009(ta)002:3610: dgos shing / bye brag lta ba'i rdzong zin cing
NK009(ta)002:3611: sgom pa'i 'phrang chod la spyod pa'i srog zin pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3612: sgo nas rtogs pas bdag bsgral bar byas nas /
NK009(ta)002:3613: de'i 'og tu las ngan gyi gdul bya la snying rje chen po mtshungs pa med pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3614: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i shes rab chen po
NK009(ta)002:3615: phul du byung ba'i stobs kyis thugs rjes gzhan sgrol
NK009(ta)002:3616: ba dang du len pa'i mtshan nyid rdzogs pa med
NK009(ta)002:3617: thabs med pas / de'ang gzhi'i sems zhes ma bcos
NK009(ta)002:3618: spros med chos sku'i dgongs pa zang thal khyab gdal
NK009(ta)002:3619: thig le nyag gcig 'od gsal nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK009(ta)002:3620: dgongs pa phar phyin ltar na zab mo dbu ma'i
NK009(ta)002:3621: lta ba rnam par dag pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3622: sngags bla med ltar na phyag rdzogs kyi ye shes e wam dang /
NK009(ta)002:3623: bde chen gyi sgras bstan pa'i don la goms pa
NK009(ta)002:3624: brtan por gyur pas chos thams cad gdod nas dbyer
NK009(ta)002:3625: med pa mnyam pa chen po'i don du mthong bas
NK009(ta)002:3626: 'khor gsum dmigs med sgyu ma'i rnam 'phrul lta bu
NK009(ta)002:3627: nges pa'i gdeng dang ldan cing /
NK009(ta)002:3628: stangs kyi sems zhes don dam dmigs mtha' dang bral
NK009(ta)002:3629: ba'i dgongs klong dang dbyer med pa'i ngang nas rnam
NK009(ta)002:3630: pa kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje'i rtsal
NK009(ta)002:3631: mdangs shugs drag ma 'gags pa'i tshul du lham mer
NK009(ta)002:3632: 'char bas gdug cig gtum pa'i gdul bya las ngan
NK009(ta)002:3633: pa'i rnam par smin pa'i rgyus 'bras bu ngan 'gro
NK009(ta)002:3634: mtha' med pa'i 'khor bar bzod du med pa'i duhkha'i
NK009(ta)002:3635: me 'bar ba'i rum na thar dus med pa de
NK009(ta)002:3636: la gzhig nas shas mi bzod pa'i byams pa dang
NK009(ta)002:3637: snying rje'i gzhan dbang las de la phan pa'i thabs
NK009(ta)002:3638: ni zhi bas 'dul du ma 'tshal bar dpa' zhing
NK009(ta)002:3639: gtum pa'i zhe sdang gi rnam pa'i thabs drag pos
NK009(ta)002:3640: btsan thabs gdong nas bzlog ste spyi bor thog lhung
NK009(ta)002:3641: ba lta bu'i drag shul mngon spyod kyi thabs mkhas
NK009(ta)002:3642: zab mos myur du gnas ngan las bsgral te zhi
NK009(ta)002:3643: ba'i lam la bkod 'dod kyi bsam pa rang 'khris
NK009(ta)002:3644: kyi dri mas ma reg pas bskul te /
NK009(ta)002:3645: drag po mngon spyod kyi las la 'jug pa de'i
NK009(ta)002:3646: tshe rnam pa zhe sdang gi sems gdug cing rtsub
NK009(ta)002:3647: pa dus mtha'i me dpung 'bar ba'i lce glal ba
NK009(ta)002:3649: ngo bo snying rje chen pos gdangs lam mer shar
NK009(ta)002:3650: bas gnas skabs mthar thug tu gzhan phan gyi bsam
NK009(ta)002:3651: pa bzang po mas bu gces pa gcig pu la
NK009(ta)002:3652: ci 'dra ba de 'dra zhig gi gnas la shin
NK009(ta)002:3653: tu goms pa'i mtshan nyid ni byang chub kyi sems
NK009(ta)002:3654: rin po che rnam pa gnyis zhes spyir theg pa
NK009(ta)002:3655: chen po'i lam gyi snying po yin pas rang gzhan
NK009(ta)002:3656: gi don sgrub par byed pa la med thabs med
NK009(ta)002:3657: cing / khyad par gsang sngags rdo rjee theg pa'i lam nas bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen /
NK009(ta)002:3659: bskyed bzlas rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK009(ta)002:3660: gi las rab 'byams ci lta bu zhig la 'jug
NK009(ta)002:3661: kyang de lta bu'i sems kyis zin na ci byas
NK009(ta)002:3662: lam du 'gyur zhing rang gzhan gyi don gnyis dka'
NK009(ta)002:3664: gzhan du zhe sdang rang rgyud pas sngags kyi mngon
NK009(ta)002:3665: spyod sogs gsang ba zab mo'i spyod pa rang dgar
NK009(ta)002:3666: spyad pas rang gzhan phung la sbyor ba'i ru dra
NK009(ta)002:3667: 'ba' zhig yin par sgrol byed slob dpon gyi mtshan
NK009(ta)002:3668: nyid gtso bo 'di dag tu 'dus pa yin la
NK009(ta)002:3669: / de'ang mdun du rang gi sems kyis sprul pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3670: dmigs bya gsal ba de'i lag pa nas bzung ste
NK009(ta)002:3672: yul dngos kyi lag pa nas bzung ste bsad pa
NK009(ta)002:3673: gnyis la khyad yod par 'dzin pa'i kun rtog yod
NK009(ta)002:3674: kyi ring la bsgral kyang rnam smin yod la /
NK009(ta)002:3675: de gnyis ka sems kyi snang ba tsam du khyad
NK009(ta)002:3676: med pas bsgral kyang sgyu ma mig yor gyi tshul
NK009(ta)002:3677: du yang spu tsam mi skye ba'i tshe na bsgral
NK009(ta)002:3678: kyang las kyi 'bras bu rang gi khur du mi
NK009(ta)002:3679: 'gyur bas / rtogs tshad de lta bu dang ldan
NK009(ta)002:3680: par bya ba la don dam byang chub kyi sems
NK009(ta)002:3681: dmigs pa kun dang bral ba'i nam mkha'i dkyil shin
NK009(ta)002:3682: tu dag pa lta bu dang /
NK009(ta)002:3683: de lta bu'i sgrol ba lam du 'gyur ba la
NK009(ta)002:3684: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems te zung du 'jug
NK009(ta)002:3685: pa'i gding dang ldan pa zhig dgos pa'i gal gnad
NK009(ta)002:3686: che ba'i rgyu mtshan de ltar yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3687: tshad dang ldan pa'i sgrol byed kyi slob dpon de
NK009(ta)002:3688: lta bus gdul dka' ba'i yul la thugs rje'i dpyang
NK009(ta)002:3690: gsang sngags thabs mkhas pa'i cho 'phrul gyi sgo nas
NK009(ta)002:3691: rjes su 'dzin pa'i thabs shes gnyis ka phul du
NK009(ta)002:3692: byung ba sgrol ba 'di la yod pa'i phyir ro
NK009(ta)002:3693: // gzhan sgrol byed kyi mtshan nyid bye bsdu phra zhib mang du gsungs pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:3694: de ltar mngon spyod zab mo'i thabs mkhas la gding
NK009(ta)002:3695: dang ldan pa'i slob dpon de nyid kyis tshar gcod
NK009(ta)002:3696: rjes su 'dzin pa'i drag shul dpa' bo rol pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3697: spyod pa 'jigs med seng ge'i brtul zhugs kyis nye
NK009(ta)002:3698: bar spyod pa de'i tshe drag po'i brtul zhugs kyi
NK009(ta)002:3699: chas dang yo byad sogs kyang /
NK009(ta)002:3701: sngags pa rgyan gyi chas kyi rdzas //
NK009(ta)002:3702: glang chen ko rlon zhing gi shun //
NK009(ta)002:3703: stag gi sham bu sbrul gyi rgyan //
NK009(ta)002:3704: thal chen zhag dang rak+tasa brgyan //
NK009(ta)002:3705: zhes sogs chas dang yo byad kyi dgos pa'i rdzas
NK009(ta)002:3706: nye bar bsdogs te 'jigs shing yang ba'i rngam zil
NK009(ta)002:3707: gyi gzi brjid cher 'bar bar bya ba'ang tshul 'dir
NK009(ta)002:3708: nye bar 'os pa'i yan lag go //
NK009(ta)002:3709: gsum pa tshul ji ltar sgrol ba'i thabs ni /
NK009(ta)002:3710: spyir phur bu bzhis gang zag rnam pa bzhi mthar
NK009(ta)002:3711: dbyung ba nyid sgrol ba'i thabs kyi rtsa ba yin
NK009(ta)002:3712: kyang / skabs 'dir mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur bu
NK009(ta)002:3713: yul dgra bgegs la gdab pa nyid gtso bor bstan
NK009(ta)002:3714: pa'i shugs las phur bu gzhan gsum po'i dgongs pa'ang
NK009(ta)002:3715: zhar byung du 'jug pa shes par bya dgos pas
NK009(ta)002:3717: tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:3718: sgrol byed kyi phur gdab dngos /
NK009(ta)002:3719: gab pa'i sngags drug bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3721: dmigs pa'i rten la gzas pa po dgug cing lha dang dbye la drag po'i thun dbab //
NK009(ta)002:3722: snying ga'i dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi srog 'phrog ste
NK009(ta)002:3723: las ngan gyi bag chags thams cad ye shes kyi
NK009(ta)002:3725: pha rol po'i tshe bdag gi tshe'i gsos su bstim pa tshe lung /
NK009(ta)002:3726: dgra bgegs kyi rnam shes 'og min du rgyal ba
NK009(ta)002:3727: yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams su 'phangs te rigs kyi
NK009(ta)002:3728: sras su bsgyur ba gnas lung ste /
NK009(ta)002:3729: de lta bu'i dgongs spyod zab mo dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3730: gnyis pa gdab las dngos ni /
NK009(ta)002:3732: gtso bo'i phur pa blangs nas ni //
NK009(ta)002:3733: bdag nyid bsrung ba'i tshe phur bya //
NK009(ta)002:3734: zhes gtso bo'i phur ba bdag nyid kyi srog lta
NK009(ta)002:3735: bu yin pas byin brlab dang mchod bstod byas la
NK009(ta)002:3738: de ltar bdag lus tshags tshud nas //
NK009(ta)002:3739: gzhan gyi lus sems dbral ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)002:3740: khro bo bcu yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:3741: lus kyi gnas bcu dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)002:3742: sgo ma bzhi yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:3743: lus kyi mtsho bzhi dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)002:3744: mi bzad phur pa drug po yis //
NK009(ta)002:3745: gnas drug srog la gdab par bya //
NK009(ta)002:3747: spyir sgrub phur brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK009(ta)002:3748: lha phur lnga bcu rtsa gcig /
NK009(ta)002:3749: gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK009(ta)002:3750: mgyogs phur brgyad cu tham pa /
NK009(ta)002:3751: phur pa sil bu grangs med /
NK009(ta)002:3752: zlog phur bcu gnyis de rnams kyis gdab par bya ba yin kyang /
NK009(ta)002:3753: 'dir gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig ste /
NK009(ta)002:3756: mi bzad pa'i phur pa drug /
NK009(ta)002:3757: sras mchog badz+ra 'dus pa'i phur bu dang nyer gcig gis gdab par gsungs te /
NK009(ta)002:3758: de'ang rnam par rgyal ba'i phur pa de ma byin par len po'i gnas mig gnyis la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3761: dbu non gsum bcas kun la 'gro dgos pa shes par bya zhing /
NK009(ta)002:3762: de bzhin dbyug sngon can gyi phur pa log par lta ba'i gnas sna gnyis la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3763: gshin rje'i gshed kyi phur pa srog gcod spong ba'i gnas yin pas rna ba gnyis la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3764: mi g.yo mgon po'i phur pa rdzun du smra ba'i gnas lce la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3765: rta mgrin gyi phur pa'ang ngag 'khyal spong ba'i gnas lce la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3766: gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i phur pa phra ma'i gnas gsang bar gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3767: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i phur pa tshig rtsub kyi gnas dpung pa g.yon la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3768: khams gsum rnam rgyal gyi phur pa gnod sems kyi gnas lce'i g.yas g.yon la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3769: h'u ka ra'i phur pa log par lta ba'i gnas spyi gtsug tu gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3770: stobs po che'i phur pa brnab sems spong ba'i gnas yin pas rkang pa'i mthil du gdab pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:3771: de dag gis ni mi dge ba bcu rtsad nas
NK009(ta)002:3772: gcad pa'i phyir khro bcu'i phur pa lus kyi gnas
NK009(ta)002:3774: tshad med pa bzhi dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir
NK009(ta)002:3775: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa lus kyi mtsho bzhi la
NK009(ta)002:3776: gdab pa ni / lcags kyu ma'i phur pa glo ba dbugs kyi mtsho la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3777: zhags pa ma'i phur pa mchin pa khrag gis mtsho la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3778: lcags sgrog ma'i phur pa an stong rus pa'i mtsho la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3779: dril bu ma'i phur pa klad pa byang chub sems kyi mtsho la gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3780: de nas pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang ldan
NK009(ta)002:3781: par bya ba'i phyir mi bzad pa'i phur pa drug
NK009(ta)002:3782: gdab pa ni / khrag gi gnad gcod pa seng ldeng gi phur pa spyi gtsug tu gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3783: dbugs kyi gnad gcod pa bya rgod kyi phur pa rkang mthil du gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3784: 'byung bzhi'i gnad gcod pa mi'i mchog phur gsang ba'i gnas su gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3785: rtsa bzhi'i gnad gcod pa tsan+dana gyi phur pa lce'i dkyil du gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3786: tshe'i gnad gcod pa lcags kyi phur pa snying gi dkyil du gdab /
NK009(ta)002:3787: srid pa'i gnad gcod pa skyer pa'i phur pa lte bar gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:3790: spyi bor gtsug tu gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3791: gnam gyi 'ju thag gcad pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3792: rkang pa'i mthil du gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3793: sa yi rten phur phyung pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3794: lce yi dkyil du gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3795: smra ba'i ngag rnams gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3796: gsang ba'i gnas su gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3797: skye ba dgu brgyud gcad pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3798: lte ba'i gnas la gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3799: bskyed pa'i sa bon gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3800: dkar nag snying la gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3801: kun gzhi'i rnam shes gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3803: de nas thams cad kyi mjug tu sras mchog badz+ra
NK009(ta)002:3804: 'dus pa'i phur pa byug bdug gis gzi byin lhag
NK009(ta)002:3805: par bskyed de gsal ba gsum gyi ngar dang ldan
NK009(ta)002:3806: pas snying dkar nag gi mtshams su gdab pa ni
NK009(ta)002:3807: rnam par shes pa de len par byed pa yin
NK009(ta)002:3808: te / tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pas zin par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:3809: de ltar gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gsungs pa ni rgyud kyi dgongs pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3810: gzhan yang sku ltar gdab pa /
NK009(ta)002:3812: thugs ltar gdab par bshad pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:3813: gzhi mthing nag la yod pa'i phur pa rnams sku ltar gdab par 'gro /
NK009(ta)002:3814: de bzhin du dmar nag la yod pa rnams gsung /
NK009(ta)002:3815: mthing nag la yod pa rnams thugs so //
NK009(ta)002:3816: yang na zhi rgyas dbang drag gi gdab las bzhir
NK009(ta)002:3817: phye ba'ang phur bus phyes pa yin par bshad cing
NK009(ta)002:3819: gcig gis sems kyi dpyis dbyung /
NK009(ta)002:3820: gnyis pas kun gzhi rtsad nas gcad /
NK009(ta)002:3821: bcu bdun gyis byung tshor gyi sgo dgag /
NK009(ta)002:3822: nyi shu pas gnam gyi 'ju thag gcad /
NK009(ta)002:3823: nyer gcig pas sa'i rten phur dbyung bar bshad pa'ang gong ma la brtsis pas tshang ngo //
NK009(ta)002:3824: spyir gdab las byas pas srog chags sems can lta
NK009(ta)002:3825: bu la snying rje med pas mtshon cha 'debs pa
NK009(ta)002:3826: lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK009(ta)002:3827: phur bu thams cad lhar gsal ba'i thugs rje dang ye shes kyi ngo bo yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3828: gdab yul de'i nyon mongs pa dang ma rig pa
NK009(ta)002:3829: la btab pas las kyi sgrib pa dang gnod sems
NK009(ta)002:3830: dag nas 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho chen
NK009(ta)002:3831: po las zhi ba myang 'das kyi go 'phang dam
NK009(ta)002:3832: par sgrol bar byed pas na /
NK009(ta)002:3833: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)002:3835: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK009(ta)002:3836: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar gzhan don rlabs su che
NK009(ta)002:3837: ba'i ngo bo dang gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3838: thabs mkhas zab mo'i che ba thun mong ma yin
NK009(ta)002:3839: pas khyad par du byas pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:3840: gzhan yang 'di dag gi skabs khrus lung sogs su go bar bya ba la gsal ba gsum /
NK009(ta)002:3842: dgongs pa rnam pa gsum bcas yod de /
NK009(ta)002:3843: gsal ba gsum ni bdag rdo rje gzhon nur gsal ba /
NK009(ta)002:3844: phur pa sras mchog tu gsal ba /
NK009(ta)002:3845: gzas pa po dngos su gsal ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:3846: de gsum po ma gsal na log rdug 'byams gsum gyi skyon 'ong ste /
NK009(ta)002:3847: bdag nyid lhar ma gsal na log /
NK009(ta)002:3848: phur pa sras mchog tu ma gsal na rdug /
NK009(ta)002:3849: gzas pa po dngos su ma gsal na 'byams 'gro ba yin no //
NK009(ta)002:3851: a dkar bya dkar gyi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:3852: thugs rje 'brel thag gi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:3853: gdung ba lu gu rgyud kyi dgongs pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:3854: 'di dag gi don rgyas pa phur 'grel 'bum nag
NK009(ta)002:3855: sogs su zhib par 'byung ba nyid shes pa gal
NK009(ta)002:3856: che'o // spyir deng sang bstan pa nyams pa'i mgo
NK009(ta)002:3857: bo tshugs pas mdo sngags thams cad kyi dgongs pa
NK009(ta)002:3859: khyad par gsang sngags log par sgrub pas sbyor sgrol gyi dgongs pa barlanga por spyod /
NK009(ta)002:3860: kun slong byang sems ris med par ma 'byangs pas
NK009(ta)002:3861: rang don nam gzhan don nyi tshe tsam 'grub par
NK009(ta)002:3862: re ba'i blo gtad log par gol bas /
NK009(ta)002:3863: dper na bsgral las kyi skabs su gong du bshad
NK009(ta)002:3864: pa'i slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid cung zad kyang mi
NK009(ta)002:3865: ldan zhing / bsgral ba'i dgongs pa mi shes bzhin
NK009(ta)002:3866: du gnod pa'am 'gal rkyen phra mo tsam byas pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3867: gang zag zhig yid yul du byas /
NK009(ta)002:3868: de la zhe sdang rang rgyud pas bskul te zan
NK009(ta)002:3869: gong gi gzugs brnyan la mtshon chas rdeg pa'i rngams
NK009(ta)002:3870: stabs byas pas ni theg chen so thar ltar na
NK009(ta)002:3871: srog gcod kyi pham pa'i nyer len dang /
NK009(ta)002:3872: byang sems kyi sems can blos spong gi ltung ba /
NK009(ta)002:3873: gsang sngags log par sgrub pa'i dam tshig nyams pa
NK009(ta)002:3874: bcas don du cung zad kyang mi 'gyur ba'i steng
NK009(ta)002:3875: du rnam smin yid du mi 'ong ba myong bar
NK009(ta)002:3876: 'gyur bas blang dor gyi gnas la shin tu bag
NK009(ta)002:3877: yod pa la brten nas sde snod rgyud sde /
NK009(ta)002:3878: gsang ba zab mo'i man ngag gi gnad rnams la
NK009(ta)002:3879: thos bsam sgom pa'i sgo nas phyin ci ma log
NK009(ta)002:3880: pa'i gnad la nges pa cung zad rnyed pa re
NK009(ta)002:3881: shin tu gal che bar snang ba'ang 'phros su smos
NK009(ta)002:3882: pa'o // gzhan yang srog gi don po gsum gyis dmigs pa'i gnad dgrol pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3883: bsgral lugs chen po bco brgyad kyis brnag pa'i las
NK009(ta)002:3884: bya ba sogs rgyud dang 'grel chen rig 'dzin brgyud
NK009(ta)002:3885: pa'i zhal gyi lung dri ma med pa dag las
NK009(ta)002:3886: 'byung ba bzhin shes par bya la /
NK009(ta)002:3888: gsum pa gab pa'i sngags drug ni /
NK009(ta)002:3889: spyir las kyi thog mtha' bar du 'gro ba zhig yin la /
NK009(ta)002:3890: khyad par bsad las kyi mtha' sdud du gtso che ste /
NK009(ta)002:3891: de la'ang mngon spyod thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro
NK009(ta)002:3892: ba yin pas kun gyi sna 'dren du btang ba
NK009(ta)002:3893: dang / sgrub pa thams cad kyi ngo bo yin pas dkyus khong khrar gtang ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:3894: las thams cad kyi mjug sdud yin pas smon lam gyi tshul du gdab pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:3895: drag sngags yin pas ngan sngags su byas te srog
NK009(ta)002:3896: la 'khor lo bskor ba dang bzhi'i sgo nas shes
NK009(ta)002:3899: lha dbral gnas nas dgug pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3900: rnam shes gzugs bstim byad du gzhug /
NK009(ta)002:3901: smyor gzhug rdul du brlag pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3902: sha khrag zhal du stob na dgyes //
NK009(ta)002:3905: 'di la las kyis dbye ba'i ldog cha nas nang gses rnam grangs drug cu tham par bshad de /
NK009(ta)002:3906: gnyen po stobs kyi lha drug /
NK009(ta)002:3907: ngan sngags las kyi phur pa drug /
NK009(ta)002:3908: gdab pa gnas kyi yul drug /
NK009(ta)002:3909: bskul bar bya ba'i pho nya drug /
NK009(ta)002:3911: gsag par bya ba'i rdzas drug /
NK009(ta)002:3912: bzla bar bya ba'i sngags drug /
NK009(ta)002:3913: bca' bar bya ba'i phyag rgya drug /
NK009(ta)002:3914: gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i ting nge 'dzin drug /
NK009(ta)002:3915: gdab pa'i smon lam drug ste /
NK009(ta)002:3916: drug tshan bcu'i sgo nas rtogs par bya dgos par bshad pas /
NK009(ta)002:3917: rtsa dum gyi smad las 'dir dngos bstan gab pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3918: sngags drug gi zhar byung gdab las kyang phyogs tsam
NK009(ta)002:3919: bstan pa'i phyir / 'di'i don rgyas pa tshig don dngos bshad pa'i skabs 'og tu 'byung gi /
NK009(ta)002:3920: 'dir bskyar zlos kyis bshad ma dgos so //
NK009(ta)002:3921: gzhan yang mngon spyod kyi las thams cad kyi mjug
NK009(ta)002:3922: sdud mnan sreg 'phang ba sogs drag shul gyi las
NK009(ta)002:3923: mang du gsungs pa dag kyang 'og tu skabs su
NK009(ta)002:3924: bab par cung zad 'chad pa las shes shing /
NK009(ta)002:3925: zhib par rgyud gzhung 'grel t+aika grub pa'i man ngag rnams las nges par bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:3926: bzhi pa ma bsgral ba'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK009(ta)002:3927: spyir rdo rje theg pa'i lam la zhugs shing rtogs
NK009(ta)002:3928: goms brtul zhugs brtan po'i rnal 'byor pas stong pa
NK009(ta)002:3929: dang snying rje chen pos kun nas bslangs te gdug
NK009(ta)002:3930: pa can rnams bsgral bar ma byas na /
NK009(ta)002:3931: rang nyid la rtsa ba'i ltung bar 'gyur ba yin te /
NK009(ta)002:3932: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi pa'i gzhung las /
NK009(ta)002:3933: gdug pa rtag tu byams ldan pa //
NK009(ta)002:3934: byed pa de ni bcu par 'dod //
NK009(ta)002:3937: gdug pa byams pa nyid mi bya //
NK009(ta)002:3940: bstan la gnod par byed pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:3941: bla ma sangs rgyas 'jig pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:3942: bla ma thub pa la zhus nas //
NK009(ta)002:3943: snying rjes bsad par bya ba nyid //
NK009(ta)002:3945: gsang sngags rnying ma'i rgyud las kyang /
NK009(ta)002:3946: nyams pa dus su mi sgrol ba //
NK009(ta)002:3947: de yang dam tshig nyams pa yin //
NK009(ta)002:3949: gshin rje gdong drug gi rgyud las /
NK009(ta)002:3950: gdug pa can la zlog ste bya //
NK009(ta)002:3951: dngos su'am yang na sngags dang gzhan //
NK009(ta)002:3953: sman gyis kyang ni bya ba ste //
NK009(ta)002:3954: de ltar ma byas de yis ni //
NK009(ta)002:3955: dam tshig nges par nyams par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:3957: khyad par phur pa myang 'das kyi rgyud chen po las /
NK009(ta)002:3958: gnyis med don ldan skyes bu des //
NK009(ta)002:3959: gnod gdug rnam gnyis ma bsgral na //
NK009(ta)002:3960: nges par ngan song 'khor bar ltung //
NK009(ta)002:3961: ci phyir nges pa'i las la bsgrib //
NK009(ta)002:3962: nges pa'i don bor log par gol //
NK009(ta)002:3963: lta ba ngan pas ras chod byas //
NK009(ta)002:3964: spyod pa rtsings pas tho cor byas //
NK009(ta)002:3965: dam tshig nyams pas gzu lum byas //
NK009(ta)002:3966: gzhung las gol bas dkyil 'khor dral //
NK009(ta)002:3967: ma nyes pa ni drag por 'joms //
NK009(ta)002:3968: rang las mkhas la skur ba 'debs //
NK009(ta)002:3969: zhes gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid kyis gong du bshad pa'i
NK009(ta)002:3970: nyams pa bdun dang zhing bcu tshang ba'i gdug cing
NK009(ta)002:3971: gtum pa zhi ba'i thabs kyis 'dul du mi btub
NK009(ta)002:3972: pa de dag rdzong 'phrang srog gi gding tshad dang
NK009(ta)002:3973: ldan la / byams dang snying rje'i gzhan dbang du
NK009(ta)002:3974: gyur pa'i rig 'dzin rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos bsgral
NK009(ta)002:3975: ba'i mthu yod bzhin du ma bsgral bar btang snyoms
NK009(ta)002:3976: ldan la / su 'jog na / spyir bla ma
NK009(ta)002:3977: rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i
NK009(ta)002:3979: khyad par sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la rnam par 'tshe ba'i gnas 'jigs su rung ba yod cing /
NK009(ta)002:3980: skye rgu sems can yongs kyi gnas skabs mthar thug
NK009(ta)002:3981: gi phan pa dang bde ba'i shul lam bzang po
NK009(ta)002:3982: dag nye bar 'gog ste phyin ci log pa'i lam
NK009(ta)002:3983: ngan pa'i g.yang sa chen por myur du 'khrid par
NK009(ta)002:3984: 'gyur ba dang / nyams pa de nyid kyang las
NK009(ta)002:3985: ngan pa'i rgyus 'bras bu mnar med rdo rje dmyal
NK009(ta)002:3986: bar bskal pa'am nam mkha' ma zhig pa de srid
NK009(ta)002:3987: du thar ba'i go skabs med par duhkha drag po
NK009(ta)002:3988: skyi g.ya' bas mnar bar 'gyur pa la thugs rje'i
NK009(ta)002:3989: dpyang thag zab mos ma btab pa'i nyes pa dang
NK009(ta)002:3990: 'gyur ba dang / / gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK009(ta)002:3991: pa'i thabs mkhas zab mos myur du gnas ngan len
NK009(ta)002:3992: gyi sa bon bcad de yang dag pa'i sa la
NK009(ta)002:3993: skyel du yod pa'i gdams ngag zab mo ji mi
NK009(ta)002:3994: snyam du chud gsan par byas par 'gyur ba sogs
NK009(ta)002:3995: kyi nyes dmigs mtha' yas pa zhig yod pa yin
NK009(ta)002:3996: 'gyur ba dang / / no // lnga pa bsgral ba'i phan yon ni /
NK009(ta)002:3998: de la drag po'i las byas na //
NK009(ta)002:4001: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK009(ta)002:4002: dgra dang 'byung po rdul du rlog /
NK009(ta)002:4003: mthu chen lha srin de bzhin te //
NK009(ta)002:4004: ci bgyis bka' dang bsgo ba nyan //
NK009(ta)002:4005: 'di dang pha rol gnyis su yang //
NK009(ta)002:4007: bdag dang gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK009(ta)002:4008: gnyis med chos skur dbyer med pas //
NK009(ta)002:4009: ngan song gsum po sgo bkag nas //
NK009(ta)002:4010: gnyis med mkha' la de bsgral na //
NK009(ta)002:4011: don dang mthun pas dam tshig skong //
NK009(ta)002:4012: sdig chen bsgral na las ngan chad //
NK009(ta)002:4013: dam nyams bskal pa bka' gzhung btsan //
NK009(ta)002:4014: log rtog bsgral na dkyil 'khor gnyan //
NK009(ta)002:4015: gnod gdug bsgral na bar chad nyung //
NK009(ta)002:4016: gzhan yang yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK009(ta)002:4018: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dgos ched phan yon
NK009(ta)002:4019: bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig mchis pa yin la
NK009(ta)002:4020: / gong gi ma bsgral ba'i skyon thams cad 'dir
NK009(ta)002:4021: yon tan du ldog ste bla ma dang bstan pa
NK009(ta)002:4022: / / skye rgu yongs la phan bde'i dpal du 'gyur zhing /
NK009(ta)002:4023: yul rang nyid kyang las ngan pa'i rgyun chad /
NK009(ta)002:4024: 'bras bu ngan 'gro las ldog sde mtho ris dang thar pa'i lam 'thob /
NK009(ta)002:4025: sgrub pa po rang nyid tshogs rgya chen po rdzogs te gdod ma'i mgon po'i nye lam du zhugs /
NK009(ta)002:4026: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa bka' btsan /
NK009(ta)002:4027: byin che ba sogs yon tan mtha' dang mu med pa 'thob pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4028: byams snying rje bcos ma ma yin pas kun las
NK009(ta)002:4029: bslang te gzhan phan gyi sems kyis ma rungs pa
NK009(ta)002:4030: gsod par byas pa kho nas kyang bsod nams rgya
NK009(ta)002:4032: bdag cag gi ston pa thugs rje can 'di nyid
NK009(ta)002:4033: slob pa lam gyi skabs su ded dpon snying rje
NK009(ta)002:4034: chen pos tshong pa lnga brgya'i srog skyob pa'i don
NK009(ta)002:4035: du mi nag ma dung thung can bsad pas bskal
NK009(ta)002:4036: pa bzhi khri'i tshogs de nyid du 'dums pa sogs
NK009(ta)002:4037: theg pa chen po'i sde snod dag las 'byung na
NK009(ta)002:4038: / 'dir byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis kyi
NK009(ta)002:4039: rtsis zin pa'i gsang sngags zab mo'i thabs khyad par
NK009(ta)002:4040: can dang ldan pas bsgral ba la de las kyang
NK009(ta)002:4041: phan yon ches rmad du byung ba dag kyang mnga'
NK009(ta)002:4042: / ba yin la / des na dgongs spyod phyin
NK009(ta)002:4043: ci ma log pa dang ldan pas sgrol ba lam
NK009(ta)002:4044: du byas pa de nyid kyis pha rol po'i tshe
NK009(ta)002:4045: bsod rang la khug pas bdag rnal 'byor pa 'tshengs
NK009(ta)002:4046: / ba yin la / / dgra bgegs kyi sha
NK009(ta)002:4047: khrag ye shes kyi bdud rtsir gyur pas bka' sdod
NK009(ta)002:4048: ma mo mkha' 'gro dam can rgya mtsho dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:4049: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams 'tshengs /
NK009(ta)002:4050: pha rol dgra bgegs kyi las ngan rgyun chod nas
NK009(ta)002:4051: bde bar gshegs pa'i sras su gyur pas gzas pa
NK009(ta)002:4053: 'tshengs pa gsum dang ldan pa'i dgongs spyod zab mo
NK009(ta)002:4054: grub pa'i rnal 'byor pa 'jigs med phyogs las rnam
NK009(ta)002:4055: rgyal gyi brtul zhugs la dbang 'byor ba'i yon tan
NK009(ta)002:4056: dang ldan par 'gyur ba sogs kyis sngags pa hom
NK009(ta)002:4057: khung kha nas sangs rgyas so zhes so zur gnubs
NK009(ta)002:4058: gsum sogs gsang sngags rnying ma ba'i sngags rgan ral
NK009(ta)002:4059: pa can rnams la yongs su grags pa 'di lags
NK009(ta)002:4060: so // drug pa de ltar bsgral ba'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni //
NK009(ta)002:4062: 'bras bu nges par chud mi za //
NK009(ta)002:4063: khro bdag chen po thabs mkhas pas //
NK009(ta)002:4064: bsgral ba'i las rnams bya bar bshad //
NK009(ta)002:4065: dang po snying rjes gzhi bzung la //
NK009(ta)002:4066: tshad med rnam bzhi sngon du gtang //
NK009(ta)002:4067: de nas bsgral ba'i phung po de //
NK009(ta)002:4068: gnyis med lha yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK009(ta)002:4069: yang dag don gyis sbyang bar bya //
NK009(ta)002:4070: nam mkha' lta bur skye ba med //
NK009(ta)002:4071: rnam dag phung po lnga yis bsdus //
NK009(ta)002:4072: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)002:4073: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK009(ta)002:4074: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK009(ta)002:4075: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)002:4077: dpal chen rdo rje nyid kyi sku //
NK009(ta)002:4078: ma lus dbyer med 'dus ma byas //
NK009(ta)002:4079: gnyis med don gyi de bzhin no //
NK009(ta)002:4080: zhes gsungs pa sogs kyis mtshon mang du 'byung ba
NK009(ta)002:4081: bzhin bsgral bya gdug pa can de dag la sngags
NK009(ta)002:4082: dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin gsum dang ldan pas
NK009(ta)002:4083: gong du ji skad smos pa lta bu'i mtshan ma
NK009(ta)002:4084: rdzas kyi phur pa ye shes kyi rang bzhin can
NK009(ta)002:4085: de dag tshad dang ldan pa'i gdab lugs kyis btab
NK009(ta)002:4086: nas thebs te gnas skabs kyi las ngan dang skye
NK009(ta)002:4087: rgyun ngan pa bcad nas sa lam gyi yon tan
NK009(ta)002:4088: khyad par can rgyud la nges par smin pa'i rten
NK009(ta)002:4089: du dpal chen yab yum gyi sras su bskrun te
NK009(ta)002:4090: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi'i go 'phang gi mthar thug mthar
NK009(ta)002:4091: lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal sa chen po bde
NK009(ta)002:4092: myur du bgrod nas khyab bdag gdod ma'i mgon po'i
NK009(ta)002:4093: thugs klong ka dag thig le nyag gcig tu dbyer
NK009(ta)002:4094: med chen por mngon par byang chub /
NK009(ta)002:4095: sku dang ye shes zab mo'i phrin las kyi cho
NK009(ta)002:4096: 'phrul mkha' mtha'i mu khyud zlum por bcings pas 'gro
NK009(ta)002:4097: sgrol thabs kyi 'khor lo rgyun chad med par bskor
NK009(ta)002:4098: ba la mnga' brnyes par 'gyur ba ni lam 'di'i
NK009(ta)002:4099: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i rnam gzhag mdor bsdus te
NK009(ta)002:4100: smos pa'o // de lta bu'i gsang sngags thabs mang
NK009(ta)002:4101: la zab pa'i dgongs pa khyad par can gyis phan
NK009(ta)002:4102: gnod kyi las rab 'byams bka' stsal ba thams cad
NK009(ta)002:4103: la bden pa'i 'bras bu dngos brgyud nas mi bslu
NK009(ta)002:4104: ba'i yid ches tshad mas grub pa thun mong ltar
NK009(ta)002:4105: na mtshan dang gzungs sngags zab mo'i byin rlabs kyis
NK009(ta)002:4106: dud 'gro yan chad ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal las grol
NK009(ta)002:4108: de bzhin sngags rnying ma'i phyogs nas btags grol /
NK009(ta)002:4109: gsar rnying kun nas 'pho ba'i man ngag sogs thun
NK009(ta)002:4110: min ji snyed cig gsungs pa rnams kha cig gis
NK009(ta)002:4111: mi 'thad pa'i klan ka byed pa ni thabs dang
NK009(ta)002:4112: man ngag zab mo la yid ches ma skyes shing
NK009(ta)002:4113: rtog ge'i rigs pa ltar snang gi rnam rtog kho
NK009(ta)002:4114: nas sun ci phyin du rgol ba tsam las don
NK009(ta)002:4116: shes ldan dag rgyal ba'i bka' dang de'i man ngag
NK009(ta)002:4117: tshad ma rnams la the tshom pa tsam yang 'byung
NK009(ta)002:4119: spyir sangs rgyas byang sems kyi thugs bskyed smon lam
NK009(ta)002:4120: thabs mkhas kyi spyod yul bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK009(ta)002:4121: dang / khyad par gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa /
NK009(ta)002:4122: de las rnal 'byor bla med kyi lam nas gsungs pa'i dgongs pa mtha' dag thabs mang ba /
NK009(ta)002:4124: dka' ba med pa sogs kyis khyad par du byas
NK009(ta)002:4125: pa'i gnad tshar gcod dang rjes 'dzin 'di dag kyang
NK009(ta)002:4126: gsang gcig pa nyid yin pas shin tu gus shing
NK009(ta)002:4127: ngo mtshar bas rdo rje theg pa'i mtshan tsam rna
NK009(ta)002:4128: ba'i lam du zhugs pa 'di dag ches skal pa
NK009(ta)002:4129: bzang por nges pa'i shes pa snying nas bskyed par
NK009(ta)002:4131: de dag gis spyi don gyi rnam bzhag mdo tsam smos zin nas /
NK009(ta)002:4132: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa smad las rtsa dum gyi don dngos bshad pa la /
NK009(ta)002:4133: 'di nyid rgyud kyi khog dbub dang bstun na bzhi pa /
NK009(ta)002:4134: lnga pa tshe khrus kyi dgongs pa rnams kyis bstan pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4135: rgyud kyi thems sbyor bcu po ltar na dgu pa
NK009(ta)002:4136: ngan sngags bsdu yig drug gsum bco brgyad kyis bsgral
NK009(ta)002:4138: bcu pa mthar phyin gsum gyis las mthar dbyung ba rnams kyi bstan don yin kyang /
NK009(ta)002:4139: 'dir rgyud tshig bzhugs tshul dgos bstan mthar chags su bshad pa'i dbang du byas na dum bu gsum /
NK009(ta)002:4140: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i las rim dngos /
NK009(ta)002:4141: mthar phyin gsum gyi bya ba /
NK009(ta)002:4142: 'phros don bshad pas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4144: thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba /
NK009(ta)002:4145: tshe khrus kyi dgongs pas brten pa dbyings su bsgral ba /
NK009(ta)002:4146: gab pa'i sngags drug bstan pa /
NK009(ta)002:4147: gdab kha'i las rim gyi gtso bo phur gdab bya ba /
NK009(ta)002:4148: gdab kha'i kha tshar rnams kyis rten gzhi bag chags kyi gzugs phung bsgral ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4150: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4151: sprul pa chen pa'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4152: pho nya chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4153: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4154: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4155: khyi yi gdong can dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4156: bsgral bar bya ba'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4157: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK009(ta)002:4158: dus gsum sangs rgyas sras bzhin du //
NK009(ta)002:4159: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK009(ta)002:4160: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK009(ta)002:4161: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK009(ta)002:4162: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK009(ta)002:4163: yud tsam gyis ni de bkug nas //
NK009(ta)002:4164: mngon spyod tshul gyis bsgral ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:4165: lus ngag phye mar mdzad nas kyang //
NK009(ta)002:4166: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:4168: de la dam tshig chen po sogs tshig rkang dang pos gtso bo yab yum bskul /
NK009(ta)002:4169: sprul pa chen po sogs tshig rkang gnyis pas khro bo bcu bskul /
NK009(ta)002:4170: pho nya chen po sogs kyis khra phyag nyi shu dang sgo ma bzhi bskul /
NK009(ta)002:4171: bdag nyid chen pos bdag nyid ma bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:4172: sa bdag chen mos sa bdag ma bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:4173: khyi yi gdong can sogs kyi shwa na ma bzhi bskul ba yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4174: phyin chad kyis drag po'i las mdzad par 'dod don gsol ba'i tshig yin no //
NK009(ta)002:4175: de dag gi tshig 'bru gnyer te cung zad bkrol na /
NK009(ta)002:4176: sngon ru dra sgrol ba'i dus su phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK009(ta)002:4177: rgyas thams cad kyi mthu stobs gcig tu bsdus te
NK009(ta)002:4178: phrin las kyi sras su dbang bskur zhing /
NK009(ta)002:4179: bdud dang log 'dren dam sri'i bar du gcod pa
NK009(ta)002:4180: sogs lhag par ma rungs pa'i phyogs la ches shin
NK009(ta)002:4181: tu rno myur mthu rtsal gyi me lce bzod par
NK009(ta)002:4182: dka' ba'i gzi byin can khro rgyal kun gyi stobs
NK009(ta)002:4183: gcig tu 'dus pa dpal rdo rje gzhon nus gdug
NK009(ta)002:4184: pa can mtha' dag zhi ba chen po'i dbyings su
NK009(ta)002:4185: drag shul snying rje rol pa'i stobs kyis 'dul bar
NK009(ta)002:4186: mdzad pa'i dam tshig stong nyid snying rje mi phyed
NK009(ta)002:4187: pa'i rdo rje'i ngo bor ji ltar bcas pa de
NK009(ta)002:4188: ltar lhag par deng gi skabs su rnal 'byor pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4189: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i dus la bab bo zhes gtso
NK009(ta)002:4191: de bzhin du sngon ru dra sgrol ba'i dus na
NK009(ta)002:4192: phyogs bcu'i dam sri ma rungs pa bcu'i gnyen por
NK009(ta)002:4193: dpal chen po'i thugs las sprul nas phyogs skyong btul
NK009(ta)002:4194: ba'am / rdo rje gzhon nu'i dbang bcu dang stobs
NK009(ta)002:4195: bcu'i ngo bo khro rgyal h'u ka ra sogs mi
NK009(ta)002:4196: bzad pa'i khro bo chen po'am sprul pa chen po
NK009(ta)002:4197: rnams kyis sngon gdug pa'i tshogs rang rang gi gnyen
NK009(ta)002:4198: pos btul ba'i dam tshig dus la deng 'dir bab
NK009(ta)002:4199: ba'am / kyi / rnal 'byor pa'i dgra bgegs bsgral bar mdzod cig ces dang /
NK009(ta)002:4200: gtso bo yab yum gyi thugs rje'i cho 'phrul khro
NK009(ta)002:4201: rgyal bcu'i yang sprul khra phyag nyi shu dag sgo
NK009(ta)002:4202: ma bzhi'i pho nya chen po rnams kyis sngon dam
NK009(ta)002:4203: sri'i yang sprul gdug can rnams btul ba'i dam tshig
NK009(ta)002:4204: gi dus la deng 'dir bab pas /
NK009(ta)002:4205: sgrub pa po'i dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phrin las bskul ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4206: bka'i srung ma'i dbang po'i tshul du rnam par rol pa bdag nyid ma bzhi dang /
NK009(ta)002:4207: yang ru dra'i byi mo sras mor sprul pa'i sa
NK009(ta)002:4208: bdag chen mo bzhi'i dpal gyi bka' nyan bran dang
NK009(ta)002:4209: mngags pa'i phrin las shugs drag po'i tshul gyis sgrub
NK009(ta)002:4210: par mdzad pa'i dus la bab pas mngon spyod kyi
NK009(ta)002:4211: phrin las mdzad par bskul ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4212: yang sngon dpal chen pos ye shes kyi ma mo
NK009(ta)002:4213: rnams 'phar sbyang wa khyi'i gdong can du sprul pa
NK009(ta)002:4214: shwa na ma bzhi la 'dir khyi'i gdong can dubasgyura
NK009(ta)002:4215: te shwa na mu kha zhes pa khyi dang spyang
NK009(ta)002:4216: ka'i gdong can gnyis ka la 'jug cing /
NK009(ta)002:4217: shwa na gtso bor spyang ki la 'jug par gtso
NK009(ta)002:4218: mo spyang ki'i gdong dang zhon pa gnyis ka yin
NK009(ta)002:4219: pas gtso mo'i shugs kyis gzhan rnams kyang spyang ki'i
NK009(ta)002:4220: gdong can du 'ong ba yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:4221: snga 'gyur bka' gter thams cad du shwa na mu
NK009(ta)002:4222: kha zhes khyi spyang gnyis kar 'jug par byas nas
NK009(ta)002:4223: skad dod rang sar bzhag pa yin kyang /
NK009(ta)002:4224: 'dir bod skad du bsgyur ba ltar na'ang don la 'gal ba cher med do //
NK009(ta)002:4225: des na shwa na ma bzhi'i thugs dam dus la bab bo //
NK009(ta)002:4226: mngon spyod kyi phrin las la g.yel ba med par
NK009(ta)002:4227: mdzod cig ces gtso 'khor sprul pa bran dang mngags
NK009(ta)002:4228: pa'i tshogs thams cad kyi dam tshig chen po'i dus
NK009(ta)002:4230: brnag par bya ba'i dgra bgegs dam sri zhi bas
NK009(ta)002:4231: 'dul du mi 'tshal ba rnams drag po mngon spyod
NK009(ta)002:4232: kyi thabs kyis myur du bsgral bar bya ba'i phrin
NK009(ta)002:4233: las la g.yel ba med pa'i tshul du rnal 'byor
NK009(ta)002:4234: pa'i dpung dang gnyen du nye bar bzhengs pa'i dus
NK009(ta)002:4235: la bab pas dgongs par mdzod cig ces bskul nas
NK009(ta)002:4236: / dgra bgegs gang zhig sgrol na /
NK009(ta)002:4237: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK009(ta)002:4238: nas dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras
NK009(ta)002:4239: byang chub sems dpa' bzhin du sems can gyi don
NK009(ta)002:4240: byed pa'i rgyal ba'i gdung rig 'dzin par dam bcas
NK009(ta)002:4241: pa'i bdag cag dpon slob rnams la ni do bdo
NK009(ta)002:4242: zhing phod btsugs la brnyas pa byed pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4243: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dang skye rgu yongs la
NK009(ta)002:4244: bsam sbyor phyin ci log pa'i sgo nas gnod cing
NK009(ta)002:4245: gdug pa can du gyur pa'i gzugs can gyi dgra
NK009(ta)002:4246: nyams pa bdun la sogs pa dang ldan pa /
NK009(ta)002:4247: gzugs med kyi bgegs dam sri bdud dang bar du
NK009(ta)002:4248: bcod pa mtha' dag ji snyed pa de dag rnams
NK009(ta)002:4249: khro bo chen po rdo rje gzhon nu sras 'khor
NK009(ta)002:4250: sprul pa bka' sdod dang bcas pa'i byin rlabs kyi
NK009(ta)002:4251: pho nya'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros pa
NK009(ta)002:4252: rnams kyis skad cig thang cig yud tsam gyis ni
NK009(ta)002:4253: de dag mngon spyod kyi gnas 'dir 'chor ba med
NK009(ta)002:4254: par bkug nas mngon spyod drag po'i tshul gyis bsgral
NK009(ta)002:4255: ba dang / rnam shes ye nas dag pa de gnas spar ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4256: nyer len gyi phung po chen po gzhig pa'i phyir
NK009(ta)002:4257: 'byung bzhi las skyes pa'i tha mal gyi lus ngag
NK009(ta)002:4258: yid gsum rdul phran bzhin du phye mar mdzad nas
NK009(ta)002:4259: kyang / nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyang ba'i phyir
NK009(ta)002:4260: mnan gzir gyis sdug bsngal rnams lus ngag yid gsum
NK009(ta)002:4261: gyis nyams su myong ste slan chad sdug bsngal gyi
NK009(ta)002:4262: rtsa ba chad nas zhi ba'i dbyings su 'god par
NK009(ta)002:4264: lam sogs kyi sngags 'bros su mi ster ba'i phyir zil gyis gnon pa'i snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4266: mi 'chor bar dbang du sdud pa'i snying po gsum
NK009(ta)002:4267: gyi tshul du 'di'i rjes 'brel du kha cig nas
NK009(ta)002:4268: bshad kyang / tshe khrus kyi dgongs pa'i don 'og tu 'chad do //
NK009(ta)002:4269: gnyis pa tshe khrus kyi dgongs pas brten pa dbyings su bsgral ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:4270: gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa /
NK009(ta)002:4271: log rdug 'byams gsum dang bral ba /
NK009(ta)002:4272: dgongs pa rnam gsum dang ldan pa /
NK009(ta)002:4274: tshe lung gsum gyi dgongs pas 'debs dgos shing /
NK009(ta)002:4276: gdab las dkyus la sras mchog gi phur bu dang /
NK009(ta)002:4277: sgrub pa chen por phur khrom gyi rdzas dkyil gtso
NK009(ta)002:4278: bo sras mchog la'ang dkyil 'khor gsum ga rdzogs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4279: gtso bo nyid yak+sha kro d+ha'i ngo bor gyur pas
NK009(ta)002:4281: gzas pa po ni mdun du mngon sum lta bur gsal ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4283: a dkar bya dkar gyi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:4284: thugs rje 'brel thag gi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)002:4285: gdung ba lu gu rgyud kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4292: h+r+aihsh+t+aihbi kri ta badz+ra h'u ka ra h'u /
NK009(ta)002:4293: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam ho /
NK009(ta)002:4294: sarba big+h+n+aana badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4295: ces pa'i sngags 'dis dkyil 'khor gsum gyi spyi bor h'u ka ra dkar po /
NK009(ta)002:4296: de'i spyi bor a dkar po /
NK009(ta)002:4297: phur pa'i rtse mor yang a dkar pos nye bar brgyan pa /
NK009(ta)002:4298: gzas pa po'i snying gar yang rnam par shes pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4299: ngo bo a dkar po gsal ba ni a dkar
NK009(ta)002:4301: gnyis pa gong gi sngags kyis slar yang h'u ka
NK009(ta)002:4302: ra yab yum a dang bcas pa 'od du gyur
NK009(ta)002:4303: pas dkyil 'khor gsum yongs su gang zhing bdag gi
NK009(ta)002:4304: sdig sgrib sbyong bar byed pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4305: phur pa gzas po'i snying gar dril bas phur rtse'i sa bsgral bya'i don byas shing /
NK009(ta)002:4306: bdag dang gzas pa po phur bu gsum dgongs pa gcig gis 'brel /
NK009(ta)002:4308: chos nyid gcig gis 'brel bar snang bas na thugs rje 'brel thag gi dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:4310: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)002:4312: spyir sems can thams cad snying rje chen po'i blos mi gtong zhing /
NK009(ta)002:4313: sgos las ngan can 'khor bar mi gtong bas na
NK009(ta)002:4314: gdung ba lu gu rgyud kyi 'brel ba'i dgongs pa
NK009(ta)002:4315: zhes bya ba ste khrus lung ngo //
NK009(ta)002:4317: byung tshor gyi sgo dgag pa /
NK009(ta)002:4319: kun gzhi rtsad nas gcod pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4321: gong gi sngags kyis phur pa mig la dril bas gzugs kyi byung tshor bkag /
NK009(ta)002:4322: rna ba la dril bas sgra'i byung tshor bkag /
NK009(ta)002:4325: lus reg bya bcas bkag nas sgo lnga'i rnam shes
NK009(ta)002:4326: gur gyi chon thag bsdus pa bzhin du kun gzhi
NK009(ta)002:4327: la 'ub kyis bsdus pa'i bya ba byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4328: gnyis pa sems kyi dbyings dbyung ba la'ang gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:4333: gong gi sngags kyis phur pa'i ri rab kyis bsdigs
NK009(ta)002:4334: pas gzas pa po'i sha khrag dang snying dkar nag
NK009(ta)002:4335: dpral ba ni phata dral ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4336: gnyis pa phur pa'i 'od kyis nying dkar nag gi
NK009(ta)002:4337: mtshams nas khrag gi sbal pa mthe bong tsam yod
NK009(ta)002:4338: pa bsregs / de'i nang na dwangs ma rnam pa gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)002:4339: khrag gi dwangs ma mtshal lcog la 'dra ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4340: rtsa'i dwangs ma rgyus pa klad pa 'dra ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4341: dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og tu sbas pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4342: rlangs pa tsam ste gsum yod pa de gsum gyi
NK009(ta)002:4343: dbus na kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa yi ge
NK009(ta)002:4344: a thung gi tshul du sems can thams cad la
NK009(ta)002:4345: yod pas de la sngags dang bcas te phur pa
NK009(ta)002:4346: g.yengs pas de dag gi dbus su phur pa thogs
NK009(ta)002:4348: gsum pa sngags kyis phur pa gdengs pas rnam shes
NK009(ta)002:4349: a thung de nyid rdo khab len la lcags 'du
NK009(ta)002:4350: ba bzhin nam / bye tshan la mar thim pa
NK009(ta)002:4351: bzhin du phur pa'i rtse mor 'dus par gsal ba'o
NK009(ta)002:4352: ba bzhin nam / // gsum pa kun gzhi rtsad nas gcad pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4353: de'i 'og tu de'i shul na phur pa gzhan gyis
NK009(ta)002:4354: btab la bzhag ste de'i rnam shes lhod pa med
NK009(ta)002:4356: kun gzhi rtsad nas gcod pa zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)002:4357: phur pa'i rtse mor dmigs yul gyi rnam shes a
NK009(ta)002:4358: bkrag dang ldan pa rig pa tshe dang bsod nams
NK009(ta)002:4359: dang bcas pa tshur bdag la gong gi sngags kyis
NK009(ta)002:4360: bsdus pas kho'i tshe bsod thams cad rang la thim
NK009(ta)002:4361: pas bkrag mdangs gzi brjid dang ldan par gyur pa
NK009(ta)002:4362: ni bdag gi tshe lung du bshad la /
NK009(ta)002:4363: de ni me 'bar ba la shing bsnan pa dang
NK009(ta)002:4364: mtshungs par rang nyid tshe bsod nams dang ldan par
NK009(ta)002:4365: 'gyur pa'o // des na yul gyi tshe bsod rang la thob pas bdag mi pham la /
NK009(ta)002:4366: bdag gis yul gyi sgrib pa sbyangs pas dgra mi pham pa ste gnyis ka 'tshengs pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:4367: de nas rnam par shes pa a thung gi rnam pa can du gyur pa phur rtses blangs /
NK009(ta)002:4368: rang lha'i thugs ka'i ye shes kyi rlung har gyis
NK009(ta)002:4369: byung ste des bteg nas me stag drag po yar
NK009(ta)002:4370: ba bzhin 'og min rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor
NK009(ta)002:4371: mtshams su bskyal te rigs lnga'i sras su skye bar
NK009(ta)002:4372: byed pa ni rten 'brel zab mo'i khyad par gyi
NK009(ta)002:4373: mthu las de ltar 'gyur ba'ang nges pa'i gsang ba
NK009(ta)002:4374: zab mo dang / chos nyid kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis so //
NK009(ta)002:4375: de ni gnas spar ba'i cho ga zhes gsang sngags
NK009(ta)002:4376: kyi khyad chos bla na med pa yin pa'i phyir
NK009(ta)002:4377: tshe lung dang khrus lung gi dgongs pa ma shes
NK009(ta)002:4378: na shan pa dang khyad med par slob dpon pad+ma'i
NK009(ta)002:4379: zhal snga nas 'doms par mdzad pa yin no //
NK009(ta)002:4380: gong du bstan pa'i sngags don yang khrus lung ltar bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4381: tshe lung ltar bshad pa gnyis las /
NK009(ta)002:4383: lam zhes pas rigs kyi yab lnga /
NK009(ta)002:4384: h'u lam zhes pas yum lnga lag pa g.yas g.yon gyi sor mo dag la bskyed pa'i don dang /
NK009(ta)002:4385: s+t+wam b+h+aa ya n+aan zhes pas yab yum gnyis med
NK009(ta)002:4386: du sbyor bas lag gi 'du byed bsgom pa'i don
NK009(ta)002:4387: dang / mo ham g+h+aa ta ya ming dang rus /
NK009(ta)002:4391: badz+ra rdo rje ste gnyis su med pa'i don //
NK009(ta)002:4392: de bskyed pa'i rgyu h'u yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4394: h'u gis bsdus la sbyongs shig pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4395: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ye shes kyi phur ba /
NK009(ta)002:4396: dzah h'u bam hohphyaga rgya bzhis dgug bcing la sogs pa byas nas /
NK009(ta)002:4399: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ni ye shes kyi phur pas 'debs pa /
NK009(ta)002:4400: h'u gis bsdus la phata kyis gtor zhig pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4403: h'u lam zhes pas sku gsung thugs ri rab ltar brjid pas non cig /
NK009(ta)002:4405: s+t+wam b+ha ya n+aan zhes sa 'og tu gzir la non /
NK009(ta)002:4407: mo ham g+ha ta ya zhes pa ming dang rus su bcas pa'i dgra bgegs /
NK009(ta)002:4409: b+ha ga w+aan zhes bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyi skus non cig pa /
NK009(ta)002:4410: tshul lam thabs ji ltar gnon cing gzir na /
NK009(ta)002:4411: h+r+aihsh+t+aihbi kri zhes pas thabs shes snyoms par zhugs la non cig /
NK009(ta)002:4413: badz+ra h'u ka ra h'u zhes pas dpal ldan rang
NK009(ta)002:4414: bzhin gyi rdo rje phur pa las bsdus la sems
NK009(ta)002:4415: kyi rnam par rtog pa chod cig ces dang /
NK009(ta)002:4416: de ltar bcad nas lus sems la yod pa'i rtog
NK009(ta)002:4417: med kyi ye shes tshur bsdus la rnam par rtog
NK009(ta)002:4418: pa dang bcas pa'i lus sems kun bsregs la thal
NK009(ta)002:4420: gang du bsreg cing brlag par bya na /
NK009(ta)002:4421: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hohzhesa pas
NK009(ta)002:4422: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum 'khor khro bo
NK009(ta)002:4423: khro mo za gsod sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4424: zhal du bstabs te bsregs la brlag par gyis shig
NK009(ta)002:4425: pa dang / gang brlag par bya na /
NK009(ta)002:4426: sarba big+h+n+aana zhes dgra bgegs thams cad /
NK009(ta)002:4427: gang gis brlag par byed na /
NK009(ta)002:4428: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata ste sras
NK009(ta)002:4429: mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya'i sku rdo rje phur pas
NK009(ta)002:4430: thob / sems bsdus la lus phyir khrol cig ces
NK009(ta)002:4431: pa'i don yin par yig rnying bzhin du sa phur
NK009(ta)002:4433: gsum pa gab pa'i sngags drug bstan pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4434: bgegs byed pa yi bdud rnams dang //
NK009(ta)002:4436: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4437: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan pa'ang /
NK009(ta)002:4439: lha dbral gnas nas dgug pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:4440: rnam shes gzugs bstim byad du gzhug /
NK009(ta)002:4441: smyor gzhug rdul du brlag pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:4442: sha khrag zhal du bstabs na dgyes //
NK009(ta)002:4445: de la'ang bskul dang dgug gzhug bya ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4446: sngags tshan bcu gnyis po dngos bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4449: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa la bgegs
NK009(ta)002:4450: sam bar du gcod par byed pa'i bdud rnams dang
NK009(ta)002:4451: / dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis sems la mi bzod
NK009(ta)002:4452: pa'i mya ngan gyi khur mnyam du sbyor ba'i las
NK009(ta)002:4453: ngan pa la zhugs pa che ge mo zhes ming
NK009(ta)002:4454: dang rus su smos pa su dang gang yin kyang
NK009(ta)002:4455: de nyid 'khrul med du 'di dang 'adi'o zhes bya
NK009(ta)002:4456: ba gzugs ling+ga ming byang bu bla 'khor lo la
NK009(ta)002:4457: bskor ba rang gzhan la gnod pa'i log 'dren ma
NK009(ta)002:4458: rungs pa bdud kyi thibs kyis non pa'i nyams pa
NK009(ta)002:4459: bdun ldan dang zhing bcu tshang ba'i bsgral bar bya
NK009(ta)002:4460: / ba'i 'os / bsad par bya ba'i mchog gang
NK009(ta)002:4461: yin pa de dag 'khor ba'i gnas ris nas drang
NK009(ta)002:4462: ba'i phyir pho nya lcags kyu can gyis snying nas
NK009(ta)002:4463: / ba'i 'os / zungs shig / bde ba'i gnas
NK009(ta)002:4464: su bskul ba'i phyir tho ba can gyis rgyab nas
NK009(ta)002:4466: nyon mongs pa'i dbang po rang yan du mi gtong
NK009(ta)002:4467: ba'i phyir zhags pa can gyis yan lag rnam par
NK009(ta)002:4469: chings shig / bag chags kyi phung po brlag par
NK009(ta)002:4470: bya ba'i phyir gzugs kyi phung po gtogs shig gam
NK009(ta)002:4472: chings shig / sdigs shig / sdig pa'i grogs dang
NK009(ta)002:4473: bral bar bya ba'i phyir ram nag po'i phyogs kyi
NK009(ta)002:4474: dpung gnyen dang stong grogs byed pa'i dpal lam /
NK009(ta)002:4475: gnyen po dang kha phral te so sor dbye bar gyis shig /
NK009(ta)002:4476: myur du gnas ngan las bsgral te rten dang brten
NK009(ta)002:4477: pa rdul du rlog pa'i phyir mgyogs byed kyi pho
NK009(ta)002:4478: nyas myur ba'am / rings pa'i tshul lam /
NK009(ta)002:4479: sa 'og sa steng sa bla sogs shin tu bskal
NK009(ta)002:4480: ba'i ring po'i gnas gang na yod kyang rang dbang
NK009(ta)002:4482: gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis nyes byas la mthol
NK009(ta)002:4483: zhing bshags pa'i smre sngags kyi 'o dod smra ru
NK009(ta)002:4484: chug cig / thugs rjes nges par gzung bar bya ba'i phyir 'bebs byed kyis gzugs la phob cig /
NK009(ta)002:4485: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyang ba'i phyir gzir byed
NK009(ta)002:4486: kyis lus ngag yid gsum rnam par gzir bar gyis
NK009(ta)002:4487: shig / dkyil 'khor du nges par chud par bya
NK009(ta)002:4488: ba'i phyir dbang byed kyis rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid
NK009(ta)002:4489: kyi dbang du byas par gyur nas /
NK009(ta)002:4490: dam las mi 'da' ba'i phyir bka' nyan byed kyis
NK009(ta)002:4491: bsgo ba'i bka' nyan cing ma dad pa'i blo ldog
NK009(ta)002:4492: ste shin tu gus pa dang ldan par gyis shig
NK009(ta)002:4493: pa'am byos shig / ces pa ste tshig thad kar dkyus ltar bshad pa de ltar yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4494: 'og gi gab pa'i sngags drug gi so so'i 'phyong dang /
NK009(ta)002:4495: thog mar 'gro ba'i rnam shes dgug pa sogs kyi
NK009(ta)002:4496: tshig gnad kyang 'di'i khongs su 'byung ba yin no
NK009(ta)002:4497: // gnyis pa sngags tshan bcu gnyis po dngos bshad pa la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:4501: h'u pa ra bid+ya sogs nas /
NK009(ta)002:4502: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4504: 'di la don drug po re re la don bcu
NK009(ta)002:4505: bcu ste drug cu tham pa'i ldog pa dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:4507: de'ang gnyen po stobs kyi lha drug /
NK009(ta)002:4508: ngan sngags las kyi phur pa drug /
NK009(ta)002:4509: gdab pa gnas kyi gdab pa drug /
NK009(ta)002:4510: bskul bar bya ba'i pho nya drug /
NK009(ta)002:4512: gsag par bya ba'i rdzas drug /
NK009(ta)002:4513: bzla bar bya ba'i sngags drug /
NK009(ta)002:4514: bca' bar bya ba'i phyag rgya drug /
NK009(ta)002:4515: gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i ting nge 'dzin drug /
NK009(ta)002:4516: gdab par bya ba'i smon lam drug go //
NK009(ta)002:4517: dang po lha dang dbral ba la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)002:4518: gnyen po stobs kyi lha ni /
NK009(ta)002:4519: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ste ts+tshin+d+ha ts+tshin+d+ha h'u phata kyi sngags kyis so //
NK009(ta)002:4522: ngan sngags las kyi phur pa seng ldeng dmar po dang /
NK009(ta)002:4523: gdab pa'i gnas spyi gtsug ste /
NK009(ta)002:4526: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4529: gtogs shig grogs dang dbye bar gyis zhes pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4530: gsag pa'i rdzas ni gu gul khyi brun tshil chen sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:4532: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aih dan+da h+aum phata /
NK009(ta)002:4533: ces so so'i mgor k+ai la yas mnan cing /
NK009(ta)002:4534: dgra bgegs m+aa ra ya dang /
NK009(ta)002:4535: mthar big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata kyi bar du bcug pa 'og ma kun la'ang dgos par bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:4537: dud pas bdug pa'i tshul du bya 'ug pa'i sgros dbye ba'i tshul dang /
NK009(ta)002:4538: dngos su'ang rdzas dud bdug pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4540: dgra bgegs kyi lha srung dang phrol cig sogs brjod pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4542: dpal chen po'i thugs ka nas sprul pa'i pho nya
NK009(ta)002:4543: rnams kyis dbye ba'i las mdzad pas dgra bgegs lha
NK009(ta)002:4544: dang bral te mi med pa'i grong stong ngam /
NK009(ta)002:4545: bye'u khyur rdo 'phangs pas gzhan 'phur te gang la
NK009(ta)002:4546: phog pa de gcig pur lus pa ltar gyur par
NK009(ta)002:4547: bsam mo // gnyis pa gzugs la dbab pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4548: gnyen po stobs kyi lha mi g.yo mgon po ste bin+d+ha bin+d+ha h'u phata kyis mtshon pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4549: 'jig rten las kyi lha yam shud dmar po yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4553: rkang pa'i mthil te sa'i rten phur phyung ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4555: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4558: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis /
NK009(ta)002:4561: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4565: mtshe dang yungs dkar nag sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:4567: thugs ka'i 'od kyis gzas pa po dngos su bkug pa ltar ling+ga la bstim pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4573: gsum pa byad du gzhug pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4574: gnyan po stobs kyi lha khams gsum rnam rgyal te b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha h'u phata ces pa dang /
