NK009(ta)002:4575: 'jig rten las kyi lha klu'i rgyal po /
NK009(ta)002:4578: gdab pa gsang gnas su skye ba dgu rgyud gcad pa'i phyir du /
NK009(ta)002:4580: phyag brnyan chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4583: zungs shig rdungs shig rnam par chings zhes so //
NK009(ta)002:4588: byad thag gis bcing ba'i tshul bya zhing /
NK009(ta)002:4590: tshon skud sna lnga'i thag pa sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:4592: pho nya mang pos gru gu thul du bcings par bsam pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4596: sogs kyi dmod mo bya ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4597: bzhi pa smyor gzhug pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4598: gnyen po stobs kyi lha rta mgrin te /
NK009(ta)002:4599: g+h+rih+na g+h+rih+na h'uhphata ces pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:4600: las kyi lha rgyal po pe dkar ro //
NK009(ta)002:4602: gdab pa lce'i dkyil du ngag 'joms pa'i phyir dang /
NK009(ta)002:4604: khyi yi gdong can dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4607: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK009(ta)002:4610: dz+wa l+aa pa ya ya dz+wa l+aa pa h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4613: dug khong du gtong ba'i tshul /
NK009(ta)002:4615: d+ha du ra dang dug sna'i chu'o //
NK009(ta)002:4617: snying ga nas 'od tsh+wa tsh+wa lta bu 'phros pas myos shing brgyal /
NK009(ta)002:4618: smyo zhing 'bogs pa sogs su gsal ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4623: ces sogs kyis dmod bor ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4624: lnga pa rdul du brlag pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4625: gnyen po stobs kyi lha dbyug sngon can te ha na ha na h'u phata dang /
NK009(ta)002:4626: las kyi lha ni bdud do //
NK009(ta)002:4630: snying dkar nag gi mtshams su sems kyi dbyings dbyung ba'i phyir gdab bo //
NK009(ta)002:4632: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4635: lus sems rdul bzhin brlag par mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:4638: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4643: rdo rje tho ba sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:4645: tho ba thogs pa'i sprul pa mang pos rdung ba'i dmigs rnam dang /
NK009(ta)002:4647: dgra bo rdul dang phye ma thal bar rlog cig /
NK009(ta)002:4649: 'di ni 'og tu kha tshar gyi las su bshad par 'gyur yang /
NK009(ta)002:4650: 'dir sa khongs ma stongs phyir bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4651: drug pa zhal du bstab pa ni /
NK009(ta)002:4652: gnyen po stobs kyi lha stobs po che ste h'u pa ra bid+yana zhes pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4658: lte ba ste bskyed pa'i sa bon gzhom pa'i don du'o //
NK009(ta)002:4660: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4662: bsgo ba'i bka' nyan gus par gyis //
NK009(ta)002:4665: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4670: e gru gsum gyi hom gzar sogs so //
NK009(ta)002:4672: khro bo khro mo'i zhal du dgyes pa'i rkan sgra dang bcas te gsol bar bsam pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:4674: lha tshogs rnams kyis sha khrag rus pa lhag ma med par bzhes shig /
NK009(ta)002:4676: mthar mgo bo la mnan pa bya /
NK009(ta)002:4679: nang khrol lha'i zhal du bstab /
NK009(ta)002:4680: dkyus khong khrar gtong ba'i skabs bzhi kun gyi mgo la gdags pa /
NK009(ta)002:4681: gsum kun gyi khong khrar gtang ba /
NK009(ta)002:4682: gcig kun gyi gzhug la gdags pa'i man ngag ltar
NK009(ta)002:4683: gab pa'i sngags drug po 'di nyid phur gdab sogs
NK009(ta)002:4684: bsgral ba kun gyi thog mtha' bar gsum du mgo
NK009(ta)002:4685: 'dren gzhung srong mjug sdud kyi tshul du 'gro ba
NK009(ta)002:4686: yin la / gong du spyi don du'ang cung zad smos pa ltar dang /
NK009(ta)002:4689: sngags tshan bcu gnyis kyi dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha'i sngags drug dang /
NK009(ta)002:4690: sngags phyi ma drug gi gab pa'i sngags drug yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4691: h'u pa ra bid+y+aa rig pa'i rgyal po /
NK009(ta)002:4693: h'u phata kyi don ni thams cad la rigs 'gre bas 'og tu 'chad la /
NK009(ta)002:4695: ts+tshin+d+ha zhes pa 'dzin byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4696: bin+d+ha zhes pa bdag bskyed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4698: ban+d+ha zhes pa 'byed byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4699: t+r+aa sha ya 'gugs byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4700: ha sa ya ra smra byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4701: sh+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya 'bebs byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4702: dz+wa la pa ya gzir byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4703: +aa be sha ya dbang du sdud pa'i snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4704: ban+d+ha ya bka' nyan byed kyi snying po /
NK009(ta)002:4705: h'u khro bo bcu bskyed de bsdu ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4706: phata spro ba'i don yin par bshad do //
NK009(ta)002:4707: bzhi pa gdab kha'i las rim gyi gtso bo phur gdab bya ba la gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:4709: sngags tsam gyis gdab las dngos bshad pa'o /
NK009(ta)002:4711: pho nya bran dag mngags pa'i tshogs //
NK009(ta)002:4712: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK009(ta)002:4713: mngon spyod ji ltar nges pa dang //
NK009(ta)002:4714: mngon spyod byin rlabs de bzhin mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:4716: de'ang tshe lung khrus gsum gyi dgongs pas brten pa dbyings su bsgral ba sngon du song nas /
NK009(ta)002:4717: 'dir rten gzhi gzhon pa la phur bu so so'i gdab kha'i las bya ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:4718: de la dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs /
NK009(ta)002:4719: bla ma rig 'dzin grub thob brgyud pa'i thugs dam
NK009(ta)002:4720: dus la bab pa'i tshul du nye bar bskul te
NK009(ta)002:4721: mngon spyod drag po gdab pa'i las kyi dpung gnyen
NK009(ta)002:4722: du gsol ba spyi sngon du bstan pa'am song zin
NK009(ta)002:4723: nas / 'dir yang khyad par du bskul ba'i tshig gi don tsam thad kar bkrol na /
NK009(ta)002:4724: de'ang pho nya ni gtso bo nas rim par sprul
NK009(ta)002:4725: pa'i pho nya rnams kyi gang du mngags pa'i gnas
NK009(ta)002:4726: su phyin par 'gro ba'i phyir pho nya zhes 'khor
NK009(ta)002:4728: skabs 'dir pho nya zhes pa gtso bor khro bcu
NK009(ta)002:4729: yab yum khra thabs nyi shu dang bcas pa yin
NK009(ta)002:4730: la / bran zhes pa'ang gtso bos bcol ba'i las
NK009(ta)002:4731: rnams byed pa'i phyir bran zhes pa spyi ming yin
NK009(ta)002:4732: la / yang / skabs thob kyi sgo ma bzhi yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4733: mngags pa'i tshogs ni zab dang gsod par byed pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4734: khra phyag dang pho nya sprul pa yang sprul nyid
NK009(ta)002:4735: sprul dang bcas pa'i tshogs te /
NK009(ta)002:4736: mdor na pho nya sum brgya drug cu'i tshogs dang
NK009(ta)002:4737: bcas pa khyed rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK009(ta)002:4738: tshig gnyan po de'i thugs la bab pas /
NK009(ta)002:4739: sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar sgrub pa po rnams
NK009(ta)002:4740: kyi mngon spyod kyi las kyi grogs bya bar khas
NK009(ta)002:4741: blangs pas ji ltar thugs la nges pa bzhin dang
NK009(ta)002:4742: / dam bcas pa'i don mngon spyod kyi phrin las
NK009(ta)002:4743: 'dir skad cig kyang mi thogs pa myur du 'grub
NK009(ta)002:4744: pa'i byin rlabs sngar ru dra bsgral ba'i gnas skabs
NK009(ta)002:4745: su cho 'phrul rol pa'i thabs mkhas zab mo ji
NK009(ta)002:4746: ltar mdzad pa de bzhin du mdzod cig /
NK009(ta)002:4748: gnyis pa gdab las dngos kyi don ni /
NK009(ta)002:4752: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK009(ta)002:4754: khro bo bcu yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:4755: lus kyi gnas bcu dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)002:4756: sgo ma bzhi yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)002:4757: lus kyi mtsho bzhi dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)002:4758: mi bzad phur pa drug po yis //
NK009(ta)002:4759: gnas drug srog la gdab par bya //
NK009(ta)002:4760: zhes pa'i bstan don ltar phur pa nyer gcig gis
NK009(ta)002:4761: gdab pa'i tshul gong du spyi don sa bcad gsum
NK009(ta)002:4762: pa'i khongs su bshad pa ltar shes par bya la
NK009(ta)002:4763: / 'dir yang sngags don dang 'brel bar cung zad smos na /
NK009(ta)002:4764: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nan /
NK009(ta)002:4765: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4766: che ge mo m+aa ra ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4767: ces pas rnam rgyal phur pa mig gnyis la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4768: de bzhin du de bzhin nyid don gyi dbu non /
NK009(ta)002:4769: k+ai la ya sngags kyi dbu non /
NK009(ta)002:4770: dus la bab tshig gi dbu non bcas dbu non gsum po kun la sbyar dgos pas /
NK009(ta)002:4772: da ha da ha badz+ra zhes dbyug sngon can gyi phur bu sna la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4773: pa tsa pa tsa badz+ra zhes pas gshin rje'i gshed kyi phur pa rna ba gnyis la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4774: ma th+aa ma th+aa badz+ra zhes pas mi g.yo mgon po'i phur pa lte ba la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4775: dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra zhes rta mgrin gyi phur pa yang lce la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4776: su ru su ru badz+ra zhes pas gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i phur pa gsang gnas su gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4777: mu ru mu ru badz+rasa bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i phur pa dpung pa g.yon la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4779: dza ye bi dza ye badz+rasa khams gsum rnam rgyal gyi phur pa dpyi la gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4780: a dzi te a pa r+aa dzi te badz+rasa h'u ka ra'i phur pa spyi gtsug tu gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4781: ma ra se nya pra mrda ni h'u phata ces
NK009(ta)002:4782: pas stobs po che'i phur pa rkang mthil du gdab
NK009(ta)002:4783: pa de dag gis mi dge ba bcu rtsad nas
NK009(ta)002:4785: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa'ang lcags kyu ma'i phur pa glo ba /
NK009(ta)002:4786: zhags pa ma'i phur pa mchin pa /
NK009(ta)002:4787: lcags sgrog ma'i phur pa an stong /
NK009(ta)002:4788: dril bu ma'i phur pa klad pa ste mtsho bzhi
NK009(ta)002:4789: la gdab pa ni tshad med bzhi dang ldan par
NK009(ta)002:4791: mi bzad pa'i phur pa seng ldeng bya rgod /
NK009(ta)002:4795: skyer ba ste drug sngags drug gis gnas drug la
NK009(ta)002:4796: gdab pa ni pha rol du phyin pa drug ldan
NK009(ta)002:4797: du bsgrub pa'i don yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4798: gong du gab pa'i sngags drug bsnyen pa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar ro //
NK009(ta)002:4799: thams cad kyi mjug tu sras mchog badz+ra 'dus pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4800: phur pa snying dkar nag gi mtshams su gdab pa
NK009(ta)002:4801: ni tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pa gong du
NK009(ta)002:4803: de dag ni rgyud kyi dgongs pas 'grel chen 'bum
NK009(ta)002:4804: nag tu bshad pa ltar gdab phur nyi shu rtsa
NK009(ta)002:4805: gcig gis rten gzhi sgrol ba'i gdab kha bstan pa
NK009(ta)002:4807: sras mchog sgo ma khro mo brgyad //
NK009(ta)002:4808: khro bo bcu dang khro mo gnyis //
NK009(ta)002:4809: dam can la sogs rim bzhin no //
NK009(ta)002:4810: zhes pa ltar khong khra'i las thun brdeg pa /
NK009(ta)002:4812: gtun du brdung ba gsum gsum gyis mjug bsdus pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4813: gtso sras zung 'brel gyi phur pa gnas gsum du
NK009(ta)002:4815: de phyin chad kyi phur gdab thams cad mi ldog
NK009(ta)002:4816: pa'i phrin las mthar 'byin gyi don du gtso bo'i
NK009(ta)002:4818: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa yan lag gi tshigs bzhir btab ste khong khra'i las gsum gtang /
NK009(ta)002:4819: yum brgyad kyis srid pa chags rim nas gdab cing
NK009(ta)002:4820: gsod byed rnams rang rang gi g.yon du gdab mthar
NK009(ta)002:4822: khro bo bcu'i phur bu rig pa'i gnas rim nas
NK009(ta)002:4823: gdab cing za byed rnams rang rang gi g.yas su
NK009(ta)002:4824: gdab mthar khong khra'i las gsum gtang /
NK009(ta)002:4825: steng 'og tu yum gnyis gsod byed dag dang bcas
NK009(ta)002:4826: pa dge sdig cha snyoms nas btab ste khong khra'i
NK009(ta)002:4827: las gsum gtang / sur phug gam thal byung du gdab pa zhes nang sras bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:4828: sras mchog nyer gcig rnams gnas nges med du gdab /
NK009(ta)002:4829: dam can bcu gnyis lhu bcu gnyis /
NK009(ta)002:4831: dbang phyug gnyer brgyad bdun tshad bzhir bgos la mthil bzhi /
NK009(ta)002:4832: gzhan rnams kyang gnas nges med du gdab ste mtha' sdud khong khra'i las rgyas par gtang ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:4833: man ngag lag len du bsdebs pa'i gnad yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4834: thun mong thun min gyi gtun brdung /
NK009(ta)002:4835: zhal bstab sogs 'di'i khongs su 'gro dgos pa yin kyang /
NK009(ta)002:4836: rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul thad kar bshad pa'i skabs su bab pas 'og tu 'byung ngo //
NK009(ta)002:4837: lnga pa gdab pa'i kha tshar rnams kyis rten gzhi bag chags kyi gzugs phung bsgral ba la gsum /
NK009(ta)002:4842: rdo rje gsang ba'i sogs nas /
NK009(ta)002:4843: h'u ma ma pa sh+aam ku ru /
NK009(ta)002:4844: zhes pa'i bar gyis bskul bstan te /
NK009(ta)002:4846: rdo rje ni dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i don skye 'jig med pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:4847: don de rtogs par dka' zhing phal gyi spyod yul
NK009(ta)002:4848: ma yin par gsang ba'i ste theg pa chen po'i
NK009(ta)002:4849: bka' 'am lung phyin ci ma log pa mchog gi
NK009(ta)002:4851: mtshams med lnga la bdo ba'i sdig can gnod byed
NK009(ta)002:4852: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bka'i ra ba las 'da' bar
NK009(ta)002:4853: byed pa'i bsgral ba'i yul du gyur pa rnams /
NK009(ta)002:4854: ye shes kyi lha tshogs khams gsum dbang du byed pa'i mthu dang /
NK009(ta)002:4855: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i stobs chen po dang
NK009(ta)002:4856: ldan pa'i khro bo chen po bcu la sogs pa
NK009(ta)002:4857: yis / mgo bo'am klad pa tshal pa brgya la sogs pa ru gyis shig /
NK009(ta)002:4858: de bas na bdag cag la nyon cig dang gnod cing bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang /
NK009(ta)002:4859: mdor na yang dag pa'i lam las log par 'dren pa'i tshogs zhes bos nas /
NK009(ta)002:4860: rdo rje gzhon nu nga yis bka' bsgos pa las 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK009(ta)002:4863: bdag gi dbang du gyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:4864: ces bskul ba dang bcas te thun gyi char dbab /
NK009(ta)002:4865: mtshon cha sgrol gri mthu stobs kyi rno dbal ngar
NK009(ta)002:4866: dang ldan pa thugs rje ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK009(ta)002:4867: bas gzugs kyi phung po ma dag pa'i cha shas
NK009(ta)002:4868: shul du lhag pa de mgo nas brtsams yan lag
NK009(ta)002:4869: lnga g.yon skor gyi tshul du gcad /
NK009(ta)002:4870: mthar khog pa kha phyes te dum bu stong du'ang gtubs te sil bur gtong ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4871: gnyis pa gtun brdung la bskul dang /
NK009(ta)002:4874: gdug cing sdang sems sogs nas /
NK009(ta)002:4875: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)002:4877: de'ang gang bsgral bar bya ba'i yul du gyur pa
NK009(ta)002:4878: lus ngag gdug cing zhe sdang gi sems dang ldan
NK009(ta)002:4879: pa'i bar du gcod pa'i bdud rnams gsod par gyis
NK009(ta)002:4880: shig / des na nag po'i phyogs su gyur pa'i lha min nam /
NK009(ta)002:4881: 'on te lha yin kyang rung sgrub pa po nga
NK009(ta)002:4882: la bar du gcod par byed pa po rnams kyi
NK009(ta)002:4883: sgo gsum log pa'i mthu dang /
NK009(ta)002:4884: cir yang ston pa'i rdzu 'phrul thams cad med par mdzod cig /
NK009(ta)002:4887: gnyis pa la gtun brdung thun mong ba dang /
NK009(ta)002:4888: thun min mkha' gsang sbyor ba'i gtun brdung gnyis las /
NK009(ta)002:4890: rdungs shi rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK009(ta)002:4891: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK009(ta)002:4892: rdo rje me yis snying bsregs nas //
NK009(ta)002:4893: lus sems rdul bzhin brlag par mdzod //
NK009(ta)002:4896: dgra bgegs de nyid kyi gzugs phung mtshon gyis gtubs pa de nyid rdungs shig /
NK009(ta)002:4897: ji ltar rdung bar byed pa'i tshul ni /
NK009(ta)002:4898: rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun zhes pa ni tho ba ste /
NK009(ta)002:4899: sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin dang rdo rje gzhon nu'i bka'
NK009(ta)002:4900: las 'da' bar byed pa'i sdig can mtshams med pa
NK009(ta)002:4901: lnga dang / de dang nye ba lnga la sogs par spyod par byed pa rnams la sogs te /
NK009(ta)002:4902: nyams pa'i mtshan nyid bdun nam /
NK009(ta)002:4903: bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa'i sdig pa can ma
NK009(ta)002:4904: lus pa rnams rdo rje tho ba des brdungs pas
NK009(ta)002:4905: / rdo rjee tho ba de las mthu stobs rdzu
NK009(ta)002:4906: 'phrul gyi me char drag pos sdig can gang zhig
NK009(ta)002:4907: gi rnam shes kyi snying po'i dri ma rten gzhi
NK009(ta)002:4908: phung po'i lhag ma dang bcas pa bsregs nas /
NK009(ta)002:4909: lus sems thams cad rdul phran bzhin du thal bar brlag par mdzod la /
NK009(ta)002:4910: dri ma med pa'i sems chos nyid mnyam yangs gdal ba chen por sgrol zhig /
NK009(ta)002:4912: gnyis pa thun min mkha' gsang sbyor ba'i gtun brdung ni /
NK009(ta)002:4913: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK009(ta)002:4914: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK009(ta)002:4915: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar bya /
NK009(ta)002:4916: kha tam kha tam kha tam /
NK009(ta)002:4920: de'ang thabs shes yab yum sbyor ba'i sgo nas yum
NK009(ta)002:4921: khro mo 'bar ba'i b+ha ga chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK009(ta)002:4922: gtun khung du / yab khro bo 'bar ba'i gsang
NK009(ta)002:4923: ba rig pa ye shes kyi rdo rje'i tho bas
NK009(ta)002:4924: mkha' gsang thabs dang shes rab mnyam par rol pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4925: klong du dag mnyam dgongs pa dbyer med lhag pa'i
NK009(ta)002:4926: chos sku chen po'i dbyings su brdungs par byas nas
NK009(ta)002:4927: gtun khung du / / bar gcod kyi byed po
NK009(ta)002:4928: lha yin kyang rung ste rdul phran phye mar byas
NK009(ta)002:4929: gtun khung du / / / rnam shes sangs rgyas kyi sras su bsgral bar bya ba yin no //
NK009(ta)002:4931: kha tam rnam pa gsum byung ba'i dgongs pa ni
NK009(ta)002:4932: dang pos snang srid dngos po khro bo dang khro
NK009(ta)002:4933: mo'i rang bzhin / gnyis pas khro mo rnams kyi
NK009(ta)002:4934: e chos 'byung gru gsum thar pa chen po'i dbyings
NK009(ta)002:4935: kyi gtun khung du bsgral bya'i phung po gnas pa
NK009(ta)002:4936: mo'i rang bzhin / la / kha tam gsum pas
NK009(ta)002:4937: khro bo rnams kyi rig pa ye shes kyi rdo
NK009(ta)002:4938: rje tho bas brdungs te byang chub sems kyi me
NK009(ta)002:4939: lce drag tu 'phros pas dgra bgegs kyi de bzhin
NK009(ta)002:4940: gshegs pa lnga dang spyan sogs yum lnga bsregs /
NK009(ta)002:4941: dbyings dang ye shes ro gcig tu byas /
NK009(ta)002:4942: brdungs pa'i sha khrag gis khams gsum gang ba la h'u gsum gyis dug gsum bsdus /
NK009(ta)002:4943: phata gsum gyis dkyil 'khor gsum gyi khro bo'i sprul
NK009(ta)002:4944: pas stong gsum gang bar byed pa'i don du 'chad
NK009(ta)002:4945: pa nyid do // gsum pa gab pa'i sngags drug las /
NK009(ta)002:4946: gcig kun gyi mjug la gdags pa ni zhal bstab ste /
NK009(ta)002:4947: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+h+aa kha kha /
NK009(ta)002:4953: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+h+aa zhes pas khro bo gnod sbyin zhes bos nas /
NK009(ta)002:4955: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi zhes pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la spyi bstab pa ste /
NK009(ta)002:4956: de ltar phul bas sha khrag rus gsum lhag ma
NK009(ta)002:4957: til 'bru tsam yang med par khro bo khro mo
NK009(ta)002:4958: sprul pa dang bcas pa de rnams kyis gsol te
NK009(ta)002:4959: mnyam nyid bde chen yangs pa'i zhal gyi hom khung
NK009(ta)002:4960: du bsregs / thugs dgyes pas ha ha zhes stong
NK009(ta)002:4961: gsum gang ba'i khro bo'i gad rgyangs 'brug ltar sgrogs
NK009(ta)002:4962: pa dang bcas te lhag med du rol nas /
NK009(ta)002:4963: dngos grub stsal te h'u h+aum zhes dkyil 'khor gsum
NK009(ta)002:4964: po 'od gsal bde ba chen po'i klong du ltim
NK009(ta)002:4965: gyis zhu / de'i ngang las phata phata kyi sgras
NK009(ta)002:4966: snang cha chos nyid bden pa dkyil 'khor gsum gsal
NK009(ta)002:4970: rdo rje khro bo 'bar ba dang //
NK009(ta)002:4971: rdo rje za byed srin po dang //
NK009(ta)002:4972: rdo rje gnod sbyin zhal gdangs par //
NK009(ta)002:4973: mtshan ma'i dngos po bstim par bya //
NK009(ta)002:4974: zhes gsungs pa'i don rten dang brten pa'i dngos po
NK009(ta)002:4975: thams cad spros med bde chen chos kyi dbyings su
NK009(ta)002:4976: btsan thabs su stim par byed pa'i thabs mkhas rmad
NK009(ta)002:4978: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i las rim dngos mdo tsam bshad zin to //
NK009(ta)002:4979: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa mthar phyin gsum gyi bya ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:4989: bsgrub bya dmigs su bsal ba la drag las brtsam pa'i dus yin na /
NK009(ta)002:4990: las nam grub pa dang gdod gso bar bya'i /
NK009(ta)002:4991: las ma grub par gso bar sngas na las myur du mi 'grub pa'i rgyu yin par gsungs so //
NK009(ta)002:4992: bsgrub bya dmigs bsal med na phur bu btab pa'i rjes nyid la gso ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:4993: gnyis pa yul ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:4997: gsum pa dgos ched kyang gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:4999: drag po'i las kyi rnam smin rgyud la mi gos par bya ba'i ched do //
NK009(ta)002:5001: phyag rgya'i lha rnams gzir mnan gyis dme ba'i las
NK009(ta)002:5002: la sbyar bas bsod nams kyi don du mi rung
NK009(ta)002:5004: gzas pa po gso ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:5005: snying rje byang chub kyi sems kyis zin pas bsgral
NK009(ta)002:5006: bya rnams la phan gdags shing bskyab par bya ba'i
NK009(ta)002:5007: phyir ro // gso ba'i thabs la'ang gsum ste /
NK009(ta)002:5008: las dang bya bas gso ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:5009: k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi tan+t+ra las 'byung ba'i cho ga zhib mo lta bu'o //
NK009(ta)002:5010: man ngag gis gso ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:5011: dmigs bya phur bu bdag gsum gyi byang chub kyi
NK009(ta)002:5012: sems ljang dmar mthing ga'i 'od rnam pa gsum dbyer
NK009(ta)002:5013: med 'od kyi thig le gcig tu bsdus la mi
NK009(ta)002:5014: dmigs pa sbyong ba'i man ngag rig pa mchog gi
NK009(ta)002:5015: rgyud las gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK009(ta)002:5016: 'dir phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu nyid nas gsungs
NK009(ta)002:5017: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gso ba'i tshig 'di nyid
NK009(ta)002:5021: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis rlabs kyis byin gyis brlabs so //
NK009(ta)002:5022: sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis mthur 'gyur ro //
NK009(ta)002:5023: brnag pa de kho na nyid do //
NK009(ta)002:5024: zhes bskul nas k+ai la ya brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas
NK009(ta)002:5025: pas sngar btab pa'i phur bu'i khro bo de rnams
NK009(ta)002:5026: ye shes kyi 'od zer gong bu'i rnam par gyur
NK009(ta)002:5027: pa tshur 'dus bdag la thim pas sku gsung thugs
NK009(ta)002:5028: kyi dngos grub thob ste rang nyid gdod nas lhar
NK009(ta)002:5029: gsal ba de'ang sku che la yan lag rags pas
NK009(ta)002:5030: che btsan 'gran zla dang bral bar gyur ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:5032: gso phur dang sngar btab pa'i sras mchog phur bu
NK009(ta)002:5033: gnyis kyi dbal nas bzung ste k+ai la ya lan
NK009(ta)002:5034: nyer gcig bzlas shing klad la lan gsum bskor bas
NK009(ta)002:5036: de thams cad slar 'dus pas stod khro bo zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK009(ta)002:5037: smad phur bu'i rnam pa can /
NK009(ta)002:5038: sku ri rab ltar brjid cing che ba las ye
NK009(ta)002:5039: shes kyi me 'bar zhing 'ur sgra drag po sgrogs
NK009(ta)002:5040: pas lha rnams la nyes pas mi gos shing gzi
NK009(ta)002:5041: byin dang ldan par gyur pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:5042: gzas pa po gso ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:5043: slar yang ye shes pa bcug pa'i phur bu bsgril zhing k+ai la ya lan bco brgyad bzlas te /
NK009(ta)002:5044: dmigs yul gyi snying dkar nag gi mtshams su btab
NK009(ta)002:5045: pas phur bu'i ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis gzas
NK009(ta)002:5046: po'i khams bco brgyad kyis mtshon pa'i las dang nyon
NK009(ta)002:5047: mongs pa'i dri ma thams cad dag nas sems nyid
NK009(ta)002:5048: rdul bral dwangs ma'i thig le yi ge a'i rnam
NK009(ta)002:5050: h'u h'u h'u gis bdag gi thugs ka'i ye shes
NK009(ta)002:5051: sems dpa'i thugs srog 'od ba thag gzeng ba ltar
NK009(ta)002:5052: spros pa'i rta la a yig bskyon /
NK009(ta)002:5053: ho ho ho zhes pas 'og min du rdo rje
NK009(ta)002:5054: sems dpa' yab yum sbyor mtshams su thim par gyur
NK009(ta)002:5055: pa dang / slar yang k+ai la ya lan brgya
NK009(ta)002:5056: rtsa brgyad bzlas nas phata phata phata kyis rnam shes
NK009(ta)002:5057: ar gsal ba rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kar thim
NK009(ta)002:5058: pas dbyer med du byang chub /
NK009(ta)002:5059: slar dbu ma'i lam brgyud gsang ba nas yum gyi mkhar babs /
NK009(ta)002:5060: gzhan don gzugs sku rdo rje sems dpa'i sras kyi
NK009(ta)002:5061: thu bor snang nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur
NK009(ta)002:5062: pa'i phrin las kyi thabs mkhas gsang ba zab mo'i
NK009(ta)002:5063: gnas kyi man ngag gi nges pa 'di lta bu
NK009(ta)002:5065: de ni gnas lung dpyang thag gi cho ga thugs
NK009(ta)002:5066: rje rjes 'dzin gyi phur gdab ces kyang gsungs pa
NK009(ta)002:5067: yin te / 'di dag gi don mdo tsam snying por dril te brjod pa yin la /
NK009(ta)002:5068: don zhib mor phye ste bshad du rung yang yi ges 'jigs so //
NK009(ta)002:5069: de dag gis rgyud kyi dngos bstan yongs su rdzogs pa bshad zin nas /
NK009(ta)002:5070: rtsa ba'i dum bu'am sa bcad gsum pa 'phros don bshad pas mjug bsdu ba la /
NK009(ta)002:5071: mnan sreg 'phang gsum gyis las kyi mjug bsdu zhes gsungs pa'i khog don gyi dgongs pas /
NK009(ta)002:5072: spyir sngags kyi phrin las phal che ba srung zlog bsad gsum du 'du ba yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:5073: des na srung ba'i mtha' sdud mnan gtad /
NK009(ta)002:5074: zlog pa'i mtha' sdud 'phang ba zor /
NK009(ta)002:5075: bsad pa'i mtha' sdud sreg pa hom gyi gzer kha ste gsum du mchis pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:5077: dper na yul du 'jigs pa'i dgra jag gi rnam
NK009(ta)002:5078: par 'tshe ba mi 'byung bar bya ba'i mel tshe
NK009(ta)002:5079: byas nas / mthar dgra de lag tu zin na
NK009(ta)002:5080: ldang ba med pa'i khri mun dam por bcug pa
NK009(ta)002:5081: ji bzhin dgra bgegs kyi gnod 'tshe las rgyal ba'i
NK009(ta)002:5082: srung ba'i rim pa mang du byas pa'i mthar /
NK009(ta)002:5083: de dag kun tu ldang med mnan gtad kyi rgyas
NK009(ta)002:5084: gdab pas mtha' bsdu bar bya dgos pa'i phyir ro
NK009(ta)002:5085: // de'ang gsang sngags kyi gzhung re re'i rjes su 'brangs nas rang rang gi lugs mang yang /
NK009(ta)002:5086: sangs rgyas gnyis pa o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen
NK009(ta)002:5087: po pad+ma sogs grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po dag
NK009(ta)002:5088: gi dgongs pa'i dbang du btang na /
NK009(ta)002:5092: de re re la'ang brkus te gtad pa /
NK009(ta)002:5095: de dag re rer yang 'jam gtad dang /
NK009(ta)002:5097: nor bu lugs su gtad pa gsum re'i dbye ba dang bcas pa yod la /
NK009(ta)002:5098: spyir mnan gtad la grib ma /
NK009(ta)002:5100: kha rlangs te mi gtong ba gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5101: man ngag dang ldan na dgra phung /
NK009(ta)002:5102: srung ba med na rang phung /
NK009(ta)002:5103: dus tshod ma shes na rdzas phung ba ste phung ba gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5106: gtad log gtad pa ste gdams pa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5109: skam sa gsum ste gzhug sa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5110: 'tsho la'ang lkugs pa kha med gnam gyi mtsho /
NK009(ta)002:5111: long ba mig med sa'i mtsho /
NK009(ta)002:5112: smyon pa rwa med shing gi mtsho gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5113: chu mig la'ang nag po ral gcig nags kyi chu /
NK009(ta)002:5114: dmar po gting khrol brag gi chu /
NK009(ta)002:5115: 'bras bu rwa sngon dar gyi chu ste gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5116: skam sa la'ang rgyal mtshan nam mchod rten gyi rtsa /
NK009(ta)002:5118: stag gi 'dzum la gtad pa ste gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5121: mna' dgag pa ste gces pa gsum /
NK009(ta)002:5127: klu la gtad pa sogs gang la gtad pa'i yul /
NK009(ta)002:5128: de dag so so dang 'tshams pa' gang du mnan pa'i sa /
NK009(ta)002:5130: dgra bgegs kyi ming rus ling+ga bri thabs dang /
NK009(ta)002:5131: rgyal rigs spyang ki'i thod pa /
NK009(ta)002:5132: btsun pa dang rje'u rigs glang thod /
NK009(ta)002:5133: sngags pa rab chad kyi thod pa sogs de dang der basngagasa pa'i mnan thod so sor grub nas /
NK009(ta)002:5135: lha sngags phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyas gdab cing /
NK009(ta)002:5136: las bzhi'i bros sbyong bar byas pas dgra bgegs dam
NK009(ta)002:5137: sri gang yin de dag nam yang ldang ba'i nus
NK009(ta)002:5138: pa med par mi lcags su bcug ste btson du
NK009(ta)002:5139: 'ching ba ji ltar nam zhig gnod pa'i sems zhi
NK009(ta)002:5140: ba dang thar pa'i go 'phang la sbyor bar byed
NK009(ta)002:5143: dper na gnod pa'i dgra zhig g.yul sprad nas lag tu zin pa'i tshe bsad nas /
NK009(ta)002:5144: slar gzugs phung yang me chur sbyangs te med par byed pa ltar /
NK009(ta)002:5145: bsad pa'i mngon spyod kyi srog phrogs par byas pa
NK009(ta)002:5146: de'i gzugs kyi phung po dang bcas pa me lha
NK009(ta)002:5147: ye shes pa'i zhal gyi hom rab tu 'bar ba'i
NK009(ta)002:5148: klong du bsregs par byas pas bsad pa'i mtha' sdud
NK009(ta)002:5149: kyi las kyi gzer kha yin la /
NK009(ta)002:5150: spyir nad gdon sdig sgrib sogs zhi ba'i sbyin sreg /
NK009(ta)002:5151: tshe bsod dpal 'byor nyams rtogs ye shes sogs rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg /
NK009(ta)002:5152: khams gsum srid gsum rlung sems snang ba sogs dbang du byed pa'i sbyin sreg /
NK009(ta)002:5153: dgra bgegs gnod byed 'gal rkyen bar chad sogs zlog pa drag po'i sbyin sreg ste /
NK009(ta)002:5160: 'dug stangs sogs rgyud dang man ngag gi nges pas
NK009(ta)002:5161: gsal la rgyas pa'i spros pa mang du yod cing
NK009(ta)002:5163: rdo rje me yis snying bsregs nas //
NK009(ta)002:5164: zhes pa'i rgyud tshig gis bsreg pa me'i sbyor ba /
NK009(ta)002:5165: de las kyang gsang ba'i mtha' sdud drag po hom gyi las gtso bor bstan par bzhed /
NK009(ta)002:5166: thab khung sogs kyi mtshan nyid /
NK009(ta)002:5169: log paralta ba'i gdug pa can //
NK009(ta)002:5170: mngon spyod hom ni spar bar bya //
NK009(ta)002:5171: nag po'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum la //
NK009(ta)002:5172: ngos rer sor ni nyi shu bya //
NK009(ta)002:5174: lus gnag khros pas lho phyogs blta //
NK009(ta)002:5175: skra ni spyi bor bcings nas su //
NK009(ta)002:5176: lus la thal ba chen por byug /
NK009(ta)002:5177: khros pa'i sems kyis leng+ga bsreg /
NK009(ta)002:5180: sdong po me reg shing shun la //
NK009(ta)002:5181: gzugs brnyan byas la dgug gdab bya //
NK009(ta)002:5182: tha ma dug gi me la bsreg /
NK009(ta)002:5183: tshangs pa'i tshe dang ldan pa yang //
NK009(ta)002:5186: nag po shing gi shun lpags la //
NK009(ta)002:5187: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bris //
NK009(ta)002:5188: me de la ni bsregs pa ni //
NK009(ta)002:5189: lha yang rung ste brlag par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:5190: zhes sogs las drug tshang ba'i sgo nas bsreg pa dang /
NK009(ta)002:5191: drag po'i bsad thabs dgu la sogs pas kun rdzob
NK009(ta)002:5192: mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'brel gyi mthu dang nus
NK009(ta)002:5193: pas bsgral bya'i srog myur du 'phrog cing /
NK009(ta)002:5194: don dam ye shes me lce 'bar ba'i zhal gyi
NK009(ta)002:5195: hom du ma dag lnga phung gi tshogs kyi phung
NK009(ta)002:5196: shing bsregs pas dag pa chos nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings
NK009(ta)002:5197: su ye shes kyi me lce 'od rab tu gsal
NK009(ta)002:5198: bas ma rig pa'i mun pa sangs te shes bya
NK009(ta)002:5199: kun la ye shes rgyas pa'i go 'phang dam par
NK009(ta)002:5200: sbyor bar byed pa'i thabs mkhas te /
NK009(ta)002:5201: zhi rgyas dbang gsum phan 'dogs pa'i sbyor ba /
NK009(ta)002:5202: drag po tshar gcod pa'i las sbyor te /
NK009(ta)002:5203: mdor na sregs blugs kyang phan 'dogs tshar gcod kyi yan lag tu 'du ba'o //
NK009(ta)002:5204: gsum pa 'phang ba zor thun ni /
NK009(ta)002:5205: dper na pha rol gyi g.yul las rgyal ba'i phyir du dmag bsdu /
NK009(ta)002:5207: mtshon bdar ba'i sgo nas 'thab pa'i sbyor chog thams cad zin pa'i 'og tu /
NK009(ta)002:5208: gang du g.yul bkye ba'i sa phyogs su phyin nas dgra dang g.yul sprad dgos pa ltar /
NK009(ta)002:5209: dgra bgegs byad ma'i mthu stobs gzhom pa'i phyir du
NK009(ta)002:5210: gtor zlog gi yan lag thams cad tshang bar bsags
NK009(ta)002:5212: gtor zor nad dug mtshon cha'i phung po bdag mdun
NK009(ta)002:5213: gyi lha tshogs 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK009(ta)002:5214: pa'i dmag dpung gis bskyod nas gang la dmigs pa'i
NK009(ta)002:5215: yul du ma 'phangs na don mi 'grub pas /
NK009(ta)002:5216: zlog pa'i gzer kha'i las kyi mtha' sdud 'phang ba zor thun gyi las rim yin la /
NK009(ta)002:5218: phur thun mda' thun dug thun dang //
NK009(ta)002:5219: khrag thun nyungs thun mtshe thun dang //
NK009(ta)002:5220: rdo thun rnam pa bdun zhes bya //
NK009(ta)002:5221: bsad pa'i las rnams kun la shis //
NK009(ta)002:5223: dang po zor bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs /
NK009(ta)002:5224: de la rdzas dgod de ting 'dzin gyis so so'i nus pa gdon /
NK009(ta)002:5225: mthar las la sbyor ba'i skabs su man ngag gi
NK009(ta)002:5226: gnad dang ldan par so sor 'phangs pas gang la
NK009(ta)002:5227: dmigs pa'i yul rgyab brten lha srung dang bcas pa
NK009(ta)002:5228: thal ba'i rdul phran rlung gis gtor ba ltar kha
NK009(ta)002:5229: phung rjes med du gtong ba'i thabs mkhas mig 'phrul
NK009(ta)002:5231: lha sngags ting nge 'dzin rdzas kyi rten 'brel thun
NK009(ta)002:5232: mong ma yin pa'i gnad re res kyang tshar gcod
NK009(ta)002:5233: rjes 'dzin phan gnod kyi las kyi gzer kha sna
NK009(ta)002:5234: tshogs pas don gnyis sgrub par byed pa ni gsang
NK009(ta)002:5235: sngags rdo rje theg pa kho na'i khyad chos yin
NK009(ta)002:5236: la / las kyi khro bo sras mchog gi ngo bo gri lcags kyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)002:5237: gshin rje'i gshed kyi ngo bo mda' 'ug sgro ma dug khrag gis spags pa /
NK009(ta)002:5238: rnam par rgyal ba'i ngo bo mda' khra sgro ma gu gul gyis byugs pa /
NK009(ta)002:5239: rta mgrin gyi ngo bo mda' srin byi'i sgro can
NK009(ta)002:5240: tshil chen gyis bran pa sogs made'u dug shing las
NK009(ta)002:5241: bcos pa / de dag kyang dug gi mda' thun /
NK009(ta)002:5242: sngags kyi mda' thun sogs man ngag gi nges pa dag ldan pas bsgrubs te 'phang ba ni /
NK009(ta)002:5244: gser skyems rgyas par gtang bar bya //
NK009(ta)002:5245: ma nyes dpang gzug las rnams bskul //
NK009(ta)002:5246: rdo rje'i glu ni drag tu blang //
NK009(ta)002:5247: lho phyogs kha bltas ha has gdab //
NK009(ta)002:5248: rkang pa g.yas pa bag tsam bskum //
NK009(ta)002:5249: g.yon pa rab tu bgrad la 'phang //
NK009(ta)002:5251: thod pa gling drug nag po'i phyogs //
NK009(ta)002:5252: gdong cig thang cig de la byug /
NK009(ta)002:5253: ba dang lcang ser re'u lcag pa //
NK009(ta)002:5254: spyang dug thar nu ske tshe dang //
NK009(ta)002:5255: glang chen snying dang chu srin snying //
NK009(ta)002:5256: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams bkug cing bstim //
NK009(ta)002:5257: ha la'i dug chen 'bar bar bsam //
NK009(ta)002:5259: rab chad nag po'i thod par dme khrag sogs khrag snas bkang ba khrag thun dang /
NK009(ta)002:5261: grong la gtor na mi nad dang //
NK009(ta)002:5263: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i khrag thun gyi las ltar gtor ma byas te 'phang pa gtor zor dang /
NK009(ta)002:5265: gang la dmig de brlag par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:5267: klu la brgyabs na mdze nad 'byung //
NK009(ta)002:5268: mkhar la brgyabs na grong brdal 'jig /
NK009(ta)002:5269: ces sogs gsungs pa'i nyungs kar nag sogs kyi rdzas bsgrubs te thod par blugs pa nyungs thun dang /
NK009(ta)002:5270: mtshe zor dang rdo zor ni las thams cad la 'jug pa yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:5272: mtshe dang rdo thun gdug pa la //
NK009(ta)002:5273: rab tu basngagasa pa de nyid brdeg /
NK009(ta)002:5274: de yis thal bar brlag par 'gyur //
NK009(ta)002:5275: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i zor thun gyi las rnams so
NK009(ta)002:5276: so'i man ngag gi gnad dang ldan pas 'phangs na
NK009(ta)002:5278: sgyogs kyi 'phrul 'khor drag po'i sbyor ba bzhin dmigs
NK009(ta)002:5279: pa'i yul ring por mi thogs par 'joms par byed
NK009(ta)002:5280: pa'i mthu dang nus pa khyad par du mnga' ba
NK009(ta)002:5281: yin la / de ltar srung log bsad pa'i rjes
NK009(ta)002:5282: sdud mnan sreg 'phang ba'i gzer kha'i las rim rgyud
NK009(ta)002:5283: dang man ngag rig 'dzin grub pa'i tshogs kyi phyag
NK009(ta)002:5284: bzhes nyams med kyi lugs mang du mchis pa las
NK009(ta)002:5285: yin la / / 'dir phrin las phur pa rol
NK009(ta)002:5286: pa'i bshad 'bum chen mo rig 'dzin slob dpon rnam
NK009(ta)002:5287: gsum gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i gzhung las 'byung ba
NK009(ta)002:5288: ltar sa bcad tsam bstan zin gyi /
NK009(ta)002:5289: spyi dang khyad par gyi tshul las brtsams te dpyis phyin par bshad du yod kyang /
NK009(ta)002:5290: man ngag gi nges pa gzhan du 'byung ba las shes par bya ba nyid gal che'i /
NK009(ta)002:5291: 'dir mang du dogs pas ma spros so //
NK009(ta)002:5292: de dag rnams kyis phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi
NK009(ta)002:5293: dum bu gzhung 'phros don dang bcas pa tshang bar
NK009(ta)002:5295: gzhung yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'gyur byang ni /
NK009(ta)002:5296: rdo rje phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi bid+yot+ta ma
NK009(ta)002:5297: la 'bum sde'i nang nas rdo rje rigs kyi dum
NK009(ta)002:5299: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dngos kyi phyag dpe rgya gar gyi dpe dang mthun par /
NK009(ta)002:5300: dpal ldan sa skya'i lo ts+aa ba gnas lnga rig
NK009(ta)002:5301: pa'i pan+di ta kun dga' rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po
NK009(ta)002:5302: zhes mtshan nyi zla ltar gsal ba des /
NK009(ta)002:5304: shangs sreg shing du legs par sbyar ba'i skad las bod skad du bsgyur cing /
NK009(ta)002:5305: slar yang zhus dag gi sgo nas legs par gtan la phab pa'o //
NK009(ta)002:5307: de ltar rtsa rgyud kyi dum bu 'di nyid tshig
NK009(ta)002:5308: nyung la don gyi cha nas phrin las rol pa'i
NK009(ta)002:5309: dgongs pa thams cad ma tshang ba med pa dngos
NK009(ta)002:5310: shugs kyi sgo nas bstan par mdzad pas shin tu
NK009(ta)002:5314: man ngag gi bshad tshul ci ltar byas kyang chog mod /
NK009(ta)002:5315: 'dir rgyud tshig thad kar bkral te gtso bor rgyud
NK009(ta)002:5316: ltar bshad pa'i lugs su 'bru gnyer ba'i tshig 'grel
NK009(ta)002:5317: tsam bgyis te las dang po pas go sla gtso
NK009(ta)002:5318: bor bzung / rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa /
NK009(ta)002:5320: shugs bstan gyi nges pa rnams kyang 'grel chen 'bum nag /
NK009(ta)002:5321: a mes zhabs kyi mkhon phur rnam bshad sogs khungs
NK009(ta)002:5322: ldan gyi rgyud gzhung la gzhig 'brel bcug ste mdor
NK009(ta)002:5323: bsdus pa'i lam nas bsrang bar byas pa yin gyi
NK009(ta)002:5325: mtha' dpyod sogs mdzes khrigs kyi spros pa thams cad dor ba yin pas /
NK009(ta)002:5326: thog mar 'di tsam gyi nges pa'i gsang la blo
NK009(ta)002:5327: goms nas mthar gyis phur gzhung rgya mtsho lta bu'i
NK009(ta)002:5328: rgyud lung man ngag zab cing rgya che ba'i don
NK009(ta)002:5329: gyi rin chen mtha' dag thos bsam sgom pa'i rnam
NK009(ta)002:5330: dpyod kyi ded dpon chen pos rang dbang du 'dren
NK009(ta)002:5331: par byed pa'i sgor 'gyur ram snyam mo //
NK009(ta)002:5333: rgyal kun mthu stobs 'dus pa'i me chen gyis //
NK009(ta)002:5334: 'gal rkyen bar du gcod pa'i tshang tshing nags //
NK009(ta)002:5335: thal bar brlagsa nas mchog thun dngos grub kyi //
NK009(ta)002:5336: 'bras bzang sbyin mdzad phrin las rol pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)002:5337: rgyud dang sgrub sde kun nas rab 'phags pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:5338: ngo mtshar nyi ma'i gzi byin lhag par mnga' //
NK009(ta)002:5339: 'phags bod rig 'dzin yongs kyi grub gnyis kyi //
NK009(ta)002:5340: rnam thar me tog gang gi mthu las bzhad //
NK009(ta)002:5341: dpal chen nyid kyi rang byung mi shigs glus //
NK009(ta)002:5342: rdo rje'i rgyud dang lung gi nges pa ste //
NK009(ta)002:5343: de bzhin man ngag rgya mtsho rab bsgrags pa //
NK009(ta)002:5344: pha mtha' mi mtshon chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam //
NK009(ta)002:5345: phrin las rol pa'i dpal dang gnyis med pa //
NK009(ta)002:5346: mtsho skyes rgyal ba gnyis pa la sogs pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:5347: snga 'gyur pan grub rig 'dzin che rnams kyi //
NK009(ta)002:5348: drin las ljongs 'dir tshul 'di'i la ma srol gsal //
NK009(ta)002:5349: rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu phyung ba yis //
NK009(ta)002:5350: phur gzhung nges ba'i gsang rnams rtogs byed pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:5351: rdo rje n+aa da mi shigs sgra dbyangs can //
NK009(ta)002:5352: pad+ma ka ra'i thugs kyi brnag pa nyid //
NK009(ta)002:5353: 'di don tshul bzhin nges pa'i mthu thob na //
NK009(ta)002:5354: phrin las rol pa'i rgyud don man ngag bcas //
NK009(ta)002:5355: khong du chub phyir khyad 'phags nye brgyud kyi //
NK009(ta)002:5356: byin rlabs ma yal bshad bka' dang ldan pas //
NK009(ta)002:5357: 'di na nyung ngu'i ngag gis don gyi gnad //
NK009(ta)002:5358: gsal la go bde'i rnam bshad 'di spel ba //
NK009(ta)002:5359: snga 'gyur rig 'dzin skyes mchog rnam dpyod can //
NK009(ta)002:5360: de dag kun gyi blo gros sgo 'byed yin //
NK009(ta)002:5361: ma bshad pa dang log par bshad pa yi //
NK009(ta)002:5362: nongs pa mchis kun rtsa gsum lhag pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)002:5363: khyad par zung 'jug dpal chen ku m+aa ra //
NK009(ta)002:5364: gtso dang 'khor du bcas pa'i spyan sngar 'chags //
NK009(ta)002:5365: gsang ba zab mo'i dgongs pa bkrol byas pa'i //
NK009(ta)002:5366: rnam dkar mthu yis rgyal bstan dar zhing rgyas //
NK009(ta)002:5367: bshad dang sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba yis //
NK009(ta)002:5368: nag phyogs gdug pa'i mthu stobs nyams gyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:5369: snang srid zil gnon pad+ma thod phreng sogs //
NK009(ta)002:5370: snga 'gyur rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i ring lugs mchog /
NK009(ta)002:5371: rgyud dang sgrub sde'i bka' srol mi nub par //
NK009(ta)002:5372: dbyar gyi mtsho ltar 'phel zhing rgyas gyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:5373: khyad par phrin las phur pa rol ba yi //
NK009(ta)002:5374: byin rlabs nus mthu gnam lcags tsh+wa tsh+wa'i dbal //
NK009(ta)002:5375: bdud dang dam sri kla klo'i snying la 'phros //
NK009(ta)002:5376: gnod sems gdug rtsub gzhob tu bsreg gyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:5377: gsang chen snying po'i bshad sgrub zab mo yi //
NK009(ta)002:5378: seng ge'i sgra chen rgyun chad mi mnga' bas //
NK009(ta)002:5379: log rtog nag phyogs glang po'i brtul zhugs can //
NK009(ta)002:5380: kun gyi spobs pa phra mor byed gyur cig /
NK009(ta)002:5381: phur bzhi'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa grub pa'i rig 'dzin tshom bur bcas //
NK009(ta)002:5382: sras bcas rgyal ba rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i dgyes pa'i zhal ras zla ba tshes //
NK009(ta)002:5383: shis pa' 'od zer 'bum du spro zhing sa gsum dge ba'i glu dbyangs bcas //
NK009(ta)002:5384: mdzes pa'i me tog char du bsnyil bas dge mtshan 'dzam gling kun khyab shog /
NK009(ta)002:5385: ces phur pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dum bu'i 'grel
NK009(ta)002:5386: pa go sla nyung gsal gyi tshul du bkod pa
NK009(ta)002:5387: 'adi'ang rigs kun khyab bdag bka' babs chen po bdun
NK009(ta)002:5388: gyi mdzod 'chang thams cad mkhyen gzigs 'jam dbyangs mkhyen
NK009(ta)002:5389: brtse'i dbang pos mkhon lugs phur pa'i smin grol dang
NK009(ta)002:5390: nye brgyud lan gsum du gsan pa'i rgyud bshad bcas
NK009(ta)002:5391: rgyas par stsal nas rgyud 'grel 'bri ba dang bshad
NK009(ta)002:5392: rgyun spel ba gnad gal che ba'i bka' lung dmigs
NK009(ta)002:5393: gsal stsal ba thob kyang don gnyer mkhan dkon pa
NK009(ta)002:5394: sogs kyis btang snyoms gyur nas rgyun ring song ba
NK009(ta)002:5395: na / rgyal bstan gsal ba'i snang byed e wam
NK009(ta)002:5396: thar rtse zhabs drung 'jam dbyangs blo gter dbang po
NK009(ta)002:5397: na / dang / rgyal ba kahthoga pa'i seng ge'i
NK009(ta)002:5398: khri 'dzin pa si tu mchog sprul o rgyan bstan
NK009(ta)002:5399: 'dzin chos kyi rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po zung gis
NK009(ta)002:5400: gsung bskul nan du phebs pa ltar /
NK009(ta)002:5401: thub bstan ris med pa la mi phyed dad pa'i
NK009(ta)002:5402: pad+mo rgyas pa ku s+aa li karma ngag dbang yon
NK009(ta)002:5403: tan rgya matsho'am rgyal sras blo gros mtha' yas kyis
NK009(ta)002:5404: sh+r+ai de w+ai ko ti gsum pa ts+aa 'dra rin
NK009(ta)002:5405: chen brag gi sgrub gnas kun bzang bde chen 'od
NK009(ta)002:5406: gsal gling du rang lo brgyad bcu rtsa bdun pa
NK009(ta)002:5407: la bgyis pa'i yig sbyor sogs kyi mthun rkyen mdzad
NK009(ta)002:5408: pa po ni bslab pa gsum gyi bdag nyid shes
NK009(ta)002:5409: bya kun la ma rmongs pa bla ma karma bkra
NK009(ta)002:5410: shis chos 'phel nas mdzad pa bstan 'gror sman pa'i
